# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:20
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_91dbeffc:

    # n "{vspace=60}The next morning, I recall what a perfect night last night was. So much so that I can't stop thinking about it."
    n "\n\n翌朝、昨日の夜はなんてすばらしかったのだろうと記憶を反芻する。思い出が強すぎて、考えるのをやめることができない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:22
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_f8ec4968:

    # n "It's probably not the most appropriate time to reminisce, since I have a test first period."
    n "回想にふけっている場合ではなさそうだ。一時間目からテストがある。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:24
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_9f6d1f3d:

    # n "Ah, it's so unfair. How can they do this? They hold a festival that is the culmination of what has to be at least a few weeks' worth of work on a Sunday, and then follow up with exams starting the very next morning?"
    n "あー、ほんとに不公平だよな。どうしてこんなことをしてくれるんだ？　過去何週間かの作業の集大成として学園祭を日曜日に開いておいて、その翌朝から続けて試験をやるってのか？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:26
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_288c3239:

    # n "It's got to be some kind of sick joke."
    n "悪趣味な冗談に違いない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:28
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_f42d1960:

    # n "I'm not too worried about it, but I wonder if they really couldn't have held off on this for at least another week."
    n "試験自体はそれほど心配はないけど、せめてあと１週間くらいあとに延ばせなかったのか、と疑問に思う。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:30
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_1f91f161:

    # n "{vspace=60}Well, at least the weather this morning is nice enough that I can study outside before class."
    n "\n\nまあ、少なくとも今朝は天気がいいから、始業前に外で予習ができるな。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:37
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:41
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_a8e10ab2:

    # n "{vspace=60}It's a lot more refreshing out here than it would be in the classroom. Not to mention with how quiet it is, I'm starting to think that everyone else will be sleeping in pretty late today."
    n "\n\n教室にいるよりは外にいるほうがずっと気分がすっきりする。静かなのは言うまでもない。今日はみんな相当遅くまで寝ているんじゃないか、と思い始める。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:43
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_e3c899a0:

    # n "I put down the notes I'm reviewing for a second and stare out at the school grounds, still littered with festival stalls."
    n "読み返していたノートをちょっと地面において、まだ学園祭の屋台が散らかっている校庭に目を向ける。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:45
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_9194aafc:

    # n "Looking at them now in the daytime, without paper lanterns or crowds of people to draw my attention away from them, I notice something peculiar."
    n "日差しが明るく、屋台から目を奪うような提灯や人混みがない時に見ると、妙なことに気づく。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:47
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_8bd0e480:

    # n "A lot of the stalls that Shizune, Misha, and I visited last night also happen to be ones that we worked on."
    n "昨日静音やミーシャと一緒に見て回った屋台のほとんどは、俺たち自身で作ったものだった。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:49
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_e49a48d7:

    # n "{vspace=30}…"
    n "\n……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:51
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_af19685d:

    # n "{vspace=30}That's cute. Did Shizune come up with this? It had to be intentional, especially knowing her. Did she hope that I would catch on and see the fruit of our labors?"
    n "\nかわいらしいじゃないか。静音が考えたんだろうか？　あいつのことだから、意図的にやったに違いない。俺がそのことに気づいて、自分たちが苦労して成し遂げたものを目の当たりにすることを期待していたのか？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:61
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_0d5522a7:

    # "I hear footsteps crunching the grass behind me and turn around. I feel slightly paranoid, but all I find is Shizune standing there with an innocuous look on her face."
    "芝生を踏みしだく足音が聞こえて、俺は振り向く。ちょっと行き過ぎた妄想をしてしまうけど、そこには何の表情も浮かべていない静音が立っているだけだった。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:68
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_ef2b123c:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:70
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_8e4a18dc:

    # hi "Good morning."
    hi "おはよう"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:72
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_b657b756:

    # "Why do I keep forgetting that she can't hear me?"
    "どうしていつも、静音には聞こえないってことを忘れるんだろう？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:74
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_853cc0c6:

    # "It's probably because I've gotten so used to Misha translating for both of us that I haven't actually run into many situations where I was forced to acknowledge Shizune's deafness and the problems that could stem from it."
    "たぶんミーシャが俺たち二人のために通訳してくれることに慣れすぎてしまって、俺が静音の耳が聞こえないこと、そこから生まれる問題に直面することがあまりなかったからだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:76
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_05d13e5b:

    # "I think yesterday was the first."
    "そうなったのは昨日が初めてだったと思う。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:78
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_4fa96385:

    # "I give her a wave anyway. I can do at least this much, but I'm not even going to pretend for a minute that I could hold up a conversation with her, considering my ignorance of sign language."
    "とにかく静音に手を振る。少なくともこのくらいはできるけど、手話を全然知らないことを考えれば、静音と会話ができるなんて決して思えない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:80
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_2806dcfa:

    # "Would it be rude to just go back to my notes? I don't really know what else I could do."
    "このまま予習に戻ったら失礼だろうか？　他にどうすればいいのか正直わからない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:82
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_75a17d86:

    # hi "Where's Misha?"
    hi "ミーシャはどうしたの？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:87
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_ef2b123c_1:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:89
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_64b2364d:

    # hi "Not just because I can't understand you. You two are always together anyway, so I'm not used to seeing you apart."
    hi "話が分からないからってだけじゃなくてさ。二人ともいつも一緒だし、一人でいるのは見慣れないなって"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:91
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_efe0be43:

    # "I know it's silly but for some reason talking to her makes me feel less awkward."
    "バカみたいなのは分かってるけど、どういうわけか静音に話しかけていると気まずさが薄れる気がする。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:102
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_0f894574:

    # "Surprisingly, she doesn't get mad at all. She starts signing; but it's different than usual. Shizune's hands move more slowly, and the gestures are simpler."
    "驚いたことに、静音は全然怒り出さない。手話を始めるけど、それはいつもの仕草とは違う。静音の手の動きはもっとゆっくりしていて、仕草もより単純だ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:104
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_1361b9fe:

    # "I quickly realize that this isn't sign language at all, but she's still attempting to communicate with me."
    "俺はすぐに気づく。これは手話でもなんでもないけど、それでも静音は俺と会話しようとしているんだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:106
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_1fdc3c62:

    # hi "So is this the sign language equivalent of breaking it down into layman's terms?"
    hi "じゃあそれは『手話を一般人にもわかりやすくしたもの』なのか？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:111
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_fd352afc:

    # "I'm terrified that if I attempt to gesticulate back, I'd just look like a total dumbass. The look on Shizune's face tells me that she is starting to think that trying to have any kind of back and forth like this is not exactly the best way to accomplish things."
    "もしこっちから手話で返そうとしたら、俺はただのバカにしか見えないじゃないかと恐怖する。静音の表情を見ると、今みたいな形でやりとりをしようとするのはあまりうまくないと思い始めているみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:113
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_8a2fc558:

    # "There has to be a better way."
    "もっといいやり方があるだろう。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:115
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_5df29a5d:

    # "Writing on a pad? Well, I do have paper and a pencil. What else, though?"
    "メモ帳に書くか？　まあ紙と鉛筆はあるけど。でも他に何がある？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:117
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_033ae216:

    # "Cell phones? I don't really have much use for mine here, so I barely carry it around, and I don't know if Shizune even has one."
    "携帯とか？　あるけどここではあまり使い道がないから、ほとんど持ち歩いていないし、静音が持っているかどうかも知らない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:125
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_8b67e2d6:

    # "She takes the initiative, holding up a finger to ask for a pause before pulling out a pad and pen from her bag and writing a single word on it:"
    "静音が先に動く。ちょっと待ってと指を立て、かばんからメモ帳とペンを取り出して一言書き付ける。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:132
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_ef2b123c_2:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:134
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_7f436bd2:

    # "I stare blankly at her and receive a similar but somehow more intimidating stare in response. She nudges the pad in my direction forcefully, clearly wanting me to reply."
    "俺はぼんやりと静音を見つめる。向こうからは似たような、でももっと威圧的な視線が返ってくる。静音はメモ帳を俺に向かってずいと突き出す。明らかに返事を求めている。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:141
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_180c00ec:

    # "Shizune beams with a disproportionate amount of happiness. She starts twirling her pen triumphantly as she thinks about where to go from here."
    "静音は不釣り合いなくらいうれしそうな笑顔を見せる。勝ち誇ったようにペンを回しながら、次はどうしようかと考えている。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:143
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_a3c44b6a:

    # hi "Oh, come on, it's not like we just invented fire."
    hi "おいなんだよ、大げさだな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:148
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_dbde6151:

    # "Shizune pushes up her glasses curtly, as if she had heard me, and then starts writing at a furious pace."
    "まるで今のが聞こえたかのように、静音はぶっきらぼうに眼鏡を押し上げると、ものすごい勢いで書き始める。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:152
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_28366303:

    # "I'm confused; am I supposed to take it from her and write 'okay' now?"
    "どうすりゃいいんだ。そのメモ帳を受け取って『わかった』って書けばいいのか？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:154
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_98112932:

    # "This is about the furthest thing I could imagine from a smooth, flowing conversation. It makes me envy the ease with which Misha is able to communicate with Shizune."
    "スムーズで流れるような会話とは遠くかけ離れている。ミーシャがたやすく静音と会話できているのがねたましくなる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:161
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_552347f1:

    # "I'm pretty sure I can get away with answering simple yes or no questions like this with nods."
    "こんな簡単な『はい』か『いいえ』の質問だったら、うなずくだけで返しても許されるに違いない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:168
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_a494c9b2:

    # "…Is that so?"
    "……そうなのか？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:172
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_724ccde2:

    # "Before handing that response back to her, though, I remember what I'd noticed earlier, and add:"
    "しかし返事を静音に渡す前に、さっき気がついたことを思い出して、書き加える。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:179
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_4e19594f:

    # "She shakes her head from side to side indignantly."
    "静音は憤慨したように首を左右に振る。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:188
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_a1792a8c:

    # "I'm sort of touched. Still, I have to wonder why she would go so out of her way, and I ask as much in my response."
    "なんだか心が打たれる。それでも、どうして静音がそこまでしてくれるのか、疑問を抱かずにはいられない。静音に答えるときにそう尋ねる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:197
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_54755ec7:

    # "I want to say that I was depressed for days, but stop. It's true, I was moping quite a bit, and not being too subtle about it half the time, either, so it's possible that she knew. Was everything she did just to cheer me up, then?"
    "俺はずっと落ち込んでたんだ、と言いたかったけど、やめる。その通りだ、俺は相当腐ってたし、しょっちゅうそれを表に出していたから、静音が気づいていたというのはありうることだ。 じゃあ静音がしてくれたことは全部、ただ俺を元気づけるためだったのか？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:199
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_9d5a9627:

    # hi "Thanks."
    hi "ありがとう"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:201
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_c7a3064d:

    # "I mumble it before I can catch myself, but Shizune doesn't seem to care. I write it down instead, and she nods once, as if unused to it."
    "気づくまもなく、そうつぶやいている。でも静音は気にしていないようだ。代わりに今度はメモ帳に書く。静音はそういうことに慣れていないかのように、１回だけうなずく。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:203
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_7b1d242e:

    # "The silence between us grows more vast with each passing second, and there's nothing I can do to break it. Having to write everything down on paper kind of destroys any hope of trying to be casual."
    "二人の間の沈黙が一秒ごとにどんどん膨れあがり、俺にはそれを破りたくてもどうすることもできない。何もかも紙に書かないといけないんじゃ、さりげなく何かをすることなんてできるわけがない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:210
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_5523dee2:

    # "Shizune pushes the pad right in front of my eyes, breaking my concentration. Taking the initiative again, as always."
    "静音は俺の目の前にメモ帳を押し出して、俺の意識を破る。また先手を取られた。いつも通りだな。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:215
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_81adc568:

    # "As she walks into the school building, I can't help feeling a little sad."
    "静音が学校に向かう間、俺は少し悲しい気分になってしまう。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:217
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_76b2fe88_2:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:221
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_0c09c5e5:

    # n "{vspace=60}That felt like the longest twenty minutes of my life, and all because it's so alien to me to have a face-to-face conversation with someone by passing notes to each other that I can't help coming up blank most of the time."
    n "\n\n一生の中で一番長い２０分だったような気がする。それもみんな、メモ帳をやりとりすることで一対一の会話をするなんて経験が今まで全くなかったからだ。おかげでほぼずっと頭の中が真っ白だった。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:223
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_3bde1f9f:

    # n "It makes me want to learn sign language."
    n "こういうことがあると、手話を勉強したいという気になる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:225
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_17cc4301:

    # n "That's easier said than done. Although in a school like Yamaku, they might very well have sign language classes. In that case, there would be little reason not to pursue this."
    n "言うだけなら簡単だ。でも山久みたいな学校なら、たぶん手話のクラスがあるだろう。だとしたら、やってみない理由はほとんどない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:227
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_278daf1f:

    # n "The only person who I can think to ask, at the moment, is Misha."
    n "そのことを聞ける唯一の人物は、今のところは、ミーシャだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:229
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_e1f004ef:

    # n "How badly do I want to know this? There's two options: wait until after class, or go look for her now."
    n "俺はどれだけ真剣に手話クラスのことを知りたいんだろう？　選択肢は二つある。放課後まで待つか、今すぐミーシャを探しに行くかだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:231
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_1bb73432:

    # n "I guess I'll go now, but I'm not certain where she is. My best bet would be to start searching for her in the girls' dorm, though. After all, if she wasn't with Shizune, that's probably the only place where she would be."
    n "今すぐ行くことにする。でもミーシャがどこにいるか分からない。女子寮に行って探すのが一番確率が高そうだけど。どっちにしても、静音と一緒にいないなら、たぶんそこにしかいないだろう。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:235
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_76b2fe88_3:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:245
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_281173e0:

    # n "{vspace=60}A guy casually prowling around the girls' dorm early in the morning is unacceptable, but asking Misha about sign language classes in front of Shizune would be just unthinkable."
    n "\n\n男子が朝っぱらから何気なく女子寮の中をうろついているなんて許されないだろうけど、静音の目の前でミーシャに手話クラスのことを聞くなんて絶対にありえない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:247
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_b1147a07:

    # n "She has to come to school sometime. After all, we're in the same class, so she too has to take this test."
    n "ミーシャもいつかは学校に来るだろう。大体同じクラスなんだから、あいつも同じテストを受けなきゃいけないんだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:249
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_a2ce23c7:

    # n "If I wait here, I'll be sure to see her sooner or later."
    n "ここで待っていれば、そのうち会えるに違いない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:251
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_2ee46b2b:

    # n "I just hope she doesn't walk past me while I'm flipping through my notes."
    n "俺がノートを読み返している間に、通り過ぎてしまわないといいんだけど。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:253
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_1d3a5f46:

    # n "{vspace=60}It turns out to be a pretty long wait. As students file into the school, I wonder if Misha is going to be late."
    n "\n\n結局、かなり長い間待つことになった。生徒たちが学校に集まる間、ミーシャは遅刻だろうかと疑問を抱く。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:255
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_9b185b81:

    # n "Eventually I catch sight of her. While she bounces across the grounds, it hits me that I'd have to be blind to miss her with her incredibly distinctive hair."
    n "やがてミーシャの姿が目に入る。地面をぴょんぴょんと跳ねるのを見て、盲目でもなければあれだけ目立つ髪は見逃さないだろうと思い至る。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:259
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_76b2fe88_4:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:266
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_c44f4be9:

    # mi "Hi, Hicchan~! Good morning~!"
    mi "こんちわ、ひっちゃ～ん！　おっはよ～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:268
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_699b492a:

    # hi "'Morning."
    hi "おはよう"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:270
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_ce523a9e:

    # "I don't have a lot of time left before class starts, so I cut directly to the chase."
    "授業が始まるまであまり時間がないので、単刀直入に切り出す。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:272
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_b8123627:

    # hi "Hey, can I ask you a question?"
    hi "なあ、一つ質問してもいいか？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:277
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_5ba755dd:

    # mi "A question? Hm~… Okay, Hicchan~! Sure~ sure~! I have time, but only because I'm late!"
    mi "質問？　んん～……おっけー、ひっちゃん～！　もちろんもちろん～！　時間ならあるから、でも遅刻したせいだけどね！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:279
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_4361f86d:

    # hi "What does that mean?"
    hi "どういう意味だ？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:284
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_fc7d4033:

    # mi "Haha~. I should have woken up earlier, but I was so tired~… if I had, I would have to study, but since I didn't, it won't hurt~! What is it, Hicchan?"
    mi "はは、本当はもっと早く起きなきゃいけなかったんだけど、すっごく疲れてたし～……早起きしてたら勉強しなきゃいけなかったけど、早起きしなかったから問題ないんだよ～！　それでどうしたの、ひっちゃん？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:286
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_e690168c:

    # hi "Well, there are sign language classes here, right?"
    hi "そうだ、ここには手話のクラスがあるよな？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:291
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_75ba6ace:

    # mi "Yup~! They're electives! Why do you want to know, Hicchan?"
    mi "あるよ～！　選択科目だよ！　どうして知りたいの、ひっちゃん？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:293
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_9f808d12:

    # "For some reason that question briefly makes me panic."
    "どういうわけか、その質問を聞いた俺はあっさりとパニックを起こす。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:295
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_59d4b561:

    # hi "No reason. It sounds interesting, but I guess it's too late to sign up now, right?"
    hi "別に。面白そうだなって思って。でも今から履修するのはもう遅いんだろ？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:297
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_bdde3da7:

    # "I'm not exactly being too subtle here, but Misha never seems to pick up on things like that anyway, so I'm probably being more cautious than is necessary."
    "今のはバレバレじゃないだろうか。でもミーシャはこういうことにはそもそも気づきそうにないので、俺が必要以上に警戒しすぎているということなんだろう。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:302
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_9c8a481a:

    # mi "Hm~? Ah, well, Hicchan, I've heard there are fewer and fewer students taking sign language every year. So! If you want to, I'm sure they will let you in~!"
    mi "う～ん？　あー、でもねひっちゃん、手話のクラスを取る生徒は毎年減る一方だって聞いたよ。だから！　受けたかったら、きっと入れてくれると思うよ～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:307
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_85486fda:

    # mi "Are you thinking of learning sign language, Hicchan?"
    mi "手話の勉強するつもりなの、ひっちゃん？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:309
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_348ab03f:

    # hi "…Yeah."
    hi "……ああ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:314
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_713b9765:

    # mi "If you learned sign language, Hicchan, that would make Shicchan really happy~. If you want, we can go to the teachers' office after school. They'll probably let you in."
    mi "ひっちゃん、手話ができるようになったら、しっちゃんはとっても喜ぶと思うよ～。もしよかったら、放課後に一緒に職員室に行かない？　きっとクラスに入れてくれるよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:316
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_b4a26cf6:

    # hi "That would be great."
    hi "それは助かるな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:318
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_402b5bcb:

    # hi "Don't tell Shizune that I want to learn it, though."
    hi "でも俺が手話を勉強したがってること、静音には言わないでくれよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:323
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_bb0504e6:

    # mi "Why not?"
    mi "どうして？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:325
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_f6a449f7:

    # hi "So it can be a surprise. Besides, it'll look bad if you tell her this morning, and then I find out in the afternoon that I can't take the classes."
    hi "静音を驚かせたいんだよ。それに今朝そのことを言って、午後になって授業を取れませんでした、なんてことになったら気まずいだろ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:330
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_14d6edc6:

    # mi "Aw~. You're right, Hicchan. Still, this will be hard~… It's such good news…"
    mi "え～。確かにそうだね、ひっちゃん。でもそれ難しいよ～……すごくすてきな話なのに……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:332
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_380395ab:

    # hi "I'm in the Student Council, so I might as well try learning it. Even if it's just the basics, it'd be a step up from nothing. Besides, Shizune and I can't keep relaying everything through you as if you were a phone or something, right?"
    hi "俺も生徒会に入ってるし、勉強してみてもいいと思ったんだ。基本だけだとしても何も知らないよりは一歩前進さ。それに静音も俺も、いつまでも電話か何かみたいに全部お前を通して話すわけにはいかないだろ？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:334
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:341
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_e39fcd2d:

    # mi "Wahaha~!"
    mi "わはは～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:346
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_54a7b100:

    # mi "You're right, Hicchan~!"
    mi "そうだね、ひっちゃん～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:348
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_ce617998_1:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:353
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_00fb0fea:

    # "The bell rings to signal the start of first period, cutting our conversation short. I guess I'll just ask a teacher after classes are through."
    "鐘が鳴って一時間目の始まりを告げ、会話は途中で遮られる。授業が終わってから先生に聞くことにするか。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:355
translate jp a2_shizune_message_passing_2fd84c09:

    # "Her reaction was a little strange, but I forget about it as the day goes on."
    "ミーシャのリアクションはなんだか変だった。でも日が経つにつれ、そのことは忘れてしまう。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:371
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_2c507019:

    # "The bell rings and the teacher at the front of the room gestures that classes are over for the day."
    "ベルが鳴り、教室の正面に立つ先生が手話で授業の終わりを知らせる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:375
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_f2632e7a:

    # "Although getting into this class was surprisingly easy, it's only been a few days and I'm still not used to the experience. The actual signing is easier to pick up than I expected, but most of my classmates are hard of hearing."
    "クラスに入るのは驚くほど簡単だったけど、まだ数日しかたってないし、俺自身もまだ手話の授業には慣れてない。手話そのものは思っていたよりもわかりやすいものだった。でもクラスメイトのほとんどは難聴者だ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:377
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_0c002680:

    # "On top of that, the teacher favors immersion. I haven't heard her speak since I asked if I could take the class. It's an alien concept, and really unnerving."
    "その上、授業のやり方が徹底している。俺が手話クラスをとってもいいかと聞いたとき以来、先生が言葉を発するのを聞いていない。異質な考え方だ。とても不安になる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:382
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_b1f84c9f:

    # "The moment I step out of the classroom, I hear a familiar laugh explode through the air a short distance to my left."
    "教室を出た直後に、自分のすぐ左から聞き覚えのある弾けた笑い声がするのが空気を伝わってくる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:387
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_300b2599:

    # mi "Hi, Hicchan~!"
    mi "こんちは、ひっちゃん～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:389
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_e934ea59:

    # "Misha's not in my sign language class, so this is the first time I've seen her in this context. I still don't know whether her not being in my class is good or bad."
    "ミーシャは俺とは別の手話クラスを取っているので、この辺で会うのは初めてだ。同じクラスじゃなくて良かったのか悪かったのかは、まだ判断がつかない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:391
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_8f3cab4c:

    # "It would be more interesting with her in it, but the potential for awkward situations would increase drastically."
    "一緒のクラスだったらもっと授業もおもしろくなったかもしれない。でも気まずい状況に陥る可能性も大幅に上がるだろう。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:393
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_ca61152d:

    # hi "Hi."
    hi "やあ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:398
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_2750d507:

    # mi "It's a surprise to see you here, Hicchan! …Ah, that's right! You're taking sign language, aren't you~? Right~!"
    mi "こんなところで会ってびっくりしたよ、ひっちゃん！　……あっ、そうだ！　手話のクラス取ってるんだよね！　そうでしょ～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:403
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_753a99dd:

    # mi "What do you think of it so far, Hicchan?"
    mi "どんな感じだった、ひっちゃん？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:405
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_e34e8301:

    # hi "It's not easy to learn a new language, but I think I'm getting the hang of it. Despite how different it is from other languages, it's still easier than English."
    hi "新しく言語を学ぶってのは簡単じゃないけど、なんとなく感じはつかんでる気がするよ。いくら他の言語と違いがあるっていっても、英語よりは簡単だからな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:410
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_5476afa9:

    # mi "Haha~! Really, Hicchan?"
    mi "はは～！　そうなんだ、ひっちゃん？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:415
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_d2bf800b:

    # mi "Hm~… I agree~!"
    mi "う～ん……わたしもそう思うよ！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:417
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_60737e58:

    # "I was just joking, but she's apparently totally serious."
    "冗談だったんだけど、ミーシャは真剣に受け取ったようだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:419
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_f7e53f9c:

    # "I wonder how Misha can effortlessly translate things to me while simultaneously having a conversation with Shizune in a different language like she does."
    "ミーシャは俺に手話を通訳しつつ、同時に静音と別の言語で会話する、ということを苦もなくこなす。いったいどうすればあんなことができるんだろう、と不思議に思う。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:421
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_5367ce39:

    # "Until now, I've taken for granted how amazing it is."
    "今までは、その見事な技能を当たり前のものだと思っていた。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:423
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_0e9f3bcc:

    # "Someone bumps into my shoulder and apologizes. It's getting kind of crowded here, what with it being the end of the day and all."
    "誰かが俺の肩にぶつかって、謝ってくる。学校ももうすぐ終わる時間だからか、ちょっと人が多くなってきた。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:425
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_52eb164f:

    # hi "I think we should talk somewhere else instead of the hallway. Let's go to the roof or something."
    hi "廊下じゃなくて、どこか別のところで話した方がいいな。屋上でも行かないか"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:430
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_6a3da49d:

    # mi "Okay~!"
    mi "おっけ～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:432
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_98a86c84:

    # "I decide to continue talking on the way. It's surprisingly quiet enough to carry on a conversation while doing so."
    "行きすがら、話を進めることにする。道中は驚くほど静かで、会話を続けるには差し支えない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:442
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_8033e165:

    # hi "It's still taking me some time to get used to having to look at the teacher constantly. I guess I took all those years of simply listening to the lectures while I doodled for granted. It makes taking notes a lot more difficult, too."
    hi "先生を見続けなきゃいけない、ってのに慣れるにはまだ時間がかかりそうだ。今までずっと、先生の話を聞きながら落書きすることを当たり前のことだと思ってたんだろうな。それにノートを取るのもずっと大変だよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:444
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_b1a976b7:

    # hi "The introductory class is small, and I'm already behind. I guess I have a lot of stuff to do."
    hi "初級クラスは人数は少ないけど、俺はもう遅れ始めてる。やることはたくさんあるな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:452
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_6fb5e9e5:

    # hi "Yeah, this is much better."
    hi "あー、こっちのほうがずっといいな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:454
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_9d095125:

    # "I turn around to look back at Misha and see her staring at me with her hands on her hips and her cheeks puffed outwards."
    "振り返ってミーシャを見ると、ミーシャは腰に手を当てて、頬を膨らませながら俺をにらみつけている。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:461
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_d5cfe4d2:

    # mi "Hicchan, you're behind? That's not good at all!"
    mi "ひっちゃん、遅れてるの？　そんなの全然だめじゃない！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:463
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_af0d20a9:

    # hi "I started the class a week later than everyone else. It's not that bad."
    hi "他の生徒から１週間遅れてクラスに入ったんだぜ。そこまで悪くはないだろ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:468
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_3e369f0a:

    # mi "Okay, Hicchan, let's review what you learned, then~! I'll tutor you, okay~?"
    mi "じゃあね、ひっちゃん、今まで勉強したことの復習しよう。そしたら～！　わたしが個人指導してあげる。い～い？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:470
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_25887334:

    # "This is the first time I've heard 'I'll tutor you' used outside of dirty movies; I'm not nearly as turned on as I'd have expected."
    "『わたしが個人指導してあげる』なんてセリフをエロい映画以外で聞くのは初めてだ。思ったより全然興奮しないな。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:472
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_730496fa:

    # hi "I don't know if I need a tutor yet."
    hi "まだ個人指導までしてもらわなくてもいいような気がするけど"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:477
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_e643fe3f:

    # mi "Aw…"
    mi "え～……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:479
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_a09840c0:

    # "She looks more disappointed than usual. It makes me feel awkward to see her making that kind of face."
    "普段よりもがっかりしているように見える。ミーシャのこういう表情を見ると、俺も気まずくなってしまう。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:484
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_1ba376a3:

    # mi "I want to be a sign language teacher, Hicchan! But~, it would really be great if I could try tutoring someone in it, first. Even if it's for a little while, the experience would be valuable."
    mi "わたし手話の先生になりたいんだよ、ひっちゃん！　でも～、先に誰かと個人指導の練習ができたらすごく助かるんだ。ちょっとの間でも、役に立つ経験になるよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:486
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_7f9103c6:

    # hi "Ah, well, yeah, that's true."
    hi "ああ、まあ、そうだな。それは確かに"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:488
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_70fd2256:

    # hi "I didn't know you wanted to be a sign language teacher."
    hi "手話の先生を目指してるなんて知らなかったよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:490
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_c9a51e4e:

    # "It's hard to believe she isn't intentionally trying to make me feel guilty, because she's very good at it."
    "俺の気を滅入らせるためにわざとこんなことを言っているのか、と疑ってしまう。正直とても悪いことをしてしまった気分だ。ミーシャはそういうことが得意だからな。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:492
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_dc137ec5:

    # "Still, it makes sense. She's very good at sign language already from what I've seen, and certainly has the voice for dealing with the hearing impaired. I never saw her as the teaching type, though."
    "それでも筋は通る。俺が見る限り、ミーシャは今でも手話がとても上手だ。もちろん聴覚障害者との接し方だってわきまえている。ただ、ミーシャが教えるのが得意なタイプと考えたことは一度もなかったけど。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:497
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_a678fb91:

    # mi "Hahaha~! It's the reason why I wanted to go to this school, Hicchan!"
    mi "ははは～！　この学校に来たいと思ったのはそれが理由なんだよ、ひっちゃん！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:502
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_d514e8b7:

    # mi "It's also really expensive to attend here, you know. Because I want to be a sign language teacher, I have reduced tuition fees. If it wasn't for that, I don't know if I'd be able to keep going here."
    mi "それにね、ここの学費はとっても高いんだよ。手話の先生を志望しているおかげで、わたしの学費はすこし免除されてるの。それがなければ、ここに通い続けられてたかわからない"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:504
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_d9b3c93a:

    # hi "I see. It's not that I think you would be bad at tutoring, it's just that I don't know if I need it just yet."
    hi "なるほどな。ミーシャの指導が下手だって思ってるわけじゃないんだよ。ただ自分がまだ指導してもらう必要があるかどうかわからないってだけで"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:509
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_146180c1:

    # mi "You're right, Hicchan, you're smart."
    mi "そうだね。ひっちゃん頭いいもんね"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:511
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_4f302aab:

    # hi "Well, no, that just makes me sound arrogant."
    hi "そんなことはないよ。それじゃ俺が傲慢みたいじゃないか"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:513
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_db8822b6:

    # hi "All right, please tutor me."
    hi "わかったよ。じゃあ教えてください。お願いします"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:518
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_03face0a:

    # mi "Ahahaha~! Really? Okay~! Okay okay okay~! Yay~! Thanks, Hicchan~! I'll do my best!"
    mi "あははは～！　ほんとに？　おっけ～！　おっけおっけおっけ～！　やったぁ～！　ありがと、ひっちゃん～！　わたしがんばるよ！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:523
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_c59a6d2b:

    # mi "Let's start right now~!"
    mi "今すぐ始めよ～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:525
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_0428facd:

    # hi "Too soon."
    hi "早すぎだろ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:530
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:532
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_47c17fe0:

    # mi "I miss Shicchan~…"
    mi "しっちゃんがいたらな～……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:534
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_c9c67f1d:

    # hi "Didn't you just see her this morning?"
    hi "今朝は会わなかったのか？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:539
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_c855a167:

    # mi "But it's hard to talk to her in class, Hicchan! There's no Student Council today, either~."
    mi "授業中に話しかけるのって大変なんだよ、ひっちゃん！　今日は生徒会の活動もないし～"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:541
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_c5661061:

    # hi "Well, there have been exams all week. I'd be kind of mad if there was still Student Council; I'll be glad when they are over."
    hi "まあ、今週はずっと試験だったしな。これで生徒会まであったら怒るぜ。全部終わるのが楽しみだよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:546
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_f485a5f7:

    # mi "When it's back, you're not going to skip out, right, Hicchan?"
    mi "生徒会が再開したら、さぼったりしないよね、ひっちゃん？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:548
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_d81a542c:

    # hi "Of course. I'm in it, after all."
    hi "当たり前だろ。俺も生徒会に入ってるんだから"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:550
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_bc71df72:

    # hi "Don't worry, I'm not going to just suddenly stop showing up. A promise is a promise."
    hi "心配するなよ。突然行かなくなったりはしないから。約束は約束だ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:552
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_9a95944b:

    # "Misha pauses for a second, not looking very convinced."
    "あまり信じていない様子で、ミーシャは１秒ほど沈黙する。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:557
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_4dca721e:

    # mi "Shicchan takes the Student Council very seriously, Hicchan. Now that you've joined, she works harder than before since she wants to make a good impression."
    mi "しっちゃんは生徒会のことをすごく真剣に考えてるんだよ、ひっちゃん。ひっちゃんが入会してから、いいところを見せようとして、前よりもずっと生徒会の仕事をがんばってる"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:562
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_80d9e5ad:

    # mi "Some other people joined, at first, but they stopped coming soon after. Shicchan tried to get more people interested in the Student Council but wasn't successful."
    mi "ほかにも入った人はいたけど、すぐに来なくなっちゃったの。しっちゃんはもっと生徒会に興味を持ってくれる人を増やそうとしたけど、うまくいかなかった"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:567
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_02c4b8e4:

    # mi "Even when someone would join, they'd stop coming eventually. They'd make excuses and just put it off more and more until they stopped coming altogether."
    mi "入ってくれる人がいても、そのうちに来なくなっちゃうの。なんだかんだって理由を付けて、来るのをどんどん先送りにして、結局顔を出さなくなって"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:572
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_31a622df:

    # mi "However… I believe that you really mean it, Hicchan."
    mi "でも……ひっちゃんは本気で言ってるんだって、信じるよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:574
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_1f0f7779:

    # "My eyes stay focused on her hands, tilting and moving almost of their own free will, softly signing everything she is saying to herself as she speaks."
    "ミーシャがしゃべる間、その両手が自分の意志を持っているかのように傾いたり動いたりして、口にした言葉を手話にして伝えている。俺の目はその手元から離れない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:579
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_0f52295b:

    # mi "When you said you would join, she was really happy."
    mi "ひっちゃんが入会するって言ってくれたとき、しっちゃんはすごく喜んでたんだよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:584
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_f1f008cb:

    # mi "Shicchan thinks you're interesting, Hicchan. An uninteresting person won't have the drive needed to join. Even if they do, a person that isn't interesting will quit soon after."
    mi "しっちゃんは、ひっちゃんが面白い人だって思ってるよ。面白くない人だったら、参加するだけの意欲がない。もしあったとしても、面白くない人だったらすぐやめちゃう、って"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:586
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_9db8992b:

    # mi "That's what Shicchan said."
    mi "しっちゃんはそう言ってた"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:591
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_2dd72d36:

    # mi "So~! It's my duty to make sure you keep going~!"
    mi "だから～！　ひっちゃんがちゃんと続けてくれるようにするのがわたしの役目ってわけ～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:593
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_dbec42c4:

    # hi "Is that why you want to tutor me? You're kind of sneaky."
    hi "だから俺に個人指導したいってことか？　なんかずるい奴だな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:598
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_43105377:

    # mi "Really, Hicchan? That's the first time anyone has said that about me~! Wahahaha~!"
    mi "ほんとに、ひっちゃん？　わたしのこと、そんな風に言われたのって初めてだよ～！　わははは～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:600
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_6d76e2e9:

    # "There's no chance that I would avoid student council work now."
    "これじゃあ、もう生徒会の仕事からは逃げられそうにないな。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:602
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_9d519120:

    # "Thinking back over the past few days, I've started to realize that the only reason I joined in the first place was because of Shizune; her competitiveness and force of will are alluring."
    "この数日間のことを考えると、そもそも生徒会に入った唯一の理由は静音だったことに気づき始めていた。あいつの負けず嫌いさと強気さに俺は興味を引かれている。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:604
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_5ac7b856:

    # "I can't tell Misha that, though."
    "そんなことはミーシャには言えないけど。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:609
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_0b374656:

    # mi "Okay, Hicchan, let's review what you learned in class today~!"
    mi "じゃあね、ひっちゃん、今日の授業で習ったことを復習しましょう～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:611
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_ea7d507b:

    # hi "You don't even know what I learned in class today."
    hi "お前、俺が今日授業でやったことなんて知らないだろ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:616
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_47d43dc9:

    # mi "Hm~, you're right, Hicchan~! Okay, let's start with the basics, then~! I'll just teach you everything from the beginning~!"
    mi "う～ん、そうだねひっちゃん～！　おっけー、じゃあ基本から始めようか～！　一番最初から全部教えてあげるよ～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:618
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_cd9123d1:

    # hi "You're kidding, right?"
    hi "それ、冗談だよな？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:623
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_b21211fc:

    # mi "Huh~?"
    mi "え～？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:625
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_ae886b73:

    # hi "You're serious? That's like, days of lessons, and we're not even learning on the same level…"
    hi "本気なのか？　そんなの授業だったら何日もかかるし、しかも俺たちは学んでるレベルだって違うんだぜ……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:630
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_59aa4b5e:

    # mi "It's like riding a bike, Hicchan~! You never forget the basics! Wahaha~!"
    mi "こんなの自転車に乗るようなものだよ、ひっちゃん～！　基本は絶対忘れないの！　わはは～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:635
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_34719828:

    # mi "I don't know how to ride a bike, though~…"
    mi "でも、わたしは自転車の乗り方わかんないんだけどね～……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:637
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_9d8a2c49:

    # "Oh no."
    "なんてこった。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:642
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_35ab135a:

    # mi "Right, right~. I want to be a teacher one day, so of course I know what I'm doing… Okay~! Okay okay okay~! We're starting~!"
    mi "うんうん～。わたしはいつかは先生になりたいから、もちろん自分が何やってるかはわかってるよ……おっけ～！　おっけおっけおっけ～！　じゃあ始めるよ～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:649
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_a3b008f1:

    # mi "Uh…"
    mi "えっと……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:654
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_40d58157:

    # mi "…Mmm~…"
    mi "……んんん～……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:659
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_2342e611:

    # mi "Ahahaha~…"
    mi "あははは～……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:661
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_8575efe5:

    # "She looks like she's trying very hard, so this could be bad. Well, learning a language is vastly different from teaching it, and the first step is usually the hardest part. Honestly, I couldn't do any better."
    "ミーシャはものすごくがんばっているように見える。ということはこれはまずいのかもしれない。 まあ、言語を学ぶことと教えることにはとても大きな違いがあるし、その最初のステップはたいていの場合一番難しいところだ。正直、俺だってミーシャよりうまくやれるとも思えない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:663
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_e2cf25f9:

    # "Still…"
    "でもなあ……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:668
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_5da649f2:

    # mi "Um… Sign language was formally introduced in the 18th century by a Frenchman named… ah… whose name I can't pronounce, and he started the first public school for the deaf in 1755, but the unwritten history of sign language is said to…"
    mi "えっと……公式な話をすると、１８世紀に……あー……名前は発音できないけど、フランスの人が手話を発表したの。その人は世界初のろう学校を1755年に始めて、でも文書には残っていない手話の歴史が……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:673
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_c4f05c8e:

    # mi "I don't really know where to start. Sorry~… Well~, what better place to start than the history of sign language? Right~? Right~!"
    mi "どこから話せばいいのかわからないよ。ごめんね～……とにかく～、手話の歴史はお話を始めるには一番いいでしょ？　でしょ？　ね～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:678
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_455911f8:

    # mi "No, wait, maybe the alphabet. Okay~, the alphabet it is, then!"
    mi "あ、待って、５０音の方がいいかも。おっけ～、じゃあ５０音できまりね！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:685
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_dc6cd0aa:

    # mi "Okay, Hicchan~! This is pretty basic stuff, although some people think that this is all of signing, and forget there are all kinds of specific gestures and words."
    mi "おっけ、ひっちゃん～！　これが基本の基本だよ。でもこれが手話のすべてだって思いこんで、いろんな具体的なしぐさや単語を忘れちゃう人もいるの"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:690
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_e6e0bad6:

    # mi "Although you can't really get anywhere else without the basics! This is A. Do you see it? Now, you try!"
    mi "それでも基本を知らないとどうにもならないからね！　これが『あ』だよ。わかる？　じゃあひっちゃん、やってみて！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:692
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_1817a117:

    # hi "I already know this, though."
    hi "それならもう知ってるけどな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:694
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_8a38930a:

    # "I humor her anyway."
    "ともかく、ミーシャのご機嫌をとることにする。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:699
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_a36c7048:

    # mi "Hahaha! Yeah, that's it!"
    mi "ははは！　そうだよ、その調子！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:704
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_fd2862fb:

    # mi "Now, this is B, and this is C."
    mi "じゃあ、これが『い』で、これが『う』だよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:706
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_b80df628:

    # "Misha makes one symbol with each hand, without specifying which is which."
    "ミーシャは左右それぞれの手でひとつ文字を形作る。でもどちらの手がどの文字かは言わない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:717
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_43066202:

    # mi "And now D, E, F, G, H, I, J, K, L, M, N, O, P, Q, R, S, T, U, VWXY 'n' Z~!"
    mi "で、『えお、かきくけこ、さしすせそ、たちつてと、なにぬねの』…… ……『わを』、最後に『ん』～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:719
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_ad4f94db:

    # "Yeah, this is bad."
    "ああ、こりゃ大変だ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:721
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_4fd7a3aa:

    # hi "Do you think Shizune wants to do some student council work today anyway? We could go."
    hi "やっぱり今日は生徒会の仕事をしようって静音が思ってたりはしないかな？　そっちに行ってもいいぜ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:726
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_f80a7d54:

    # mi "Of course not, Hicchan~!! Come on, I'll do it again! A, B, C, D, E, F, G, H, I, J, K… Your turn~!"
    mi "そんなわけないでしょ、ひっちゃん～！！　ほら、もう一回やるよ！　あいうえお、かきくけこ……ひっちゃんの番～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:728
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_aff046ae:

    # hi "So there's really no student council work that needs doing, or anything like that?"
    hi "じゃあ、やっておかないといけない生徒会の仕事とか、そういうものは本当にないんだな？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:733
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_58d08d5a:

    # mi "What are you talking about, Hicchan? Come on, sign, sign~!"
    mi "何言ってるの、ひっちゃん？　ほら、やってやって～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:735
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_1f92e5eb:

    # hi "Like this?"
    hi "こうか？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:740
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_b2f2e184:

    # mi "No, like this!"
    mi "ちがうよ、こう！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:742
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_00ecf413:

    # hi "Like…"
    hi "こんな感じ……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:750
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_c0b22256:

    # mi "This~!"
    mi "こうだよ～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:752
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_3d4fb1b1:

    # hi "Uh… huh…"
    hi "あー……そっか……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:757
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_22be7289:

    # mi "I wish Shicchan was here, this would be so much easier with her. Hahaha, that's how sign language is taught most of the time, anyway, with two instructors~! Did you know that, Hicchan?"
    mi "しっちゃんがいたらよかったな。いたらずっと簡単にできたのに。ははは、普通はそうやって手話を教えるんだけどね。先生が二人でね～！　ひっちゃん、知ってた？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:759
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_7efcef0d:

    # hi "No."
    hi "ないよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:761
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_b4669a73:

    # "I let my brain run through what this would be like if Shizune were here."
    "静音がここにいたらどうなるか、脳内で想像してみる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:763
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_ce617998_1:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:768
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_8e93eed4:

    # mi "Hicchan~! Are you paying attention?"
    mi "ひっちゃん～！　話聞いてる？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:770
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_142d50b9:

    # hi "Yeah."
    hi "そうだな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:775
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_e0605432:

    # mi "Shicchan says that sign language is different from any other, because you have to think about everything before you say it. That means every word has more weight, Hicchan. Every single one is more important than normal."
    mi "しっちゃんが言ってたけど、手話は何かを言う前に頭の中ですべてを考えないといけないから、他のどんな言語とも違うんだって つまり、一つ一つの単語がもっと重みを持ってるってことだよ、ひっちゃん。言葉の一つ一つが普通よりも大事なの"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:780
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_f6c880dd:

    # mi "So~, pay attention, please."
    mi "だから～、ちゃんと、集中してね"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:785
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_0d1c7fdb:

    # "She continues her basic rundown of the basics of sign language. Eventually she starts talking about stuff I start to recognize."
    "ミーシャは手話の基本について、駆け足で講義を続ける。やがて、俺にもわかる内容を話し始める。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:787
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_110e28e1:

    # "In the end, I'm impressed. It took a bit of stumbling to get there, but as a teacher, she's pretty good when she's serious."
    "終わってみると、俺は感心していた。最初はちょっとつまずいたけど、本気になったミーシャはとても教えるのがうまい。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:795
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_a69c6240:

    # "After awhile I start to notice that it's getting late, so I thank Misha, bid her goodbye, and go back to my dorm."
    "しばらくして、もう遅い時間になっていることに気づく。俺はミーシャにお礼を言って別れを告げ、寮に戻る。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:802
translate jp a2_shizune_talk_to_the_hand_910b2921:

    # "I learned a lot today."
    "たくさんのことを学んだ日だった。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:818
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_43cb5adb:

    # "I'm jolted awake by a thunderous banging sound coming from my door."
    "ドアをバンバンと叩く大きな音が聞こえてきて、俺は飛び起きる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:820
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_fdf1ae4f:

    # "My first thought is, it could be Shizune. After all, only a deaf person or a jackass would knock that loudly at this hour."
    "最初に頭に浮かんだのは静音だった。こんな時間にあんな大きな音でノックする人は、耳が聞こえない人か、さもなければ大馬鹿野郎に違いない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:822
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_0cf91355:

    # hi "Who is it?"
    hi "誰だよ？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:824
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_37c357fe:

    # "Of course, if it's Shizune, she wouldn't be able to hear that or answer it."
    "もちろん、静音だったら今の声も聞こえないし返事もできない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:826
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_d1a5c171:

    # "There's no reply, so I'm kind of pleased. I haven't seen Shizune in a while."
    "返事がないので、ちょっとうれしくなる。しばらく静音に会っていなかったし。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:836
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_62b4673d:

    # "Opening the door, I find Kenji standing out in the hall, his eyes nervously darting from side to side."
    "ドアを開けると、健二が廊下に立っている。その目つきが神経質に右へ左へと素早く動く。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:838
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_50684ad3:

    # hi "Oh, it's you."
    hi "なんだ、お前かよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:843
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_f4ec0af8:

    # ke "Yeah, it's me. What kind of reaction is that?"
    ke "そうだよ俺だよ。なんだそのリアクションは？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:845
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_5bc44b2c:

    # hi "Well, I'd be able to give you a more personalized response if you had answered when I asked who it was."
    hi "まあな、俺が誰だって聞いたときに答えてくれていれば、もっと相手に合った返事ができたんだけどな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:850
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_08ee7198:

    # "Kenji frowns and pushes up his glasses exactly like Shizune."
    "健二はしかめ面をして、静音とまるで同じしぐさで眼鏡を持ち上げる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:852
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_e397122c:

    # ke "Why are you making that weird face?"
    ke "どうしてそんな変な顔してるんだ？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:854
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_b6ec4598:

    # "I wonder how he's able to see me making a face now, yet wasn't able to the millions of other times I've reacted to something weird he has said or done. I kind of want to pursue this, but am too tired to actually do it."
    "これまでこいつのおかしな言葉や行動に何百回顔をしかめても気づかなかったくせに、どうして今だけは俺の表情がわかるのかと不思議に思う。その理由を問い詰めたいけど、そうするにはもう疲れすぎている。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:856
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_7de334c9:

    # hi "Shizune pushes her glasses up just like that. You know, the Student Council president. It's just a little weird."
    hi "静音がそういう風に眼鏡を持ち上げるんだよ。知ってるだろ、生徒会長。なんか変だなって"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:861
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_7099a560:

    # ke "What the hell? What do you mean there's this girl who does the same thing? You mean she touches her glasses? I do that, that's my thing."
    ke "んだとお？　同じことする女子がいるってどういうことだよ？　そいつは眼鏡にさわるってのか？　これは俺の専売特許だ、俺の技だぞ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:863
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_2c20f3f3:

    # ke "Who is this bitch? Why are bitches all up in my business, stealing what I do?"
    ke "どこのどいつだそのビッチは？　どうしてビッチどもは俺のやることに首突っ込んで、俺のやることをパクりやがるんだ？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:868
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_574a6e96:

    # "His character flips from anger to fear in the blink of an eye."
    "健二の気分は怒りから恐れに一瞬でひっくり返る。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:870
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_7485d1b1:

    # ke "Is she trying to replace me? Pod people? No, wait, that's an exact copy. Pod women?"
    ke "あいつ、俺を取り替えちまおうとしてるのか？　ポッドピープルか？　いや待て、それじゃ完全なコピーだ。ポッドウーマンか？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:872
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_6b3911dc:

    # ke "It's like my two greatest fears combined."
    ke "まるで俺が最も恐れていた２つのことがくっついたみたいだ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:877
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_86b49537:

    # ke "It is!"
    ke "まさにそうだ！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:879
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_db0c0901:

    # "I can't believe he has a point…"
    "そんなわけあるかよ……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:884
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_d0dcbfc7:

    # ke "Hey, you going to go into town today?"
    ke "おい、今日は町に行くのか？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:886
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_3038084f:

    # hi "Uh, maybe later."
    hi "あー、後で行くかもな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:891
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_d09d38ef:

    # ke "Okay. Awesome. I have some… stuff I want you to pick up for me at the post office. Some delicate and secret stuff."
    ke "よし。バッチリだな。郵便局で受け取ってもらいたい……ブツがあるんだ。繊細な秘密の代物だ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:893
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_a826a9e1:

    # "He speaks in a whisper, as if talking about his mail in even a normal tone of voice will jeopardize it."
    "健二はひそひそと話す。その郵便物について普段の声の大きさで話すだけでも、それが危険にさらされるとでも言わんばかりに。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:895
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_868cf4a6:

    # hi "You can have your mail sent directly here, you know."
    hi "直接ここに送ってもらうことだってできるんだぜ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:900
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_47b6ec2a:

    # ke "No you can't. You can have your mail sent to the school, and then the Student Council picks it up, and then they give it to you. That's not the same as the mail appearing in your hands."
    ke "できるかよ。学校に送ってもらったら、生徒会がそれを受け取って、奴らが俺たちに渡すんだ。手紙が自分の手に渡るのとはわけが違う"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:902
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_d01526d3:

    # ke "I don't trust the Student Council. Many dudes don't get their mail here, you know."
    ke "俺は生徒会は信用しない。ここの男たちは郵便なんて受け取ってないんだぜ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:907
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_3ef00601:

    # ke "They probably steal it all! They think that just because it's sent to them, they have a license to steal? I can just see them now, elbow deep in mail, fast grabbing all the free swag they can get a hold on. Sickening."
    ke "あいつらは全部盗んでるに違いない！　自分たちに送られたから、自分たちには盗む権利があるとでも思ってるのか？ 俺には見えるぜ、あいつらが郵便物の山にひじまで腕を突っ込んで、持てるだけお宝をつかみ取っていくのが。反吐が出るぜ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:909
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_b205e952:

    # hi "Where can I find this mailman who can conjure mail out of thin air and into your hands?"
    hi "その、どこからともなく手紙を取り出して手渡してくれる郵便屋さんってのはどこに行けば会えるんだよ？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:911
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_117d23e4:

    # ke "I don't know, I bet the Student Council killed him to preserve their monopoly on all the students' shit."
    ke "知らん。生徒会が殺したんだろうよ、生徒の私物を独占し続けるために"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:913
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_1b31fc7a:

    # hi "It doesn't work that way."
    hi "そんなことはないだろ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:915
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_bd03f497:

    # hi "Is that what you wanted, though? Fine, I can pick up your mail for you, but eventually I'm going to collect on all these favors. You already owe me some money."
    hi "でもまあ、それが頼みごとか？　わかったよ、お前の郵便は受け取りに行ってやるけど、いずれこの貸しは返してもらうからな。お前まだ俺から借りた金があるだろ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:920
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_6cc66624:

    # ke "Thanks for reminding me. I'll pay you back after I get my package."
    ke "教えてくれてありがとうよ。ブツを受け取ったらお前に返す"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:922
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_e7169f05:

    # ke "Yeah, my bad, I can't really pay you until then. I'm still broke."
    ke "そうだな、悪いけど、それまではマジで返せないんだ。まだ一文無しでさ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:924
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_181395c1:

    # hi "Then I'm basically doing it for money, like a job. Why do you need the package first? Is there money in the package?"
    hi "じゃあ俺はお金のために受け取りに行ってやるわけだ、仕事みたいに。そもそもなんでそのブツが必要なんだよ？　金でも入ってるのか？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:929
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_cec583aa:

    # ke "Nah."
    ke "いや"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:931
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_c790c319:

    # "I am seriously dumbfounded."
    "俺は本気であきれる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:933
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_16053745:

    # hi "Why can't you get it?"
    hi "どうして自分で受け取りに行かないんだ？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:938
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_c9999502:

    # ke "Because I am going to remodel my room today into a war room."
    ke "今日はこれから自分の部屋を作戦司令室に模様替えするんだ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:940
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_481b81cc:

    # ke "As the days go by, I realize more and more how dangerous feminism is. It really is everywhere, even in places like Iran. You can't tell how far up it goes."
    ke "日が経つごとに、俺はフェミニズムの危険をより強く自覚するんだ。あれは本当にあらゆるところに存在する。イランのようなところでさえ。どこまで浸透しているかなんてわかりゃしない"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:945
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_2de5d654:

    # ke "When the war begins, if we haven't transcended the concept of nations to fight for our genders, it will be chaos."
    ke "戦争が始まったとき、俺たちの性の戦いのために国という概念を乗り越えることができていなかったら、待っているのは大混乱だ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:947
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_8be2db5e:

    # ke "No one will know who will take what side, and a war against feminism wouldn't just mean World War III, but the end of all life on Earth as we know it."
    ke "誰がどちらの側につくのか、誰もわからない。対フェミニズムの戦争はただの第三次大戦じゃない、地球上に現存するあらゆる生命の終わりだ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:949
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_d886c686:

    # ke "If we lose, all our supple Japanese women will be raped and enslaved by a bunch of sociopathic lesbian supremacists."
    ke "俺たちが負ければ、我らが柔順な大和撫子はみんなソシオパスのレズビアン至上主義者に強姦されて、奴隷にされてしまうんだ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:951
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_f8f5a191:

    # ke "Meanwhile, the handful of men that didn't die in the war will be castrated and forced to repair toilets and build massive monuments commemorating the feminist victory."
    ke "その間に、戦争で死ななかった一握りの男たちは去勢されて、トイレの修理とフェミニストの勝利を記念する巨大なモニュメント建造を強いられるんだ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:953
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_620cd863:

    # hi "That's crazy. You're crazy. I think you're overthinking this."
    hi "おかしいだろそれ。お前おかしいだろ。考えすぎだと思うぞ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:955
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_16da0c70:

    # ke "As the days go by, I realize more and more that you are not ballin'."
    ke "日が経つごとに、お前はつくづくいけてない奴だって思うぜ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:957
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_e7d42b77:

    # hi "We've only talked like four times."
    hi "まだ４回くらいしか話してないけどな、俺ら"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:962
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_179f1467:

    # ke "Oh. Sorry."
    ke "ああ。悪い"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:964
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_0b171c0a:

    # hi "Yeah, whatever, I'll get your package."
    hi "なんでもいいよ。お前の郵便は取ってきてやるから"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:969
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_8c4739a5:

    # ke "Awesome."
    ke "助かるぜ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:978
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_2a6d2c78:

    # "I close the door and jump right back into bed."
    "俺はドアを閉じ、またベッドに飛び込む。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:982
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_18294cec:

    # "The second my head hits the pillow, a painfully loud ringing assaults my ears, and I realize it's my clock. The alarm going off means that right now is the time I'm supposed to wake up in the first place."
    "頭を枕に乗せたとたんに、ひどくやかましいベルの音が耳を刺し、それが目覚まし時計だと気づく。目覚ましが今鳴るということは、そもそもこの時間に起きていなきゃいけないということだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:984
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_d4cebc88:

    # "On weekdays, at least."
    "少なくとも平日なら。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:988
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_07ccd715:

    # "I pick it up and throw it without looking up. It gets wedged between the bed and the wall, the noise not stopping. In fact, it seems to grow louder."
    "目覚まし時計を拾い上げて、見もせずに放り投げる。ベッドと壁の間にはまりこみ、音は鳴り続ける。というか、どんどん音が大きくなっているようだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:992
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_4b12bfea:

    # "By the time I'm able to pry it out of there I know I'm not going to be able to go back to sleep. The only thing I can think of doing now is going into town and just getting Kenji's stupid package, but it's too early for that."
    "時計を掘り出したころには、もう寝直せないほど目が冴えてしまうのはわかりきっている。今できることといえば、町に行って健二のふざけた郵便を受け取りに行くことだけだ。でもそれにはまだ時間が早すぎる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:994
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_2ec8f192:

    # "After showering, I take my medication. I'm actually very hungry today since I went without dinner yesterday, and before that I had just a very light lunch."
    "シャワーを浴びてから薬を飲む。昨日夕食を食べなかったし、その前の昼飯もとても軽かったので、今日はとても腹が減っている。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:996
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_22c80257:

    # "I eat the pills, chomping on them like a leg of lamb. They are unbelievably bitter and disgusting."
    "羊の足か何かのように、ぼりぼりと薬をかみ砕いて食べる。信じられないくらい苦くてまずい。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:998
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_f1df7fe7:

    # "Well, good medicine tastes bad, or something like that. I'm still hungry, and there's still a lot of time to kill, so I decide to go into town and find somewhere to have breakfast."
    "まあ、良薬は口にまずい、だったっけ。まだ腹は減っているし、時間はたっぷりあるので、町に出て朝ご飯を食べられる場所を探すことにする。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1000
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_ca6f4bc3:

    # "I can't remember the last time I ate out. Besides, the weather is nice, so why not?"
    "前にいつ外で食事をしたか思い出せないし。それに天気もいいし。行ってやろうじゃないか。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1007
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_2f09bb7b:

    # "The walk into town is longer than I remember, possibly because it's been a while, and probably because I rarely come here alone. There are barely any cars on the road because it's so early in the morning, making it unusually quiet."
    "町に行く道は覚えていたよりも長かった。しばらくぶりだったのと、一人で来ることがめったになかったからだろう。時間が早すぎるので、道を走る車もほとんどなくて、いつにない静けさだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1012
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_8042cdb5:

    # "The first thing I do is start looking for a place to eat. Immediately I think of the Shanghai, but I want something more substantial than sandwiches or a cake."
    "最初に食事ができる場所を探す。真っ先に上海が思い浮かぶけど、サンドイッチやケーキよりはしっかりしたものを食べたい。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1014
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_2ba8556b:

    # "Since it's so early, though, I decide to get Kenji's package first."
    "まだ時間はかなり早いけど、先に健二の荷物を受け取りに行くことにする。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1016
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_24d8feb6:

    # "Picking it up at the post office doesn't take very long, but the moment I see it, I'm enraged about what a pain in the ass it will be to carry this thing all the way back to the school."
    "郵便局で荷物を受け取るのはすぐに終わったけど、その荷物を見た瞬間に、こんなものを学校まで持って帰るのかと激怒する。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1029
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_ec8a14d4:

    # "The box is huge, you need two hands to hold it. Insultingly, it's not even very heavy."
    "その箱は巨大で、両手を使わないと持てない。腹立たしいことに、大して重いわけでもない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1031
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_62e7a391:

    # "I was thinking of wandering around for a little while, but with this thing in tow, that's going to be a real problem. I guess the Shanghai is my only option now."
    "しばらくその辺を散歩しようと思っていたのに、これを持ち歩きながらというのは大問題だ。これでは上海に行くしかないみたいだな。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1042
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_c37ae111:

    # "Everything else is closed, and the ones that aren't all have about the same menu. That fact also makes me want to throw some more business Yuuko's way."
    "他の店はどこも閉まっているし、そうでない店もメニューに大した違いはない。そのこともあって、優子さんの仕事に少し貢献してあげたいという気持ちになる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1049
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_1bcf1113:

    # "Before I can even open the door and enter, someone taps me on the shoulder from behind. I turn around and see Shizune there. Instinctively, I look for Misha, but she doesn't seem to be here."
    "ドアを開けて中に入ろうとする前に、誰かが後ろから肩を叩く。振り向くと静音がいる。本能的にミーシャの姿を探すけど、ここにはいないようだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1054
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_ece4a6b6:

    # ssh "Good morning."
    ssh "おはよう"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1056
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_f428269f:

    # "Looks like those sign language classes are already starting to pay off. I'm tempted to sign it right back, but then she might think I know a lot more than I actually do."
    "手話のクラスは早くも役に立っているみたいだ。すぐに手話で返事をしたくなるけど、そうすると俺が自分の実力以上に手話を理解していると思われてしまうかもしれない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1058
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_f0d36342:

    # "For now, I just give her a wave and open the door. She's probably here for her morning tea and didn't come here just to greet me. It turns out I'm right, as Shizune follows me inside the teahouse."
    "とりあえず、静音に手を振るだけにしてドアを開ける。静音も朝の紅茶を飲みに来たのであって、わざわざ俺に挨拶しにここに来たわけじゃないだろう。俺について店内に入ってくるので、実際その通りだったとわかる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1065
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_13d7eee9:

    # "It's a total ghost town in here. It's not exactly peak hours, but every other café I passed had at least a few customers."
    "中は完全な廃墟だった。今は混雑する時間というわけではないけど、他に見かけた店には少なくとも何人かは客がいたぞ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1067
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_6a1b2777:

    # "Actually, the Shanghai has been fairly empty every time I passed by. How does this place stay in business?"
    "実際通りかかるたびに見ているけど、上海はいつも客が入っていない。これでどうして商売を続けていられるんだろう？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1072
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_40bb4093:

    # yu "Hello! Thank you for choosing to patronize our establishment!"
    yu "いらっしゃいませ、こんにちは！　ご来店ありがとうございます！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1087
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_20043695:

    # "Yuuko bows with the force of a falling axe and her head collides with the box in my hands, launching it towards the floor."
    "斧を振り下ろすかのような速度で優子さんがお辞儀をする。そのとき俺が抱えていた箱が頭に当たって、地面に落ちてしまう。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1094
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_144eb8fa:

    # yu "Oh no, I'm sorry, I'm really sorry, sorry, please forgive me!"
    yu "大変、ごめんなさい、ほんとにごめんなさいごめんなさいごめんなさい、本当に申し訳ありません！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1096
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_f74d683b:

    # hi "It's okay, and you don't have to do that 'Hello, thanks for choosing our shop!' thing since we know you."
    hi "大丈夫ですよ、あと『ご来店ありがとうございます！』はなくていいですから。もう優子さんとは知り合いだし"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1101
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_4f476eb5:

    # yu "But it's part of my job."
    yu "でも、それも私の仕事だから"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1106
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_2038c6b7:

    # yu "You're here early, what can I get you?"
    yu "今日は早いのね。ご注文は？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1108
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_8078f022:

    # hi "I just want some coffee for now."
    hi "とりあえず、コーヒーだけで"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1121
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_e696af71:

    # "I wonder what Shizune wants. Without Misha, there's no real way to tell, or any way to even ask. I haven't learned about that yet. She's here, so I'm pretty sure that means she wants something too."
    "静音はなにを頼みたいんだろう。ミーシャがいないと、それを知る手段もないし、本人に聞くことさえできない。その辺はまだ手話クラスで教わっていない。ここにいるってことは、静音も何か頼むつもりなのは確かだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1123
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_4c6e28ef:

    # hi "Er, I don't really know what Shizune wants. Does she have a usual?"
    hi "ええと、俺は静音の注文は知らないんです。静音にもいつもの注文ってあるんですか？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1125
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_6aaf4ee5:

    # hi "Wait, she might want something else, though. Perhaps you should bring us a menu just in case."
    hi "ああでも、他のものを頼みたいと思ってるかもしれないな。念のためメニューをもらってもいいですか"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1127
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_a9c6f12d:

    # "I look around for one, but can't find anything that looks remotely like a menu."
    "メニューを探してあたりを見回すけど、多少なりともメニューっぽく見える物体は一つも見あたらない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1132
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_691bcfd9:

    # yu "Menus… I'll look for one right now."
    yu "メニューは……すぐに探してくるね"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1134
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_0f638bea:

    # hi "Huh?"
    hi "えっ？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1139
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_81303457:

    # yu "Um… there are menus. They're just… rare."
    yu "あの……メニューはあるの。ただ……レアなだけで"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1141
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_945b7462:

    # "It's only a restaurant menu, not a collector's edition."
    "ただのレストランのメニューじゃないか。特別限定版とかじゃないんだぞ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1146
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_ef2b123c:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1148
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_86d35800:

    # hi "Weird."
    hi "変なの"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1153
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_3e8507cf:

    # yu "Is that what Shizune is saying?"
    yu "静音ちゃんがそう言ってるの？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1155
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_35ef789c:

    # hi "Nah, she can't hear you. It's just weird for a café to make you have to go out of your way to look for a menu."
    hi "いえ、静音には聞こえてないですよ。ただ、わざわざメニューを探し回らないといけない喫茶店っていうのはへんてこだな、って"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1160
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_b819fda3:

    # yu "Weird…?"
    yu "へんてこ……?"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1165
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_ad5bfad1:

    # yu "Yes… you're right. It's so illogical. There are so many things… Like, why is it called the Shanghai? This is a Western style teahouse… but, the name is Chinese… and the architecture is old-fashioned, but my uniform is so modern and sophisticated…"
    yu "そうだわ……その通りよ。全然理屈に合わないわ。そんなことばっかりよ…… たとえば、どうして店の名前が上海なの？　洋風の喫茶店なのに……名前は中国風だし……それに建物は古いけど、私の制服はこんなに今風であかぬけてるし……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1167
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_2f390fcb:

    # "She looks like she's about to pass out. If she does she'll probably fall forward and make a mess of everything."
    "優子さんは今にも気絶しそうだ。そうしたら前のめりに倒れて、大変なことになるだろう。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1172
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_98cb8fdc:

    # yu "I can't work here any more."
    yu "私、もうここで働けないわ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1174
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_5e7691d0:

    # "What a bad place for her circular train of logic to end up."
    "思考がぐるぐる回ったあげくに、よりにもよってとんでもない結論にたどり着いてしまう。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1176
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_668ef6b5:

    # hi "No, come on. That kind of stuff is what sets this place apart; there are a lot of cafés around here, you know. I think it's charming, really. Please don't quit. Business is good here, isn't it?"
    hi "いや、待ってくださいよ。この辺にはいっぱい喫茶店があるけど、そういうところがあるからこの店が際だつんですって。いけてると思いますよ、ほんとに お願いだからやめないでくださいよ。ほら、商売だって順調なんでしょ？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1181
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_e21527c2:

    # yu "Not really…"
    yu "そうでもないの……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1183
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_58a606de:

    # hi "See, I think this is a good job for you. It suits you, you shouldn't quit."
    hi "やっぱり、ここは優子さんにぴったりの職場だと思いますよ。お似合いですから、やめちゃだめです"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1185
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_407b6141:

    # "I've never had to defuse this kind of crisis before."
    "こんな危機的状況を丸く納める羽目になったのは生まれて初めてだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1189
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_ea1a84fd:

    # "Eventually, I manage to calm her down, and convince her that I'm sure Shizune just wants what she usually orders here."
    "最終的にはどうにか優子さんを落ち着かせて、静音が欲しいのは普段頼んでいる品だろうと説得することができた。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1202
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_fc0919dc:

    # "Yuuko walks away to get our drinks, and by then, Shizune has already picked a table."
    "優子さんは飲み物を用意しにその場を離れる。そのころには静音が席を選んでいた。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1206
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_00ae4000:

    # "There are no other customers, and Yuuko isn't the most talkative person, so it's very quiet."
    "他には客はいない。優子さんもおしゃべりな方ではないから、店内はとても静かだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1208
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_58b6f1e0:

    # "It doesn't really bother me, but I wish that there was some way we could communicate. There are so few moments when we're alone. Shizune and Misha are almost always together, to the point where sometimes it seems like they are one."
    "俺は気にはしないけど、静音とコミュニケーションをとる手段があればよかったな。俺たちが二人きりになれる機会はとても少ない。静音とミーシャはほとんど常に一緒にいる。時には一心同体かと思えるくらいだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1210
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_141c6a82:

    # "Now, it's just me and her, and I'm unable to understand her or have her understand me. It's terrible."
    "そして今、ここには俺と静音しかいない。そして俺は静音を理解できず、静音に俺を理解してもらうこともできない。ひどい話だ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1212
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_69e8b6f0:

    # hi "You don't have your little notepad today? I know it's the weekend and all, but it's not like you to be unprepared."
    hi "今日はあの小さいメモ帳持ってないのか？　週末だからってのはあるけどさ、そういう準備をしてないってのはお前らしくないな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1214
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_beb58c29:

    # hi "Well, that's fine. I don't really like using it anyway. Still, it would come in handy now."
    hi "まあ、いいよ。メモ帳を使うのはあまり好きじゃないし。ただこういうときは役に立っただろうな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1219
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_ef2b123c_1:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1224
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_0783f6df:

    # shi "… …"
    shi "…… ……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1226
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_f486adfc:

    # "Shizune starts signing in short bursts punctuated by her stopping to take a sip of tea. It's strange how she doesn't make the slightest attempt to change how she normally acts."
    "静音は手話をし始める。短い早口のように手を動かし、紅茶を一口飲むたびに手を休める。普段とは振る舞いを変えるという意志が全く見えないので、おかしな感じがする。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1228
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_96daa63e:

    # "I'm talking to her for the most part because I'm not used to long silences. I briefly wonder if it's the same for her, in a way; however, it seems unlikely. I think it's more that she is the type who doesn't change how she acts for anyone."
    "俺が静音に向かって話しかける理由の大部分は、自分が長い沈黙に慣れていないせいだ。ふと、ある意味それは静音にとっても同じなのだろうか、と思う。でもそれはなさそうだ。 どちらかといえば、静音は誰が相手でも振る舞い方を変えないタイプなんだろう。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1230
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_bd3b9735:

    # hi "Hey, it seems like Misha joined the Student Council because of you. That makes two of us, you know. I'm only there because you forced me into it."
    hi "なあ、ミーシャはお前がいたから生徒会に入ったみたいだな。俺も同じだよ。お前が無理矢理引っ張りこんだからだけどさ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1232
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_adcc8667:

    # hi "Well, not really forced, I guess. If it wasn't for you, I wouldn't have joined."
    hi "いやまあ、ほんとに無理矢理ってわけじゃないか。お前がいなかったら、俺も生徒会には入ってなかった"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1234
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_10e9f26a:

    # "That sounds slightly romantic, and I find myself blushing a little. I feel like such an idiot."
    "なんかロマンチックな言い方になってしまった。ほのかに頬が赤くなるのを感じる。これじゃ自分が大馬鹿みたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1236
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_834afab0:

    # hi "Although, I still don't know why you joined. It should have been the first thing I asked, in retrospect, but I'm really curious. I'll have to remember to ask Misha sometime."
    hi "でもお前が生徒会に入った理由はまだ聞いてないな。今考えてみると、最初に聞いておけばよかった話だけど、すごく興味がわいてきたよ。ミーシャに聞くって覚えておかないとな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1241
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_ef2b123c_2:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1243
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_5d7d4f9f:

    # hi "It's nice to talk to you, even if you can't understand me. I wonder if it's the same for you."
    hi "そっちが理解できないとしても、お前と話すのは楽しいなって思うんだ。お前も同じように思ってるのかな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1245
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_0f23c0ce:

    # hi "That would be really… great."
    hi "もしそうだったら……すごく、いいな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1250
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_ef2b123c_3:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1252
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_4e0174cc:

    # hi "I don't think sign language will ever be as natural for me as Misha makes it look, but it's got to be a step up from using pen and paper, right?"
    hi "ミーシャがやってるみたいに手話を自然に使えるようになるのは、俺には無理だと思うけど、でも紙とペンよりはステップアップには違いないよな？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1257
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_ef2b123c_4:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1261
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_9885a81e:

    # "We've both been finished with our drinks for a while, and Shizune's eyes fall upon the box sitting in its own chair by my side."
    "もう二人とも飲み物は飲み終えていた。静音は俺の横の椅子に乗せてある箱に目を落とす。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1266
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_ef2b123c_5:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1268
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_54517eae:

    # hi "I'm just picking it up for someone, it's not mine."
    hi "人に頼まれて受け取ってきただけだよ、俺のじゃない"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1275
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_d7b6daf5:

    # "Shizune pulls it closer to her, intending to open it, and my heart almost leaps out of my throat. I quickly try to pull it back by wrapping my leg around the leg of the chair."
    "静音が箱を開けようとして自分の方に引き寄せるので、俺は心臓が口から飛び出しそうになる。あわてて椅子を自分の足で引き寄せて、取り戻そうとする。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1277
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_4544d5e4:

    # hi "What the hell, don't open it. You can't just open other people's mail, that's not legal."
    hi "何やってるんだよ、開けちゃだめだろ。人の郵便物を勝手に開けるなよ。違法だぞ、それ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1282
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_ef2b123c_6:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1284
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_9859958a:

    # hi "No!"
    hi "だめ！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1289
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_b33ba1f7:

    # shi "…!"
    shi "……！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1291
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_271d0911:

    # "Once she gets going, there is almost no stopping her. Eyes filled with excitement, she looks ready to fight me over this stupid package and I realize just how fast this could turn into a game of tug-of-war."
    "一度こうと決めたら、静音を止めることはできない。目つきは興奮で満ちていて、このくだらない箱を巡って争う気でまんまんだ。これではあっという間に綱引きのような事態になりかねないことに思い至る。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1296
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_8cc3abc0:

    # "I am almost out of my seat now and waving my arms like an air traffic controller, before she finally settles down."
    "ほとんど席からずり落ちそうになって、航空管制官みたいに腕を振り回していると、ようやく静音は矛を収める。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1301
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_46946ec2:

    # "Shizune pouts, not pleased with having her curiosity checked, and gets up to leave."
    "好奇心を満たすことができずに不機嫌な静音は、頬を膨らませて席を立つ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1303
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_58b5c907:

    # "It's about time to, I guess. We've been here a while. I protectively pick up the box before standing up myself."
    "そろそろ戻る時間か。結構長く居たし。俺は立ち上がる前に、用心深く箱を持ち上げる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1308
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_d6cf4016:

    # "Suddenly, she tents her fingers excitedly and pulls out a marker from her pocket, and starts writing on Kenji's box."
    "突然、静音が興奮したように手を合わせると、ポケットからマーカーを取り出して健二の箱になにやら書き込む。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1310
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_effde555:

    # hi "Hey, what are you doing? I said this isn't mine!"
    hi "ちょっと、何してるんだよ！　俺のじゃないって言ってるだろ！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1312
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_d5322af5:

    # hi "Hey!"
    hi "おい！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1314
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_72f7250f:

    # "I can't even see her with it blocking my vision."
    "箱で視界がさえぎられて、静音の姿も見ることができない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1316
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_b0bc164b:

    # hi "Fine, at least let me put it down first."
    hi "わかったよ、とりあえず下におろすから"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1318
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_789e9b34:

    # "I have to to read whatever she's writing, anyway."
    "何を書いたのかは見ないといけないしな。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1325
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_9540b45b:

    # "It doesn't seem like she's finished, though, and Shizune draws a fierce line afterward to signify that there's a catch."
    "まだ書き終わっていなかったようで、静音はその後ろに荒々しく線を引いて、何か裏があることを示す。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1329
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_862b88cc:

    # hi "That's stupid, there's a fifty percent chance I'll end up carrying it myself anyway."
    hi "そんなバカな話があるかよ。それじゃあ５０％の確率で俺が一人で運ぶはめになるじゃないか"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1331
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_d3fa4e81:

    # "Actually, I feel pretty stupid myself right now. I just forgot she can't hear me. I stop talking and shake my head."
    "正直、もうすでにバカみたいな気分になっている。静音には俺の声が聞こえないのを度忘れしていた。俺はしゃべるのをやめて首を振る。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1336
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_ef2b123c_7:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1341
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_b33ba1f7_1:

    # shi "…!"
    shi "……！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1346
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_b33ba1f7_2:

    # shi "…!"
    shi "……！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1348
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_e06b7a09:

    # "I can't understand her at all, but she's coming across very forcefully. It's clear that she thinks this is a great idea."
    "静音が何を言っているのかさっぱりわからないけど、とても強い勢いで訴えかけてくる。明らかにこれがいい考えだと思っているようだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1350
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_7c0b59a2:

    # "Well, if she drops the box or something, she'll have to carry it. That would make things a lot easier for me, obviously."
    "まあ、もしこの箱だかなんだかを落としたら、静音が一人で運ぶことになる。どう考えても俺にとってはその方が楽だ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1352
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_e26ca318:

    # "The odds are 50-50, then… they're probably higher than they would be for any other plan of hers. All right, I'll take it."
    "可能性は半々、だったら……それ以外に静音が考えそうな企みに比べれば高いに違いない。いいだろう、乗ってやる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1357
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_d4c8e398:

    # "Thinking about it, I'm not sure how we should do this. Then Shizune grabs hold of one end of the box and lifts it up, and I take the side that she isn't holding. Is this even right? It's very uncomfortable to walk like this."
    "考えてみれば、これはどうやって運べばいいんだろう。すると静音は箱の片側をつかんで持ち上げる。俺は反対側を持つ。こんなのでいいんだろうか？　これじゃとても歩きづらい。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1362
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_cd16030b:

    # "We leave the café, and I find myself hoping that the streets are still devoid of people. Yuuko seemed confused as to what we were doing, and I imagine it'll only get worse as more people see us."
    "俺たちは上海を離れる。道に人がいないことを願っている自分がいる。優子さんは俺たちのやっていることを見て戸惑っていたようだし、これ以上目撃者が増えたら、事態はよけいに悪くなるだろう。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1370
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_6fab88c3:

    # "Shizune doesn't seem bothered at all while walking with her arm at this unnatural angle; she just grins confidently and periodically makes some kind of weird gesture."
    "腕を不自然な角度に曲げたまま歩いていても、静音は全く気にならないようだ。自信たっぷりの笑顔を浮かべて、時々おかしな手振りを見せる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1375
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_3c766f04:

    # "There are people staring at us as time passes, and the usual morning crowd begins to fill the streets."
    "やがて人々がこちらをじろじろ見始めるようになり、いつもの朝の通行人で道がいっぱいになる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1377
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_091821c8:

    # "I feel silly, but I'm sure that if I give up, Shizune will take it as a sign of surrender. I can't allow that, because I think I'm doing well so far."
    "間抜けな気分になってくるけど、今ギブアップしたら静音に降参の合図と受け取られるに違いない。ここまではうまくやっていると思うし、そんなことを認めるわけにはいかない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1385
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_0f98732a:

    # "Initially, I just write Shizune's little hand signals off as her preemptively gloating, but I catch on quickly that she's actually signaling where she wants to go."
    "最初は、静音の手振りは単に勝負がつく前から勝ち誇っているだけだと思っていた。でもすぐに、静音は自分の行きたい方向を知らせているのだと気づく。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1387
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_24c8fb07:

    # "It dawns on me that this isn't a competition. It's not much of a challenge, first of all, and second, it's really more of an exercise in teamwork. It's just that Shizune has made a punishment for failing instead of a reward for doing well."
    "これは競争なんかじゃない、ということに徐々に思いいたる。 そもそも大して難しい話じゃないし、それにこれはどちらかといえば共同作業だ。ただ、静音は成功したらご褒美を出すかわりに、失敗したら罰を与えることにしたというだけだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1394
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_401329c5:

    # "Our fingers touch under the box, and Shizune moves her hand away, almost dropping her side of the box in the process."
    "箱の底でお互いの指が触れ合って、静音は手を遠ざける。そのおかげで静音は箱を落としそうになる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1396
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_bf15c76a:

    # "Well, that's game over for her."
    "まあ、これで静音はゲームオーバーだな。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1398
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_7f479ed4:

    # "She doesn't look very happy. Does she think I did it on purpose to make her lose? If she does, she isn't making a big deal out of it. All's fair in love and war."
    "静音は不機嫌そうな感じだ。俺が静音を負けさせるためにわざとやったと思っているんだろうか？　そうだとしても、大して気にしてはいないようだ。『恋と戦争は手段を選ばず』ってな。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1403
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_870e1436:

    # "I feel like I should take it from her and carry it myself, but she pushes me away when I try."
    "箱を引き取って俺が運ばないといけない気がする。でもそうしようとすると、静音に押し戻される。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1407
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_21bf6da5:

    # "She glares at me as if to tell me off, but she can't. With that box in her hands, she is basically gagged."
    "俺に説教するかのように静音がにらみつけてくるけど、実際にはできない。両手で箱を持っているので、口をふさがれているようなものだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1415
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_5190e505:

    # "A sad expression flickers across her face for a second, maybe on realizing that and having to acknowledge that there are some limitations she has to deal with after all."
    "悲しげな表情がちらりと静音の顔に浮かぶ。たぶん、そのことに気づいたのと、自分はこうした制約を受け入れなくてはいけない、ということを自覚させられたからか。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1417
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_d55b0d48:

    # "However, she is still as prideful as ever, even when it's to her detriment. She wouldn't accept letting me allow her to skip out on the consequences of her bet."
    "それでも、静音はこれ以上ないくらい誇りに満ちている。そのおかげで自分が損を被る状況だというのに。賭けに負けたのを俺が見逃すことを静音は認めない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1419
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_c20eec2e:

    # "Anything is fair during the game, but the results have to be honored to the letter, huh?"
    "勝負にあっては禁じ手なし、ただし結果は文字通りに受け入れるべし、か？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1421
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_4e5231c4:

    # "Shizune is an interesting type of person."
    "静音は面白いタイプの人物だな。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1426
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_3e181de6:

    # "The march back to the dorms is uneventful. Shizune passes the trip by shifting the box around occasionally like a giant Rubik's cube. It looks like another game she has invented to amuse herself."
    "寮までの行進は何事もなく終わる。道中、静音は巨大なルービックキューブのように時折箱をくるくると回して時を過ごす。また暇つぶしに思いついた遊びのようだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1428
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_f0dfa9ce:

    # "It can't be good for whatever's inside, but I don't care enough to stop her."
    "中身にはいいとは思えないけど、俺もどうでもいいと思ったので放っておく。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1430
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_a8886688:

    # "Maybe this is how she deals with things, by making everything into a game; it's hard to say for sure, though."
    "これが静音なりの物事のこなし方なのかもしれない。何もかも勝負事にしてしまう。確信は持てないけど。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1432
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_75aba597:

    # "It seems futile to try to psychoanalyze Shizune. In the short time we've known each other, I've been surprised on a fair number of occasions."
    "静音を精神分析しようとするのは無駄な努力みたいだ。知り合ってからの短い間、俺は何度も驚かされている。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1439
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_2980203a:

    # "I notice Shizune shivering. The wind is picking up, and the school is pretty high up. It makes sense that she would be cold. If I gave her my jacket, though, would she reject it?"
    "静音がふるえているのに気づく。風が強くなっているし、学校も結構高いところにある。寒がっているのもうなずける。でも俺の上着を渡したら、静音は拒否するだろうか？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1446
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_d9f448fb:

    # "I take off my jacket and drape it across her shoulders before she has a chance to protest. Her shoulders are slim and delicate, so much so that I want to let my hands linger on them."
    "俺は上着を脱いで、文句を言われる前に静音の肩にかける。その肩はあまりに細くて華奢で、ずっと手で触れていたくなるほどだった。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1451
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_ee0d0788:

    # "Shizune flinches when my fingers brush against her, understandably surprised."
    "俺の指が触れたとき、静音は驚いたようにびくりとする。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1453
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_eab1722c:

    # hi "Sorry."
    hi "ごめん"

