    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1465
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_c9a02be6:

    # "Her fingers dance lightly over the surface of the box, and I think of taking it from her, but I doubt she would let me. Shizune makes a quick gesture with her hands as best she can, pausing a bit afterward as if wanting to say more."
    "静音の指が箱の上で軽やかに動く。箱を引き取るべきかと思ったけど、そうはさせてくれないだろう。静音はかろうじて素早い手振りを見せる。その後で手を止めたのは、もっと言いたいことがあったからだろうか。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1467
translate jp a2_shizune_chinese_whispers_5e268974:

    # "I'm sure that what she means is 'thank you.' I'm glad that I was able to catch it."
    "今のは間違いなく『ありがとう』だ。ちゃんと読みとれてよかった。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1481
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1488
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_d2997a3f:

    # n "{vspace=60}The sign language teacher says I'm pretty good."
    n "\n\n手話の先生によくやっているとほめられた。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1490
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_4733eb15:

    # n "I try not to think about it too much, but the truth is I'm poring over it so much lately that it's hard not to keep coming back to it at least a couple times a day. I guess I am picking it up faster than expected, but it's still not enough."
    n "あまり考えすぎないよう努力はしているけど、実はここ最近手話のことで頭がいっぱいで、１日に何度もそのことを考えずにはいられないくらいだ。思ったよりも早く身につき始めているんだろうけど、でもまだまだだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1492
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_dad9890e:

    # n "I understand it just fine; understanding it is simple. Well, I have to put my mind to it to read it, but it's easy enough when I do."
    n "手話を読みとるのは問題ない。それだけなら簡単だ。まあ、読むときは集中しないといけないけど、集中さえしていれば十分簡単にできる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1494
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_3e3bbd49:

    # n "The signing itself is doable, I just need a little more practice. However, trying to do both at the same time, even at half the speed Misha does it? It's impossible."
    n "自分で手話をするのも何とかなる。もっと練習が必要なだけだ。でも両方を同時にやるとなったら？　ミーシャの半分の速さでも不可能だ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1496
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_5d0b9f8f:

    # n "Where I'm at now is good for my level, but in order to reach a point where I'll be able to really converse with Shizune, I'll need more work."
    n "俺のレベルからすれば、今の状態は上出来といえる。でも静音と本当に会話できるところまでたどり着くには、もっと努力しないといけない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1498
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_01a2001e:

    # n "{vspace=30}I'm doing my best to get to that point one step at a time by doing as much studying as I can squeeze in during lunch."
    n "\n１歩ずつ着実にそこにたどり着くために、俺は全力を尽くしている。昼休みにできる限りのことを詰め込んでいるんだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1502
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1506
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_378acdd4:

    # "I look up from 'Introduction to Japanese Sign Language' to check if Shizune or Misha are around."
    "『手話入門』の教科書から顔を上げて、静音やミーシャがまわりにいないか確かめる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1508
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_587bd54a:

    # "Of course, since this is taking up my lunch hour, I've had to avoid them for a few days now. What's more, I'll have to continue doing so if I want to keep Shizune from finding out."
    "もちろん、昼休みの時間を勉強につぎ込んでいるので、この数日間あの２人を避け続けるはめになっている。しかも、静音に知られないようにするなら、ずっとこんなことを続けないといけない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1510
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_5c1327e2:

    # "My back to the corner, scanning the area every ten minutes, I feel like some kind of criminal trying to evade capture."
    "背中を角に向けて、１０分おきに辺りを見回していると、追っ手から逃げようとしている犯罪者のような気がしてくる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1512
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1518
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_44a7ce24:

    # nvl clear
    # n "{vspace=60}Every chance she gets, Misha asks me why I want to hide the fact I'm learning sign language from Shizune."
    nvl clear
    n "\n\nミーシャは俺の顔を見るたびに、手話を勉強していることを静音に隠す理由を聞いてくる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1522
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_b6b7e84c:

    # n "Looking back on it, there really wasn't any reason, but now I think I know."
    n "思い返してみると、あのときはこれといった理由なんてなかった。でも今はわかる気がする。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1524
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_b0750deb:

    # n "If I want Shizune to be able to treat me as a true equal, sign language is an important step towards that goal."
    n "静音が俺のことを本当に対等な存在として見てくれるためには、手話を身につけるのは大事なステップだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1526
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_eab4dacf:

    # n "If I want to be able to treat Shizune as an equal, then sign language is an important step towards that goal."
    n "俺が静音と対等な相手として付き合いたいなら、手話を身につけるのはそのための大事なステップだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1528
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_5356577e:

    # n "Another important step is to make sure she doesn't know, so that when we're able to finally speak on equal terms, I'll be fully ready, able to do it right, not like some dilettante."
    n "もう１つ大事なステップは、静音に知られてはいけないということだ。最終的に対等な立場で話し合えるようになったときに、俺自身がきちんと準備ができていて、正しく話せるようにしたい。遊びじゃだめなんだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1530
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_7337ca16:

    # n "Anything less, I think, would be insulting. She would see it the same way."
    n "そうでなければ失礼だ、と思う。静音もそう考えるだろう。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1532
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_5626da4c:

    # n "{vspace=30}So to me, this is the only option. Especially now that I've decided to be so resolute with it."
    n "\nだから俺にとっては、これ以外に選択肢はない。自分でこんなに強く決意したのだから、なおさらだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1536
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_76b2fe88_2:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1540
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_930e27c8:

    # "Shizune has a huge aura. It's very easy to see her coming, or even to sense her coming. Mostly because Misha's hair lights up any crowd she's in like a beacon, and you can hear her laughing from a mile away."
    "静音は巨大なオーラをまとっている。目に付くのはもちろん、やってくるのが感覚でわかる。主にミーシャの髪が周りの人混みを灯台みたいに明るく照らすからだけど。それにあの笑い声は１キロ先からでも聞こえるし。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1542
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_4bd878cf:

    # "Although, even if Misha weren't with her, it would be the same. Her directness and efficiency are core parts of her, so it's no surprise that they come across in the way she walks as well."
    "でも、ミーシャが一緒でなくても同じことだ。率直さと勤勉さは静音の核心なのだから、あいつが歩くにつれてそれが伝わってくるのは驚くことじゃない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1544
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_60953e84:

    # "Due to all these factors, I'm able to put away all my things and put on my best casual face long before they see me and head my way."
    "こうした諸々の事情のおかげで、２人がこちらを認めて近づいてくるまでの間に、俺は余裕を持って自分の荷物をまとめて、いかにも普段と同じような表情を作ることができた。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1550
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_ca61152d:

    # hi "Hi."
    hi "やあ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1555
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_3d2bf224:

    # ssh "Student Councilll."
    ssh "生徒会～"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1560
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_bdebd484:

    # mi "Student Council~!"
    mi "せいとかい～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1562
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_9d93062f:

    # "'Student Council' was the first thing I asked to learn; it seemed like it would come in handy."
    "役に立ちそうだと思ったから、『生徒会』は真っ先にやり方を習っていた。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1564
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_f74b566b:

    # hi "Yeah, I've been dodging it for a while now, huh?"
    hi "ああ、しばらくそっちからは逃げ回ってたよなあ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1570
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_f7267e24:

    # mi "Yup~!"
    mi "そうだよ～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1584
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_439519ba:

    # "Shizune sits down in front of me to my right, and Misha to my left. It was a mistake putting myself in the corner; now I'm, well, cornered."
    "静音が俺の正面右手に座り、ミーシャは左に座る。部屋の隅に座るのは間違いだった。今の俺はまさに『袋のネズミ』だ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1589
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_1af80203:

    # "In the end, I'm dragged off to the student council room, but I don't mind. I was starting to miss them a bit, anyway."
    "結局、俺は生徒会室に引きずられていく。でも構わない。そろそろこの２人に会いたくなり始めていたところだし。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1591
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_d5d9845e:

    # "In some ways this makes it easier: satisfied with having caught me, Shizune doesn't ask me where I've been all this time."
    "ある意味、このおかげで話が楽になったともいえる。俺を捕まえたことに満足して、静音は俺が今までどこにいたのかを聞いてこない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1593
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_499f3308:

    # "Once I stand before the door, I wonder what could be so important that they're so eager to pull me back in."
    "ドアの前に立ってみて、そこまで熱心に俺を引っ張り戻そうとするほどの大事な事情とはなんだろうと考える。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1598
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_b6cc39b9:

    # hi "Games."
    hi "ゲームか"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1602
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_6bcef903:

    # "There are more games out than books. This at last explains why every time I come here there are stacks of books piled on every table and occasionally parts of the floor: they need the room to put all these games somewhere."
    "部屋の中のゲームの数は本よりも多い。俺が来るたびに、すべての机と、時には床の上にまで本が積んであった理由がやっとわかった。これだけのゲームをしまう場所が必要だったんだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1607
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_66b999fb:

    # mi "Hahaha~!"
    mi "ははは～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1612
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_eb1473e5:

    # mi "It's boring playing against each other so much, Hicchan. So, it's your turn, okay? Okay~! It's settled then~!"
    mi "２人きりで遊び続けるのってつまんないんだよ、ひっちゃん。だから今度はひっちゃんの番だよ、いい？　おっけ～！　じゃあ決まりだね～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1614
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_a63f7e85:

    # hi "I didn't even say anything!"
    hi "俺まだ一言もしゃべってないぞ！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1630
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_ef2b123c:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1635
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_cbdf09f8:

    # mi "Hicchan, this is one of the last days we'll be able to take it easy like this for a while. So~, it's especially important that we make the most of it, don't you think?"
    mi "ひっちゃん、もう少ししたら、今みたいにゆっくりできる日はしばらくお預けになっちゃうの。だから～、今のうちに楽しんでおくのがとっても大事ってわけ。そう思わない？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1640
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_fe171261:

    # mi "Tanabata will be coming up soon, and we'll have to put in a lot of work for that, too."
    mi "もうすぐ七夕だから、わたしたちもいっぱい仕事しないといけないの"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1646
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_7fe2e51e:

    # mi "So, for now, play with us~!"
    mi "だから、今はいっしょに遊ぼ～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1648
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_e131e3ea:

    # "Come to think of it, it's true. I hadn't even noticed because I've been so wrapped up in wanting to learn sign language. Right on the heels of one festival, a bigger one appears."
    "考えてみれば、その通りだ。手話を学ぶことに夢中になりすぎて、全く気がついていなかった。お祭りが１つ過ぎたとたんに、もっと大きな祭りがやってくる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1650
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_ec8f46de:

    # "I wonder if Shizune will try and rope a couple new members in to help with that one as well."
    "その手伝いに、静音はもう何人か新メンバーを捕まえようとするだろうか。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1652
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_b13b2718:

    # hi "You're right."
    hi "そうだな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1657
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_c519e28d:

    # mi "Hahaha~! Yay~! Hicchan agrees~! Let's celebrate!"
    mi "ははは～！　やったあ～！　ひっちゃんもそう思うって～！　お祝いしよう！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1662
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_66f8512e:

    # ssh "I know, we should play a game."
    ssh "そうだわ、ゲームをしましょう"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1667
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_5eb4028f:

    # mi "Let's play a game to celebrate, Hicchan~!"
    mi "お祝いにゲームしようよ、ひっちゃん～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1669
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_e7f7460d:

    # hi "I don't know, that kind of thing usually ends badly for me."
    hi "どうだろうなあ、そういうのって結局俺が痛い目を見て終わることが多いし"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1674
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_199cd058:

    # mi "Hicchan is worried about the stakes~."
    mi "ひっちゃんは賭けるものが心配なんだ～"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1676
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_7ce4ee2a:

    # "Misha makes a very disappointed face. It's hard to tell if she's mocking me, since her expressions are so exaggerated by default. She's an 'all-out' kind of girl."
    "ミーシャがとても残念そうな顔をする。いつでもすごく大げさな表情をするので、からかっているのか、それとも本気なのかを見極めるのが難しい。ミーシャはどんなときでも全力を出す子だからな。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1678
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_2c5a7ec0:

    # "I turn my head to Shizune. Now, this person, she is definitely mocking me."
    "静音に顔を向ける。さてと、こいつは間違いなく俺をバカにしているな。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1680
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_3020e2d7:

    # hi "Hey, stop that. But, yes, I'll play with you if you tell me what's at stake first."
    hi "おいやめろよ。でもそうだな、先に何を賭けるつもりなのか教えてくれたら、ゲームしてもいいよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1685
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_ef2b123c_1:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1690
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_16d5803a:

    # mi "How very Japanese, putting the consequences above everything else."
    mi "すごく日本人的ね、何よりも結果のことを重視するって"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1695
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_7a1d9f19:

    # mi "Hicchan, have you ever heard of the expression 'missing the forest for the trees?'"
    mi "ひっちゃん、『木を見て森を見ず』って言葉、聞いたことある？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1697
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_7efcef0d:

    # hi "No."
    hi "ないよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1699
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_47e3f9fb:

    # "That's a lie. But I have my pride, which is currently feeling wounded."
    "今のは嘘だ。でも俺にもプライドがある。今のところ傷つけられているけど。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1701
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_079974d7:

    # hi "Okay, I'll play, but I want to pick the game."
    hi "わかったよ、つきあってやる。でもゲームは俺に選ばせてくれ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1707
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_36afeb57:

    # "Misha nods."
    "ミーシャはうなずく。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1709
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_6fd7bb3c:

    # hi "Additionally, I pick the punishment if you lose."
    hi "それと、そっちが負けたら俺が罰ゲームを決めるからな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1714
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_113eaa9b:

    # "Shizune makes an X with her arms. That either means 'denied' or that she's about to use her special attack."
    "静音は腕で×印を作る。それは『拒否』の意味なのか、何か必殺技を出そうとしているのか。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1716
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_3663f0fd:

    # hi "Aha, now who's afraid of consequences?"
    hi "おっと、負けるのを怖がってるのはどっちだ？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1721
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_93b9175a:

    # ssh "How vengeful, still thinking so spitefully about a playful little joke."
    ssh "ほんとに執念深いのね、ほんの軽い冗談なのに、いつまでも根に持つなんて"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1726
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_68d3b0ea:

    # ssh "If a … bit you, you would probably bite back."
    ssh "もしあなたが……に噛まれたら、きっと噛み返すんでしょうね"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1728
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_1aff0c5c:

    # "Shizune signs a word that I don't quite catch."
    "今の静音の手話に、１つ読みとれない単語があった。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1733
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_687e57d8:

    # mi "Hicchan is so vengeful~, even though it was just a playful little joke. If an armadillo bit you, you would probably bite back!"
    mi "ひっちゃんはほんとに根に持つよね～、ちょっとした冗談だったのに。たぶん、アルマジロに噛まれてもひっちゃんは噛みつき返すんだろうね！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1735
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_d324d9c4:

    # hi "Armadillo?"
    hi "アルマジロ？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1740
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_8c35516d:

    # mi "It's foolish to bite an armadillo back, Hicchan!"
    mi "アルマジロに噛みつき返すなんて、おバカさんだよ、ひっちゃん！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1745
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_ef2b123c_2:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1750
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_6483aa78:

    # mi "But Hicchan would do it anyway, you see~! Hahaha!"
    mi "でもどうせひっちゃんはやり返しちゃうんだよね～！　ははは！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1752
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_e1f8a5e6:

    # hi "I see."
    hi "なるほどな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1757
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_abb82823:

    # "Shizune adjusts her glasses with a small flourish of her hand."
    "静音は小さな手振りとともに眼鏡を直す。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1762
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_ef2b123c_3:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1767
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_3139c78c:

    # mi "Hicchan, we didn't have anything planned at all if you were to win or lose, you just assumed there would be something like that~."
    mi "ひっちゃん、勝ち負けの結果で何かしたりさせたりとか、そんなことは全然考えてないってば。そういうことがあるだろうって、ひっちゃんが思い込んでただけだよ～"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1769
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_36d04ce4:

    # hi "I wonder why."
    hi "そりゃどうしてだろうなあ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1774
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_9cc320eb:

    # mi "Hm~, me too~! But, oh well~! There isn't. Does that change your mind, Hicchan?"
    mi "んん～、どうしてだろうね～！　でもまあいいか～！　そういうのはありませんから。これで気が変わったかな、ひっちゃん？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1776
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_57ecc993:

    # hi "Well… yes."
    hi "まあ……そうだな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1781
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_dc77c9b5:

    # "Misha windmills her arm at high speed to show her joy. Weird habit. This is the kind of thing you could only see in the student council room, occupied only by three people."
    "ミーシャは嬉しさで腕を風車のようにぐるぐる振り回す。おかしな癖だ。たった３人しかいない生徒会室の中でしか、こんな光景を見ることはできないだろう。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1783
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_c52294dd:

    # "Anywhere else she would end up socking someone in the face."
    "ここ以外の場所だったら、人の顔を殴り付けてしまうに違いない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1788
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_6729b82b:

    # mi "Yay yay~! Let's start right now~!"
    mi "やったやったぁ～！　じゃあ今すぐ始めよ～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:1790
translate jp a2_shizune_advanced_game_theory_dd2b3381:

    # hi "Not just yet."
    hi "まあちょっと待て"

