    # "Sure is a lot of work, though. I had to skip out on sign language class again, but now I'm at a level where I can understand most of Shizune and Misha's conversations with each other, so I'm not too bothered by it."
    "それにしてもすごい量の仕事だ。また手話のクラスをさぼる羽目になってしまったけど、もう静音とミーシャの会話をほとんど理解できるレベルにはなっているので、それほど気にはならない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2494
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_4e6dd9d0:

    # "Shizune still doesn't know that, though. I'm determined to keep things that way until I'm very sure of my skills. Perhaps it's a little childish of me."
    "ただ、静音はまだそのことに気づいていない。俺は自分の手話に間違いなく自信が持てるレベルになるまで、このままで通す覚悟を決めている。ちょっと子供じみた考えかもしれない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2499
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_b1e7a766:

    # ssh "Tanabata is in less than five days, but they're only going to start building the stalls tomorrow."
    ssh "あと五日もしないうちに七夕だけど、屋台の組み立ては明日にならないと始めないんだって"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2504
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_d0f50fdf:

    # mi "Hicchan, we might have to help out with building stalls again starting tomorrow."
    mi "ひっちゃん、明日からまた屋台の組み立てを手伝わないといけないかも"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2506
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_9951ef3e:

    # hi "Why? What was the point of taking them apart then? That took days, didn't it?"
    hi "どうしてさ？　だったらそもそも何のために屋台をばらしたんだよ？　何日もかかったんだろ？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2511
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_390f1153:

    # mi "Yup! That's right~! Even though Hicchan wasn't there for it~."
    mi "うん！　そうだよ～！　ひっちゃんはそのときいなかったけど～"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2513
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_86bdb112:

    # hi "I would have helped out if you asked."
    hi "言ってくれれば手伝ったのに"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2518
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_05b4d0da:

    # ssh "It wouldn't have made sense to bore you with cleanup duty after you enjoyed the festival so much."
    ssh "あれだけ学園祭を楽しんだのに、後片づけで退屈させたんじゃ意味がないでしょ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2523
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_1cf0b984:

    # mi "It wouldn't have made sense to bore you with making you clean up right after the festival, it would have ruined the fun."
    mi "学園祭のすぐ後に片づけをさせて退屈させるなんて意味がないでしょ。そしたら楽しい気分が台なしだよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2528
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_43558f05:

    # ssh "Besides…"
    ssh "それに……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2533
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_899b8809:

    # mi "Ahahaha~! Hicchan is lazy anyway, you would have tried to run away again~! Shicchan doesn't like playing foxhound."
    mi "あははは～！　ひっちゃんはどうせ怠け者だから、逃げようとしたに決まってるって～！　しっちゃんは追いかけっこをするのは嫌いだって"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2535
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_464ce438:

    # hi "That stings."
    hi "きついこと言うな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2540
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_be30204d:

    # "Shizune covers her mouth with her hand and starts shaking. It takes me a second to realize she's laughing, mostly because she's doing so completely soundlessly."
    "静音は手で口を覆って、体を震わせ始める。全く音を立てないせいもあって、笑っているのだと気づくのが一瞬遅れる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2542
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_680ffe05:

    # "It's a little strange to see, but more or less the same good-spirited kind as Misha's, without being eardrum-piercing."
    "そんな姿を見るのは少し妙だけど、笑いそのものは鼓膜をつんざく大声はないにしても、ミーシャのように朗らかなものだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2548
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_c70e5885:

    # mi "Hm~, that's a good question, though, Hicchan."
    mi "んん～、でもそれっていい質問だよ、ひっちゃん"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2550
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_0f638bea:

    # hi "Huh?"
    hi "えっ？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2555
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_8eecd1db:

    # mi "Stalls~!"
    mi "屋台のこと～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2560
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_beb31cc4:

    # ssh "It's a storage issue. The school doesn't have anywhere to store so many stalls, since each one is pretty large. They won't pay for outside storage either, so this is what they decided on. It's inefficient, but cheaper."
    ssh "保管場所の問題よ。屋台は一つ一つがかなり大きいから、あんなにたくさんの屋台を保管する場所なんて校内にない。外部の倉庫を使うお金を出すわけでもないから、そう決めたの。非効率だけどお金はかからない"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2565
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_978fd99d:

    # mi "Because~! the school doesn't have anywhere to store that many stalls, Hicchan."
    mi "つまり～！　学校の中にはそんなにたくさん屋台を置く場所がないんだよ、ひっちゃん"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2570
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_ef2b123c:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2575
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_8ccfeb0c:

    # mi "Ah, yeah yeah~, right, they do, but they don't want to pay~! Sorry, Shicchan~…"
    mi "あー、そうだねそうだね、うん、あるけど、でもお金出したくないんだよね～！　ごめんね、しっちゃん～……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2580
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_a53cb711:

    # ssh "It's because of the previous generation."
    ssh "これも前の代のせいなの"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2585
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_160a6f0d:

    # ssh "The leadership decided that outside storage costs had risen too much, and the Student Council before us was too weak-willed to tell them that it's stupid to have to build and disassemble sixty stalls twice every year."
    ssh "学校側は外部の倉庫を使うコストが上がりすぎていると判断したの。前の代の生徒会は弱腰過ぎて、毎年２回も６０個の屋台を組み立てて取り壊すのはばかばかしいって主張することができなかった"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2590
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_b33ba1f7:

    # shi "…!"
    shi "……！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2595
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_59a6539f:

    # mi "Okay~!!"
    mi "おっけ～！！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2600
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_ef2b123c_1:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2605
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_ced3b3bf:

    # mi "Hicchan, let's eat something~! It feels like we've been working all day~…"
    mi "ひっちゃん、何か食べようよ～！　もう丸一日働いたみたいな気分だよ～……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2607
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_85a66417:

    # hi "We have. Now that I think about it, I am hungry. I would have had lunch, but it was really crowded today for some reason, so I decided it wasn't worth the trouble."
    hi "実際働いてるよ。言われてみれば腹へったな。昼を食べるつもりだったけど、どういうわけか食堂がものすごく混んでたから、面倒くさくなったんだ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2612
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_f0e12e0f:

    # mi "Ahahaha~! It was like that today because they had some especially interesting things for sale on the side."
    mi "あははは～！　今日はサイドメニューにすごく特別な品があったから混んでたんだよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2614
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_ae6a84c5:

    # hi "Like what? No, don't tell me. I guess it doesn't matter, since I won't be able to eat them anyway."
    hi "どんなだよ？　いや、言わなくていい。どうせ俺には食べられないから関係ないし"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2620
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_044594ff:

    # "Shizune looks oddly pleased with herself. I wonder what the context of that could be."
    "静音は妙に満足げだ。今度はどういう裏があるんだか。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2625
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_f418375a:

    # ssh "I prepared ahead of time for this."
    ssh "このときのためにあらかじめ準備してたの"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2627
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_372c51d9:

    # "Beaming with self-satisfaction, she produces a wide assortment of food from her bag. I can immediately see that ninety percent of it or more was taken from the lunch room."
    "自己満足の笑顔を浮かべながら、かばんからあらゆる種類の食べ物を取り出す。その９割以上は食堂から持ってきたものだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2631
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_41123764:

    # "There's a lot, as well. Isn't there a limit on how much a person can buy?"
    "しかもすごい量だ。一人が買える数には制限があったんじゃないのか？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2633
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_e1e685f3:

    # "That means these gains are definitely ill-gotten."
    "つまりこの獲物は不正に入手されたに違いない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2635
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_4b488ba6:

    # hi "The veal cutlet bread is always sold out in the first minute of lunch. I'm impressed you managed to obtain one."
    hi "子牛のカツレツサンドは昼休みになったとたんに真っ先に売り切れるんだぞ。それを買えたなんて感心したよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2637
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_85879fae:

    # hi "Thank you."
    hi "ありがと"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2643
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_3d21299d:

    # "I reach for it quickly, but Shizune immediately makes a grab for it as well."
    "すばやく手を伸ばすけど、静音もすぐにそれを奪い取ろうとする。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2650
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_1c2b856d:

    # "Her hand goes slack for a second when it touches mine, but she immediately pushes forth with redoubled effort, that blazing, competitive spirit flashing dangerously in her eyes. Her fingers pry at mine, searching for an opening."
    "お互いの手が触れあって、一瞬だけ静音が手をゆるめるけど、すぐに二倍の力で押し込んでくる。 あの燃えるような競争心が瞳の中で危険なまでに閃いている。静音の指が俺の手をまさぐり、隙間を見つけてこじ開けようとする。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2652
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_57e99384:

    # "I don't budge an inch, prepared to fight for this bread with my life. I might never have another chance to eat this."
    "俺も一ミリたりとも動かない。このパンのためなら命だってかけてやる。このチャンスを逃したら二度と食べられないかもしれないんだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2654
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_05aa7f78:

    # "I am fully aware that if we continue like this, we could crush the bread, greatly reducing its edibility."
    "でもこんなことを続けていたら、パンを握りつぶしてしまって全然食べられなくなる、という可能性も重々承知している。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2656
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_f5227759:

    # hi "Misha… Tell her that unless she lets go, the bread is going to be crushed."
    hi "ミーシャ……手を離さないとパンがつぶれるぞって静音に伝えてくれよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2661
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_dfc1120c:

    # mi "Hmmmmm? Why can't you do it yourself?"
    mi "ふーーーーーん？　どうして自分で言わないの？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2663
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_acceeada:

    # "I'm startled she can so nonchalantly let slip that I could communicate with Shizune just fine if I wanted to. I almost consider the possibility it was intentional, but I'm sure she was just distracted trying to tear the wrapper off a juice box straw."
    "やろうと思えば静音とは普通に会話できるということをいとも気軽にばらされて、俺は肝を冷やす。わざとじゃないかと疑いそうになるけど、きっとジュースのストローを紙パックからはがすのに夢中だっただけだろう。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2665
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_45824435:

    # hi "Isn't it obvious? I can't let go of the bread."
    hi "別におかしくないだろ？　パンを離したくないんだよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2670
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_6da8a35f:

    # mi "I can't tell Shicchan that, then."
    mi "じゃあわたしからはしっちゃんには言えないな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2675
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_73eeacfc:

    # "She puts her palms up to the sky and shrugs, a wide grin on her face."
    "ミーシャは手のひらを上に向けて肩をすくめ、満面に笑みを浮かべる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2677
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_f5743db9:

    # hi "Why not?"
    hi "どうして？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2682
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_1d4e08c1:

    # mi "Because~! You have a stake in this, so I can't trust you~! If Shicchan wants to reply, she has to let go of the bread, and then you win. Who knows, who knows, maybe that's what you want, Hicchan?"
    mi "だって～！　ひっちゃんはそのパンを取り合ってるんだから、信用できないの～！ しっちゃんが返事しようとしたら、パンから手を離さなきゃいけなくて、そしたらひっちゃんの勝ちでしょ。どうだかどうだか、それが狙いなんじゃないの、ひっちゃん？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2687
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_f3f1109d:

    # mi "It wouldn't be fair, so I'm going to be neutral! Like Switzerland~!"
    mi "それじゃ不公平だもん、だからわたしは中立になるの！　スイスみたいにね～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2689
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_978c7176:

    # hi "Switzerland?"
    hi "スイス？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2694
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_2b801648:

    # mi "Do you know about Switzerland?"
    mi "スイスのこと知ってる？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2696
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_631048a9:

    # hi "Of course I do… it's neutral, they're neutral."
    hi "そりゃ知ってるよ……中立なんだろ、国も人も"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2701
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_e07fbc00:

    # "Shizune stares at me cockily, the tip of her tongue sticking out slightly from between her teeth as she continues to tug firmly at the veal cutlet bread between us."
    "静音が生意気そうに俺をじろじろ見る。舌の先をちょっとだけ歯の間から出しながら、しっかりと子牛のカツレツサンドを引っ張り続けている。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2706
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_185cd4a6:

    # "Suddenly, she lets go and holds her hands up, palms facing outwards. The universal gesture of peace."
    "突然、静音はパンを手放して両手を上に上げる。手のひらは上向き。世界共通の和平の身振りだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2711
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_0a861894:

    # ssh "This seems like a poor way to settle this, doesn't it? And we might crush the bread."
    ssh "こんなのはお粗末な決着の付け方だと思わない？　それにパンをつぶしてしまうかもしれないし"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2716
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_81697594:

    # "She glares, and her passive expression quickly plummets into a disapproving grimace."
    "こちらをにらみつけてくる。おとなしい表情は瞬時に責めるようなしかめ面に変わる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2721
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_b33ba1f7_1:

    # shi "…!"
    shi "……！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2726
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_db3e4a23:

    # mi "Hicchan! Drop the bread! We are negotiating now!"
    mi "ひっちゃん！　パンを離しなさい！　今は交渉中なんだから！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2728
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_18e32b3e:

    # "I drop the bread reluctantly."
    "俺は渋々パンを手放す。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2734
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_f84f6022:

    # "Misha's hand darts in from the side, her fingers drumming across the table as it makes its way over."
    "横からミーシャの手が飛び出す。指でテーブルをばたばたと叩きながらこっちまで手を伸ばしてくる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2739
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_66a94aec:

    # mi "Ah~! Haha~! Don't mind me, I don't even really like veal. I'll just take this sandwich right here~! And something to drink, too…"
    mi "あ～！　はは～！　わたしのことは気にしないで、そもそも子牛の肉なんて好きじゃないし。わたしはこっちのサンドイッチをもらうね～！　それと飲み物も……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2744
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_9f14e18b:

    # "Picking them up cautiously, she immediately retreats."
    "注意深く飲み物を拾い上げると、ミーシャはすぐに身を引く。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2746
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_de3549f7:

    # "She has the right idea. I could just pick something else, there are lots of delicious things here. The chicken katsudon bread is also a popular seller, ranking high in taste and demand. But I've already eaten one before."
    "ミーシャの考えも間違っていない。他のものを選んだっていいんだ。いっぱいおいしそうな食べ物があるんだから。チキンカツ丼パンもおいしくて人気のある、よく売れている品だ。でもこれはもう食べたことがある。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2751
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_95347d5e:

    # ssh "You're so immature, Hisao. This wouldn't be a problem if you would pick something else. The chicken katsudon bread is delicious."
    ssh "あなたって本当に幼稚ね、久夫。あなたが他のものを選べば何の問題もないのに。チキンカツ丼パンだってすごくおいしいのよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2756
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_f10d1ff2:

    # mi "You're so immature, Hicchan. Why don't you pick the chicken katsudon bread instead? It's delicious~!"
    mi "ほんとに幼稚だね、ひっちゃん。代わりにチキンカツ丼パンにしたら？すごくおいしいよ～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2758
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_d423a707:

    # hi "But I have already eaten that."
    hi "でももう食べたことがあるんだよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2763
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_ef2b123c_2:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2768
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_25a8a728:

    # mi "Hicchan~! Why are you so obsessed with eating the veal cutlet bread, spe—ci—fi—cal—ly?"
    mi "ひっちゃん～！　どうしてその子牛カツレツパンに、と・く・べ・つ・に、こだわるの？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2770
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_460d3b46:

    # hi "It's hard to get normally. Rare things are more delicious."
    hi "普通は手に入らないからだよ。珍しいものはもっとおいしいんだ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2775
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_29548e4d:

    # ssh "You are acting like a child."
    ssh "子供みたいね"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2780
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_935ced37:

    # mi "You're acting like a kid, Hicchan."
    mi "子供みたいだよ、ひっちゃん"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2782
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_30a607ee:

    # hi "Why don't you eat the chicken bread?"
    hi "お前はどうしてチキンカツ丼パン食べないんだよ？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2787
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_34af7df6:

    # ssh "That's not important."
    ssh "そんなことは重要じゃないの"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2789
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_807d343a:

    # "Turning bright red, she smiles cunningly and continues."
    "真っ赤になりながら、静音は狡猾そうな笑みを浮かべて話を続ける。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2797
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_2559e9cc:

    # ssh "There is no reasoning with you. So it looks like there is only one way to settle this: we are going to play for it."
    ssh "あなたとは話しても無駄ね。もうけりを付ける方法は一つしかない。勝負しましょう"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2802
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_3c40f586:

    # mi "That doesn't matter: we'll play for it instead~!"
    mi "そんなの関係ないよ。かわりに勝負でけりをつけるよ～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2804
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_bf96415a:

    # "Somehow, I expected this. It's the logical conclusion."
    "なんとなく、こうなるような気がしていた。論理的な帰結だ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2806
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_8e7e7da6:

    # "Shizune has been studying for a long time, pretty much continuously up until now. With our finals over, I guess that surplus energy has to go somewhere."
    "静音は長い間勉強し続けていた。今の今まで、ほとんどずっとだ。期末試験も終わったことだし、たまりにたまったエネルギーを放出しないといけないんだろう。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2808
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_ead71a0c:

    # hi "Play what?"
    hi "勝負って、どうするんだよ？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2816
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_8dd1bee3:

    # ssh "The oldest game known to man, upon which the fate of nations has been known to rest: Rock, Paper, Scissors."
    ssh "国家の運命さえ決したという人類最古のゲーム――じゃんけんよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2821
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_3ae63fca:

    # mi "We'll play Rock, Paper, Scissors."
    mi "じゃんけんで決めるよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2826
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_c6a39151:

    # mi "Really? That sounds so serious, Shicchan…"
    mi "ほんとに？　なんかすごい真剣な感じがしたよ、しっちゃん……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2830
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_25b28034:

    # "There is no humor in her expression, she is dead set on this."
    "静音の言葉遣いに冗談っぽさはまったくない。真剣そのものだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2832
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_4a1b71db:

    # hi "Okay, okay."
    hi "わかった、わかった"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2837
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_590f6a27:

    # "She draws her hand back, and I mirror her."
    "静音は手を後ろに引く。俺も同じようにする。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2839
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_b25a9f30:

    # hi "Go!"
    hi "じゃんけん、ぽん！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2844
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_b25b8117:

    # "We both put out rock. A draw. I had thought I had the perfect plan. Rock is unbeatable. Shizune frowns, deeply upset by this unexpected turn of events. Not as planned?"
    "二人ともグーを出す。あいこだ。完全に読み切っていたはずなのに。グーは無敵なのだ。静音は渋い顔をする。予想外の展開にとても不愉快そうだ。計画通りとは行かなかったかな？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2849
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_289fb96a:

    # ssh "Again!"
    ssh "あいこで！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2854
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_9b77ecb0:

    # "Two papers."
    "パーがふたつ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2856
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_4bf99ed5:

    # hi "Damn."
    hi "くっそー"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2861
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_672581fa:

    # ssh "Again!!"
    ssh "あいこで！！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2866
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_daa34f13:

    # "We both throw out two rocks again, but a third hand is among us representing scissors."
    "また二人ともグーを出す。しかし三つ目の手がチョキを出している。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2871
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_a713d15f:

    # mi "This looks like fun, can I play?"
    mi "面白そう、わたしもやっていい？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2876
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_d23dae52:

    # mi "Hahahaha~!"
    mi "はははは～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2881
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_ec41263e:

    # ssh "… … …"
    ssh "…… …… ……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2886
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_786c5ec4:

    # mi "It's a duel, Shicchan?"
    mi "決闘なの、しっちゃん？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2891
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_ef2b123c_3:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2896
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_5aad6da3:

    # mi "Eh~, dueling conduct? Hm~… You're right, you're right~! I really don't know…"
    mi "え～、決闘のルール？　む～……そうだね、そうだね～！　わたしよくわかってないから……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2901
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_ef2b123c_4:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2906
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_5b8db703:

    # "The faster she signs, the harder it is to follow. In fact, it looks like even Misha is having trouble keeping up."
    "静音の手話が速ければ速いほど、俺には読みとるのが難しくなる。実際、ミーシャでさえ追いつくのが大変そうだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2908
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_a382dadc:

    # hi "What's she talking about?"
    hi "なんて言ってるんだ？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2913
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_e05bebd9:

    # ssh "One more time!"
    ssh "もう一回！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2918
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_d5abfd86:

    # "We tie again. Every time, Shizune demands a rematch, eventually skipping that step altogether and throwing rock, paper, or scissors out with increasingly reckless abandon."
    "またあいこだ。何度やっても、静音は勝負を続けようとする。やがてその一言もすっ飛ばして、俺たちはわき目もふらずにひたすらじゃんけんを繰り返す。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2920
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_c38e1311:

    # "Even playing completely randomly, we continue to tie. This is a mathematical longshot."
    "完全に適当な手を出し続けるようになっても、ずっとあいこが続く。数学的にはものすごい偶然だ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2927
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_0226d7f5:

    # "Misha hovers above us, watching it all and laughing each time we draw. After sixteen rounds, Shizune pushes her chair away from the table and stands up."
    "ミーシャは俺たちのまわりをうろうろしながら、ずっとその様子を見ている。そしてあいこになるたびにげらげらと笑う。１６回目のあいこの後、静音はテーブルから椅子を押し出して立ち上がる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2932
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_b33ba1f7_2:

    # shi "…!"
    shi "……！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2937
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_cda7d95b:

    # mi "Enough of this, Hicchan~! I see what I have been doing wrong, this will all be over in the next round, so brace yourself, okay~? Okay~!"
    mi "もう終わりだよ、ひっちゃん～！　何を間違えてたのかわかったから、次の勝負で全部終わるよ。覚悟してね、いい～？　おっけ～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2942
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_df6abb2e:

    # mi "I have studied your thought processes and~ I see how you play. I'm anticipating your next move and will combat it expertly."
    mi "ひっちゃんの思考プロセスは見切ったし～、勝負の仕方もわかったよ。次の手は読めたから、うまくあしらっちゃうよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2944
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_b6e06a33:

    # "This is all news to me, as I can't remember what we are doing this over."
    "こんなの全部初耳だ。もう何のためにじゃんけんを続けているのか思い出せない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2949
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_781ddf47:

    # "Shizune grins confidently, a look of fearless daring on her face. Her cool eyes flash with pure competitive spirit as she draws her hand back, goading me wordlessly to do the same."
    "静音は自信たっぷりにニヤリと笑う。恐れ知らずの大胆さがその顔に浮かぶ。その手を後ろに引きながら、冷静な目つきに負けず嫌いの気合いを光らせて、俺にも同じようにしろと言葉もなしに迫る。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2951
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_2bb39d91:

    # "Her form is amazing, like a professional bowler or something, just to throw a hand motion."
    "プロのボウリング選手か何かのような、見事なフォームだ。たかがじゃんけんだというのに。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2956
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_9b77ecb0_1:

    # "Two papers."
    "パーがふたつ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2963
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_eacc7664:

    # "Shizune's body immediately goes slack, and she rubs her temples with a look of exasperation on her face as she lets out a sigh so long it sounds like a tire deflating. I realize I've gotten a lot hungrier in the time we've been doing this."
    "とたんに静音の体から緊張が解ける。怒りの表情を浮かべながらこめかみをこすり、タイヤがパンクするような音に似たため息を長々と吐き出す。この勝負を始めたときよりもずっと腹が減っていることに俺は気づく。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2965
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_83636ea0:

    # hi "We can just split it."
    hi "半分こしようぜ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2970
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_6b1e06f9:

    # "I break the bread in half and offer one half of it to Shizune. She takes it."
    "パンを半分に割って、片方を静音に差し出す。静音はそれを受け取る。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2975
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_8c0f7481:

    # ssh "Thank you."
    ssh "ありがとう"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2977
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_a5b2dfaf:

    # "She looks at the bread in her hand, studying it."
    "手の中のパンを、観察するようにじっと見ている。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2982
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_38bdf7af:

    # ssh "But this feels hollow, somehow."
    ssh "でもなんだかむなしい気分がする"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2987
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_47225dd7:

    # "Regardless of how she feels, she still eats it."
    "気持ちはどうあれ、静音は結局パンを口にする。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2989
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_0995b45f:

    # "All of a sudden, I see Misha observing the scene out of the corner of my eye."
    "突然、この状況をずっと観察していたミーシャが視界の端に入る。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2994
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_7556e045:

    # mi "Hicchan~… That was very romantic, I think."
    mi "ひっちゃん～……今のはとってもアツアツだったと思うよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:2996
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_27ece3b1:

    # hi "Oh, come on."
    hi "おい、何言ってるんだよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3001
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_2272a033:

    # mi "Wahahahahaha~!"
    mi "わははははは～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3008
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_90a8bbbf:

    # "She laughs and takes a bite of her second sandwich."
    "笑って、ミーシャは二つ目のサンドイッチをかじる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3010
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_f7c50119:

    # "We eat in silence for a while, Shizune and I managing to avoid any other contests. And then, we go back to work."
    "静音とはそれ以上勝負をせずにすんだので、俺たちはしばらく無言のまま食べ続け、そして作業に戻る。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3017
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_adef0dc8:

    # "As I finish up the day's usual filing, I think to myself that this might be Shizune's way of trying to start this week on a high note."
    "いつもの書類整理を仕上げながら、これは高いテンションで一週間を始めるための静音なりのやり方なんじゃないか、と俺は密かに考える。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3019
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_f76ab2c5:

    # "After all, tomorrow is when the real work will begin, and with her hands literally full building stalls, she won't be able to 'talk' very much."
    "結局、本番の仕事が始まるのは明日からだし。屋台の組み立てで両手がふさがってしまうので、静音が『話す』ことはあまりできなくなる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3021
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_3984c524:

    # "It will likely be pretty dull and tiring, like it was the first time around. I'm appreciative of her effort, in that case. It's nice to have days like this, as a way of enjoying yourself before the days ahead. I think that was her idea as well."
    "たぶん最初の時のように、とても退屈で疲れる作業になるだろう。だとしたら、俺は静音の気遣いに感謝する。こういう一日があるのはいいことだ。これからの日々に向けて楽しい気分になれる、というのは。 それも静音の考えのうちだったんだろう。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3023
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_a6a754db:

    # "…I also remember that I still have to get rid of Kenji's package. The damn thing is bulky, and somehow I've never been able to track him down since I picked it up."
    "……まだ健二の小包を始末していなかったことも思い出す。あれは邪魔くさいし、しかも包みを受け取ってからずっと健二を見かけていない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3028
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_aa98e0e1:

    # "After Student Council is adjourned for the day, I walk towards the vending machines to look for something to drink, parting from Shizune and Misha. It's a short trip, but after even just a few seconds I start to get the feeling I'm not alone."
    "その日の生徒会の活動が終わってから、俺は静音とミーシャと別れて、飲み物を買いに自動販売機へ向かう。短い道のりだけど、数秒も経たないうちに誰かが付いてきている気配を感じる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3033
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_f7eaabdd:

    # "A pair of hands cover my eyes."
    "誰かの手が俺の目を覆う。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3035
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_ae790774:

    # mi "Guess who~!"
    mi "だ～れだ！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3037
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_df2f31c1:

    # hi "Shizune?"
    hi "静音か？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3039
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_1eb817f1:

    # mi "Wahahaha~! It's me, Hicchan~!"
    mi "わははは～！　わたしだよ、ひっちゃん～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3041
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_9fc74fe3:

    # hi "Yeah, I know."
    hi "ああ、わかってるよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3056
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_9da17c60:

    # mi "Then why did you say it was Shicchan~? It's okay to be wrong sometimes, Hicchan~! You're too proud."
    mi "じゃあどうしてしっちゃんだって言ったの～？　時々は間違ったっていいんだよ、ひっちゃん～！　ひっちゃんはプライド高すぎだよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3061
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_8d8f11c9:

    # mi "Anyway~, after Student Council, you don't usually have any plans, right~? So, you're just going to go straight to your dorm?"
    mi "とにかく～、生徒会の後は、いつも予定とか何もないでしょ～？　だから、寮にまっすぐ戻るだけなんだよね？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3063
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_2f946f7c:

    # hi "Where else would I go?"
    hi "ほかにどこに行くってんだよ？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3068
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_4e041a94:

    # mi "Okay, that's great~! That's great, Hicchan~! I wanted to talk to you today, so this works out perfectly!"
    mi "おっけ、よかった～！　ばっちりだよ、ひっちゃん～！　今日はひっちゃんとお話ししたかったから、とっても都合がいいよ！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3070
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_59e20535:

    # "Two high school students, alone after classes in a quiet, empty building. As the sun dyes the sky a romantic amber color, the cute girl says that she wants to talk."
    "人気のない校舎で、放課後に高校生が二人きり。夕日が空をロマンチックな琥珀色で染める中、かわいらしい女の子が話があると言ってくる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3072
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_3195bdd9:

    # "What a secretive and appealing situation, my imagination is buzzing. It's likely not going to be anywhere near as exciting as I am making it out to be, but it's fun to play it up that way."
    "なんて秘密めいたおいしいシチュエーションなんだ。俺は想像をたくましくしてしまう。自分が妄想しているような状況になるとはとうてい思えないけど、そういうふりをするのは楽しい。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3078
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_bc84ea9f:

    # "The popping sound of my canned coffee opening destroys any chance of maintaining such a cheesy mood, sounding louder than I'd have ever thought imaginable, amplified by the context of the situation. I sigh in disappointment and relief."
    "缶コーヒーを開ける音で、そんなクサいムードを保つチャンスも吹っ飛んでしまう。想像も付かないほど大きな音だったけど、状況も手伝ってよけいに大きく聞こえる。俺は失望と安心の混ざったため息をつく。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3080
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_56155f43:

    # hi "So, what is it?"
    hi "で、何だよ？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3085
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_10e14648:

    # mi "Hm? Oh! Actually~… I'm a little behind in some of my classes, and if I don't catch up, it could be a problem~! I can't put it off any longer."
    mi "えっ？　ああ！　実はね～……授業に追いつけてない科目があって、このままだとまずいかもしれないの～！　これ以上先延ばしにはできないの"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3090
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_4782d009:

    # mi "My teachers say that I have to really start taking things seriously, so I should listen, especially~ because this is the third time."
    mi "もう真剣に授業に取り組まなきゃだめだって先生に言われて、それでちゃんと授業を聞かないといけないの。なんてったって～、これでもう３回目だからね"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3092
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_0bb44282:

    # mi "Sorry~! I'm sorry, Hicchan."
    mi "ごめんね～！　ほんとにごめんね、ひっちゃん"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3094
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_a7c33e8c:

    # hi "Why are you apologizing?"
    hi "どうして謝るんだよ？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3099
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_37979213:

    # mi "I won't be able to help you or Shicchan with Student Council for a few days~. It'll only be for two or three days, really! I'll definitely try and come back as soon as possible! But~…"
    mi "しばらくひっちゃんとしっちゃんの生徒会の仕事を手伝えなくなっちゃうの～。２、３日だけだから、ほんとに！　絶対がんばってできるだけ早く復帰するから！　でも～……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3101
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_778717eb:

    # "I can't say I'm happy about this. It's supposed to be getting really busy this week too, isn't it? That's some unfortunate timing. For a second I want to ask if maybe Shizune could pull some strings to get her out of it."
    "うれしい気分とは言えない。今週はものすごく忙しくなる予定じゃなかったのか？　なんて間の悪い。静音なら何か手を回してミーシャを救い出せるんじゃないかと、思わず聞いてしまいそうになる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3103
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_af7eb60a:

    # "But Misha looks so genuinely apologetic about it. It would be pretty dickish of me to say something like that."
    "でもミーシャは純粋に申し訳なさそうにしている。そんなことを口にするのはただの馬鹿野郎だ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3105
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_ad6eced8:

    # "Besides, if she says it's something that can't be put off any longer, I'm inclined to believe her, considering how surprisingly serious she can be with student council duties."
    "それに、本人がこれ以上先送りできないと言うのなら、俺はミーシャを信じたい。生徒会の仕事だって驚くほど真剣に取り組んでいるのだから。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3107
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_daea919f:

    # hi "Yeah, I see. It's okay. You managed with just Shizune and yourself last year, didn't you? So I'm sure I'll be able to as well. Don't worry about it."
    hi "ああ、わかったよ。大丈夫。去年は静音と二人きりでなんとかしたんだろ？　きっと俺にだってできるさ。心配すんなって"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3112
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_9a0c3d37:

    # mi "Really? Thank you, Hicchan~! Really~! Yay yay~! I didn't know Hicchan would take it so well~! I thought you would be worried, with how there's going to be so~ much work, with Tanabata coming up and everything~!"
    mi "ほんとに？　ありがと、ひっちゃん～！　まじで！　やったやった～！　ひっちゃんが納得してくれるって思わなかったよ～！　仕事がすっごくたくさんあるから、心配すると思ってたよ、七夕とかいろいろね～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3114
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_446d2e71:

    # "Damn, she knows me oddly well."
    "なんだよ、やけに俺のことをわかってるな。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3119
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_0f7c1b59:

    # mi "…But~! Hicchan is so composed~! I'm glad~…"
    mi "……でも～！　ひっちゃんはすごく冷静だね～！　うれしいよ～……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3121
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_b46d7f9a:

    # hi "Haha, yeah. You're sort of right, I was thinking about it, but it's not that big a deal. I'm not going to freak out over that."
    hi "はは、そうだな。たしかにそうだよ、そのことは考えてたけど、でも大したことじゃない。それでパニックになったりはしないよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3123
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_5bd36c0b:

    # hi "It's going to be a little annoying passing that pad back and forth to talk to Shizune, though."
    hi "静音と話すのにメモ帳をずっとやりとりし続けるのはちょっと大変かもしれないけどな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3128
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_411093b0:

    # mi "Hicchan, just tell Shicchan that you can use sign language too! I don't understand why you won't."
    mi "ひっちゃん、自分も手話が使えるってしっちゃんに言っちゃいなよ！　どうして言わないのかわかんないよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3130
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_0ccd3ca5:

    # hi "Not yet. I can understand most things already, but I want to be really sure. Heh, actually, I wouldn't mind. The secrecy is killing me too, and it would be nice to be able to talk to her in a real conversation."
    hi "まだだめだ。ほとんどわかるようになってるけど、間違いないようにしておきたい。てか、実際どうでもいいんだけど。ずっと秘密にしてるのは俺もつらいよ。それに静音と本当に会話できたらいいだろうなって思う"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3132
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_902d4614:

    # hi "Don't worry, I'm going to have to tell her eventually. I want to. Actually, I'm trying to think of a good opportunity for it."
    hi "大丈夫だよ、そのうちあいつには言わないといけないから。そのためのいいタイミングを考えてるところなんだ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3137
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_5462dd05:

    # mi "That won't be a problem, Hicchan~!"
    mi "そのことなら心配ないよ、ひっちゃん～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3139
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_f5743db9_1:

    # hi "Why not?"
    hi "どうして？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3146
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_088068c7:

    # mi "Well~, because I… kind of… told Shicchan that you could understand her. She was worried about the same thing, that you wouldn't be able to understand each other~! So~! I was worried, but it worked out fine in the end after all~!"
    mi "えっと～、それはわたしが……ひっちゃんはしっちゃんの言葉がわかるよって教えてあげた……っていうか しっちゃんも同じことを心配してたの。お互いのことを理解できないんじゃないかって～！　だから～！　わたしも心配してたけど、最後には結局うまくいったね～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3151
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_4416cc89:

    # mi "Hahaha?"
    mi "ははは？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3153
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_d573c9a3:

    # "I lose it."
    "もうだめだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3157
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_3ca9cba2:

    # hi "AAAAAAAAAAHHH!!"
    hi "あああああああああああああ！！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3159
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_0c8f9157:

    # hi "Do you know how stupid I look now? I sat there for like half the damn day acting like I couldn't read sign language, and are you seriously telling me that she knew the whole time I could?"
    hi "俺がどれだけバカみたいに見えるかお前わかってるのか？　こっちは丸一日手話なんてわかりませんってふりしてたのに、静音は最初から知ってたって、本気で言ってるのかよ？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3161
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_aab12e18:

    # hi "She was probably thinking, 'this guy is a complete jackass, pretending he can't understand me.' I just made a total ass of myself."
    hi "きっと『私のことをわからないふりをして、とんだ大バカね』なんて思ってるに違いないんだ。俺は自分で自分を笑い物にしちまったんだぞ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3163
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_0e2eaf69:

    # hi "How could you let me do this?!"
    hi "なんてことさせてくれるんだよ！？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3168
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_40ccfe0b:

    # "Misha frowns, seeming lost for words on realizing that I'm taking this differently than she might have expected. She doesn't speak again until after seeing that I've calmed down."
    "ミーシャは顔をしかめる。自分が思っていたような受け止め方を俺がしていないことに、言葉を失っているようだ。俺が落ち着くのを見届けるまで、ミーシャは口を開かない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3173
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_ca3c077b:

    # mi "…But, Hicchan, I think this is definitely for the best~!"
    mi "……でもひっちゃん、結局これが一番だったと思うよ～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3175
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_ea4b22d2:

    # "She says without batting an eye, having waited patiently through my panic to say it."
    "俺のパニックが収まるまで辛抱強く待った上で、ミーシャはまばたきもせずに言う。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3177
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_08abd534:

    # "The cheerful delivery of her words makes it seem like she sliced out the time between when she dropped the bomb on me and now. It's pretty funny, in a way."
    "その陽気な言い方は、さっき俺に向けて爆弾を落とした瞬間から今までの時間がすっ飛ばされたような気分にさせる。ある意味、かなりおかしい。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3179
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_20da1f49:

    # hi "You have such a one track mind, you know that?"
    hi "お前ってほんとに単細胞だよな、知ってたか？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3184
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_57954593:

    # mi "Yes~!"
    mi "知ってるよ～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3188
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_40ba0fc2:

    # "The damage is done. If Misha can believe that things will work out with such unflinching surety, then maybe it's worth giving it a chance."
    "どうせもう後の祭りだ。ミーシャがこれだけ断固たる確かさでこれがうまく行くと信じているなら、その可能性に賭けてみる価値はあるのかもしれない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3190
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_1b368aa2:

    # "And if things don't work out, I'll run as fast as I possibly can…"
    "それに、もしうまくいかなければ、全速力で走って逃げるさ……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3192
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_84c851e4:

    # "To try and make it up to me anyway just in case, she offers to buy me another drink from the vending machine. It's a very small token of apology, but I suppose it's the thought that counts, and her thoughts are sincere."
    "埋め合わせをしようと、ミーシャは自動販売機のドリンクをもう一つおごってくれる。とてもささやかなお詫びの印だけど、大事なのは気持ちということだろう。それにミーシャの思いやりは心からのものだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3194
translate jp a2_shizune_bread_scissors_paper_d592f071:

    # "Plus it's a free drink, so I accept."
    "ついでにおごりなので、俺はそれに甘える。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3208
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_a93a5827:

    # "I throw back my daily fistful of pills with a glass of water."
    "今日もひと握り分の薬をコップの水で飲み下す。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3210
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_62964872:

    # "After a solid eight hours of sleep, I don't really know what I was so afraid of last night. As I chew a particularly large tablet in half, I continue to rationalize my worries away."
    "８時間の熟睡から目覚めてみると、昨夜の心配ごとがいったいなんだったのか、もう思い出せない。やたらと大きな錠剤を半分にかみ砕きながら、俺はあれこれ理屈付けをして不安な気持ちを打ち消し続ける。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3215
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3219
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_820ec817:

    # n "{vspace=30}Shizune knew I was taking sign language classes all day yesterday, and didn't make a big deal out of it."
    n "\n\n\n\n\n静音は俺が手話の授業を受けていたことを昨日ずっと知っていて、でも何も詮索しなかった。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3221
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_ac8eb21f:

    # n "She might be mute, but that doesn't mean she can't make her feelings known. No, in fact, it seems like she's all the more direct for it."
    n "口がきけないからといって、自分の気持ちを伝えることができないわけじゃない。いや、だからこそあいつは遠慮せずに気持ちを表に出しているように見える。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3223
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_535b5992:

    # n "She doesn't beat around the bush or hold back, she always makes herself clear unapologetically, so there can be no mistakes."
    n "回りくどい言い方をしたり、気持ちを抑えたりしない。誤解の余地がないように、いつも悪びれることなく自分の意見をはっきりと伝える。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3225
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_a0cf7ff1:

    # n "So, if she wasn't mad then, it's unlikely she would be at all. And on top of that, I didn't do anything wrong, anyway."
    n "つまり、昨日の時点で静音が怒っていなかったのなら、最初から怒ってなんかいないということだ。そもそも、俺が何か間違ったことをしたわけでもない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3227
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_25233c1c:

    # n "But as that fear of mine recedes, the thought of spending a couple days with Shizune without Misha takes its place. I hadn't really thought about it yesterday, but the idea becomes more and more intimidating. It's true I can understand sign language pretty well, but…"
    n "\n\n\n\n\nでも俺の不安が静まるにつれて、しばらくミーシャ抜きで静音と二人きりで過ごさないといけないことに思いが至る。昨日はあまり気にしなかったけど、どんどん心配になってくる。確かにもう手話はかなり理解できるようになった、でも……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3229
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_b5228e60:

    # n "I would definitely hesitate to say I can understand it above a basic level, and if she were to speed up her signing, which she does quite a bit, I don't think I could keep up."
    n "その理解が初級よりもましだと言うには大いにためらいがある。それに静音はいつもそうするけど、手話のスピードが上がったら、ついていける気がしない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3231
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_4b4c80d0:

    # n "Signing, too, is not my strong suit. Doing both at the same time like Misha can is still a distant dream."
    n "手話をするのだって得意とはいえない。ミーシャのように両方を同時にこなすのはまだまだ遠い夢だ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3235
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3243
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_e6edfcee:

    # mi "Hicchan~!"
    mi "ひっちゃん～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3245
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_81d99227:

    # hi "What?"
    hi "なんだよ？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3250
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_9ab6fbff:

    # mi "Don't forget, you said you would help out with building stalls today~! Behind the school after classes are over, okay~?"
    mi "忘れちゃだめだよ、今日は屋台の組み立てを手伝ってくれるって言ったよね～！　放課後に校舎の裏だよ、おっけ～？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3252
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_ee322606:

    # hi "I know, I know."
    hi "はいはい、わかってるよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3257
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_ef2b123c:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3262
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_fe2b1e0f:

    # mi "Last time you helped out, Hicchan, we really appreciated it~! This time, it's even more important, so skipping out is unforgivable, okay?"
    mi "前に手伝ってくれたときはね、ひっちゃん、とっても助かったんだよ～！　今度は前よりももっと大事だから、絶対さぼったりしちゃだめだからね、わかった？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3264
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_63e897ac:

    # "I want to ask why that is, but there isn't any opportunity to. Besides, Misha is behind in her classes, so it seems like a bad idea to distract her now that I know that. I can always ask her at lunch, which is what I end up doing."
    "その理由を聞きたいけど、聞くチャンスは得られなかった。それに授業についていけていないと知っている以上、ミーシャの気を散らすのは良くない。昼休みなら聞いてもいいだろうと思ったので、結局そうする。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3271
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_9eac2121:

    # mi "Because, Hicchan, a festival that celebrates a town is exactly what it sounds like. It's to celebrate your home and its history."
    mi "それはね、ひっちゃん、町のお祭りは言葉通り、ふるさとや町の歴史を祝うものでしょ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3276
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_c06d5fbf:

    # mi "Tanabata is different, it's for wishes and lovers~! That definitely makes it more important, doesn't it? Yeah~, naturally, it would be~."
    mi "七夕はそうじゃなくて、お願いや恋人のお祭りなわけ～！　だからずっと大事なお祭りなんだよ、そうでしょ？　そうだよ～、当然だよね～"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3278
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_f9e579ae:

    # hi "Is that really what it's for, though?"
    hi "七夕ってほんとにそういうお祭りだったっけ？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3283
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_ef2b123c_1:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3288
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_7f1df333:

    # mi "Hicchan, you have no sense of fun…"
    mi "ひっちゃんは遊び心ってものが全然ないよ……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3290
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_20984015:

    # "She puffs out her cheeks in displeasure before blowing the air out like a deflating balloon."
    "不機嫌そうに頬を膨らませると、風船がしぼむときのようにぷうっと息を吹き出す。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3295
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_c65cc816:

    # mi "You have to appreciate things like that, even if it's just an excuse to eat interesting things and dress up in the end~!"
    mi "そういうことにもっと感謝の気持ちを持たなきゃだめだよ、おいしいものを食べておめかしするための口実だとしてもね～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3300
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_8d7189c0:

    # mi "I'll be disappointed in you if you don't, okay?"
    mi "そうしないなら、ひっちゃんには失望しちゃうよ、わかった？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3304
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_9ba55b5d:

    # "Before I can say anything, she turns to the side to inhale a croquette."
    "何か返事をしようとする間もなく、ミーシャは横を向いてコロッケを一口で飲み込む。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3309
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_804b8ab5:

    # "After classes, I meet Shizune behind the school, where it seems she already set everything up sometime yesterday."
    "放課後、校舎裏で静音と落ち合う。見る限り、どうやら昨日のうちに準備をすべて済ませていたようだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3314
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_c67d22c9:

    # "She greets me with a short wave, and then with a flourish of the hammer already in her hand, extends her arm towards the stalls behind her, some of them already half completed, others still haphazard piles of board bundled together with string."
    "軽く手を振って俺を迎えると、すでに手に持っていたハンマーを見せびらかして、後ろにある屋台に向かって腕を伸ばす。 いくつかはもう途中まで組み上がっているけど、それ以外はひもで縛った板がごちゃごちゃと山積みになっているだけだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3326
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_0a10b872:

    # "As time passes, I realize the pills can only do so much. I still get way more tired than should be normal. Luckily, Shizune's back is to me, so I can afford to take a lot of breaks without having to worry about her wondering why."
    "時間が経つにつれ、薬の効果には限りがあることを思い知る。今もありえないくらい体が疲れる。幸い、静音はこっちに背中を向けているから、理由を詮索される心配なしにたっぷり休憩することができる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3328
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_a54388ab:

    # "When I stop and think about it, though, I start to feel pretty guilty for taking advantage of her inability to hear that my hammer's stopped banging. It's a terrible thing to be happy about."
    "でもちょっと考えてみると、俺はハンマーを叩く音が途切れるのを静音が聞き取れない弱みにつけこんでいる。そのことがとても後ろめたく思えてくる。喜ぶなんてとんでもないことだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3330
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_41dc5b40:

    # "Her work ethic is admirable. It's obvious that it bores her, and even annoys her, but she doesn't slacken her pace. When she gets tired nailing a stall together with one arm, she switches to the other."
    "静音の勤勉さは尊敬に値する。仕事にうんざりしているどころかいらだっているのも明らかだけど、それでもペースを落としたりはしない。片手で釘を打つのに疲れると、もう一方の手に切り替えている。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3332
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_a4a4f781:

    # hi "Shizune—"
    hi "静音――"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3334
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_11100cc5:

    # "I feel like an idiot the second I say her name."
    "名前を呼んだ直後、バカみたいな気分になる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3336
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_eb5017b5:

    # "I can't tell her what I think. There's a hammer in my hand as well, and in the end, I feel like I have to keep up with her."
    "今の気持ちは静音には言えない。俺の手にもハンマーがある。結局、静音に遅れずについていかなきゃだめだという気分になってくる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3338
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_825f0419:

    # "I can't slack off either, especially when it's just the two of us. There's no time to sign, no opportunity. Not even for a compliment for a job well done."
    "俺だってさぼってはいられない。俺たち二人だけしかいないのだからなおさらだ。手話を伝える時間も、そのチャンスもない。お疲れさまと言葉をかけることさえできない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3340
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_362b7064:

    # "Even something as casual as that would require me to put my hammer down, get her attention, and then sign it to her."
    "そんな何気ない一言でさえ、ハンマーをおいて静音の注意を引き、手を動かして手話で伝えなければいけない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3342
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_9f060d0e:

    # "A simple gesture turned into something so needlessly complex, like a single footstep taken on a road that's longer than first imagined."
    "単純な手ぶりだというのに、不必要に複雑になってしまう。道に向かって踏み出した一歩が、思っていたよりも長かったときのように。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3344
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_3a6286cb:

    # "I've known her long enough to know this, and still forgot it."
    "それを理解できるくらいには静音とは長く付き合ってきたつもりだけど、それでも俺は度忘れしてしまっていた。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3346
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_24143e76:

    # "The air is filled with the rhythmic knocking of nails being driven into wood."
    "釘が木材に埋め込まれるリズミカルな音が空気を満たしている。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3348
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_adf35f89:

    # "It's actually kind of nice after a while. To pass the monotony of the task at hand, I try to match my hammering to Shizune's, then alternate it to try and form a beat. Of course, she doesn't notice."
    "しばらくして、なんだかいいなと思えてくる。目の前の仕事の単調さをまぎらわそうと、静音がハンマーを打つのと同じタイミングで、そして裏拍子を取るように交互に釘を打ってみる。もちろん静音は気が付かない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3350
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_9369fc6c:

    # "It makes me wonder, does the lack of sound make this work seem more drawn out and boring to her?"
    "音が聞こえないことで、静音にとってはよけいに作業が退屈でつまらないものに感じられたりするんだろうか？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3354
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_96fd4e25:

    # "Is it strange, being unable to hear the results of her actions even as she feels the vibrations through her fingers? Or, having no concept of sound, does it bother her at all?"
    "振動が指に伝わっているのに、自分の行動の結果を耳で聞くことができないというのは、おかしなことなのか？　音という概念を知らないこと自体、静音はそもそも気にしているんだろうか？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3356
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_b45f635a:

    # "Distracted, I don't notice Shizune sneaking up on me until her head pops into view."
    "気が散ってしまった俺は、静音の頭が目の前に飛び出してくるまで、そばに忍び寄られていたことに気づかない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3364
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_993b7491:

    # ssh "Taking a break?"
    ssh "休憩してるの？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3366
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_e4d90053:

    # his "Yeah, I guess."
    his "ああ、そんな感じ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3371
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_5be049a4:

    # ssh "Okay, let's do that."
    ssh "いいわ、そうしましょう"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3376
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_709cde7a:

    # ssh "You can understand sign language."
    ssh "手話がわかるのね"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3381
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_493e7037:

    # ssh "That makes it more convenient for both of us. Even though you hid it from me."
    ssh "お互いにとって好都合ね。私には隠してたけど"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3383
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_e3992bb2:

    # hi "Hahaha…"
    hi "ははは……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3388
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_9c4c4dc6:

    # ssh "Why?"
    ssh "どうして？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3390
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_ebc3850f:

    # his "Why what?"
    his "どうしてって、何が？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3395
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_b29c71b0:

    # ssh "Why did you decide to take sign language?"
    ssh "どうして手話のクラスをとろうって思ったの？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3397
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_8554e78c:

    # "Her eyes don't break off from mine even for a second, if she needs to read my response, her peripheral vision is good enough. Once she has something in her gaze, she doesn't look away."
    "静音の視線は一秒たりとも俺の目から離れない。俺の反応を見たいのだとしたら、周辺視野で十分だろう。一度何かが視界に入ったら、静音は絶対に目をそらさない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3399
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_20e0ebfc:

    # "It's strange how piercing her eyes can be, dark as a lake at night."
    "静音の目は驚くほど鋭く、夜の湖のように暗い。不思議な感じがする。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3401
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_12e673ca:

    # his "Because I wanted to. It seemed like it would come in handy. And it did, didn't it?"
    his "そうしたかったからさ。そのうち役に立つかもって思ったんだ。実際役に立っただろ？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3406
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_1d374688:

    # ssh "Yes."
    ssh "そう"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3411
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_ef2b123c_2:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3413
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_9e9ab637:

    # his "Sorry, I didn't catch any of that."
    his "ごめん、今の一言もわからなかった"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3415
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_11973358:

    # his "See? This kind of thing still comes up now and then. I wish Misha was here."
    his "ほらな？　時々今みたいなことになるんだ。ミーシャがいてくれたらよかったな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3420
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_a2e299b1:

    # ssh "She has work to make up for, doesn't she? That might be partly my fault. Misha doesn't need supplemental lessons. Her grades aren't the best, but she understands how the decisions she makes affect others. That puts her ahead of many people."
    ssh "ミーシャには追いつかないといけない勉強があるんでしょう？　私にも責任があるかもしれない ミーシャには補習は必要ない。成績は上出来とは言えないけど、自分の決めたことが他の人にどう影響するかは理解している。その点は他の人よりもずっと優れているわ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3425
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_dfc886c1:

    # ssh "Especially certain blondes."
    ssh "特にどこかの金髪よりはね"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3427
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_853713d8:

    # hi "Ah…"
    hi "あー……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3429
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_11de2b2a:

    # "She doesn't forget things easily."
    "結構根に持つタイプなんだな。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3434
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_5e45212f:

    # ssh "Your sign language is very good. You're learning oddly fast."
    ssh "あなたの手話はとても上手ね。そんなに早く覚えるなんておかしいでしょ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3436
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_b88ae183:

    # his "I've been taking classes for a while now. And it's kind of easy to pick up after awhile, through immersion, or osmosis, that kind of thing. It's not too bad."
    his "もう手話のクラスを始めてからずいぶんたつからね。それにしばらく続けていると、集中できるっていうか、しみこんでくるっていうか、だんだんわかりやすくなっていくし。いい感じだよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3438
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_6980a74b:

    # his "And if I'm really stuck, Misha's there, too."
    his "それに、本当にわからないときはミーシャもいるし"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3443
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_ef2b123c_3:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3448
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_ef2b123c_4:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3450
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_8f510342:

    # "I guess I spoke too soon. I didn't understand any of that. Time to backpedal."
    "うかつだったな。今の手話はひとつもわからなかった。前言撤回か。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3452
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_5014f579:

    # his "Well, yeah, it's actually not that easy. It's actually hard as hell. Like trying to pick up broken glass."
    his "まあ、そうだな、本当はそんなに簡単じゃない。実際には死ぬほど難しいよ。割れたガラスのかけらを拾うようなものだな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3454
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_130f7731:

    # his "But I guess in some ways it's interesting, as well. Like an adventure. Well, no…"
    his "でもある意味、興味深くもあるんだ。冒険みたいな。まあ、ちがうけど……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3459
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_7bc4868e:

    # ssh "Picking up broken glass is not an adventure."
    ssh "ガラスのかけらを拾うのは冒険とは言わないでしょ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3461
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_eb68620b:

    # his "Sure it is. It's just as challenging."
    his "言うさ。同じくらい難しいってこと"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3466
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_0be2b26c:

    # ssh "If you use a dustpan and a broom it's not."
    ssh "ほうきとちりとりを使えば簡単よ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3468
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_1d6d16cd:

    # "I feel frustrated and sad."
    "俺はイライラして、悲しくなってくる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3470
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_a7e8e59d:

    # "When I look up, I notice she has a can of soda in her hand."
    "顔を上げると、静音が手にソーダの缶を持っているのに気づく。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3472
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_70f21aba:

    # hi "Where did you get that?"
    hi "どこでそれを？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3477
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_b3137d7a:

    # "I forget to sign it, but she understands anyway, following my eyes, and produces another one from behind her back. She tosses it in my direction, and I catch it with both hands."
    "手話で伝えるのを度忘れしたけど、俺の目線を追っていた静音には伝わる。そして背中からもう一缶取り出し、こっちに放り投げる。俺は両手でそれを受け止める。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3482
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_b17cfe05:

    # ssh "I brought an extra one for you."
    ssh "あなたの分も持ってきたの"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3486
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_00be4e0c:

    # "She pauses to slide her fingernail under the tab of her can and pop it open before setting it aside for a moment."
    "静音は手を止めると、缶のタブに爪をかけてふたを開け、そのまま脇に置く。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3491
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_3d737473:

    # ssh "If you are going to try and help me so much, then I have to look out for you too. It's only natural."
    ssh "そんなにがんばって私のことを助けてくれるんだから、私だってあなたのことを気にかけないとね。当然でしょう"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3496
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_8f8df02e:

    # ssh "If you're going to learn sign language, that is something entirely different. I'm naturally going to be impressed. What separates the two is obligation."
    ssh "でもあなたが手話を習うというのなら、それは全く話が別。感心するのが当たり前。二つを分けるのは義務かどうかよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3503
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_913d21b1:

    # ssh "I'm very happy."
    ssh "私、とてもうれしい"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3508
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_2d844480:

    # "She downs her drink in one go, stretches her arms behind her back and jumps to her feet."
    "ドリンク缶を一息に飲み干すと、静音は後ろに腕を伸ばし、さっと立ち上がる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3513
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_3b271474:

    # ssh "OK! Back to work!"
    ssh "オーケー！　仕事に戻るよ！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3518
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_23eded14:

    # "And like that, it's over. Shizune returns to her work with the same energy as before, the lingering traces of a smile on her face the only evidence that she had taken a break at all."
    "そうして、話は終わる。静音はさっきと同じように仕事に精を出す。口の端にわずかに残る笑みが、多少なりとも休憩を取ったという唯一の証だ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3525
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_f2eabd90:

    # "As I do the same, I think that Misha was right in saying everything would work out for the best. Everything so far seems to be going in that direction."
    "同じように作業に戻りながら、なにもかもうまくいく、というミーシャの言葉は正しかったのだと思う。今のところは、すべてのことがいい方向に向かっている。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3527
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_27846fc3:

    # "Misha swings by as it starts to get darker, looking just as tired as I feel, and Shizune decides to stop for today."
    "暗くなり始める頃、ミーシャが顔を出す。俺と同じくらい疲れているみたいだ。そしてこの辺で終わりにしようと静音が告げる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3529
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_eafd22b1:

    # "As we cover the day's work and go our separate ways, I look at how fluidly they talk to each other, and how easily they laugh together as they walk to their dorm."
    "今日の成果にカバーをかけてそれぞれに帰り道につく間、俺は静音とミーシャが寮へと戻る間に、二人が流れるように会話し、やすやすと一緒に笑い合うのを見つめる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3531
translate jp a2_shizune_interface_7a4cbffd:

    # "It makes me appreciate Misha's skill at sign language more. I wonder if I'll ever reach that level, or if I even will have the time to."
    "ミーシャの手話のうまさに改めて感心する。いったい俺はあんなレベルに達することができるんだろうか。そもそもそんな時間はあるんだろうか。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3547
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_2802b712:

    # "The first thing I do this morning is trip once again over Kenji's package as I get out of bed, finding myself diving headfirst into the floor before I'm even fully awake."
    "今朝一番の出来事は、ベッドから出たとたんに健二の小包につまずいて、まだ目もちゃんと覚めていないのに頭から床に突っ込んだことだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3558
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_eba94ef1:

    # "I want to smack this thing with the first blunt object I can find, like I'm going for a home run, but I don't even have the energy for that this early in the morning… and it would likely damage whatever's inside. And that would be mean."
    "手近にある鈍器でこいつを殴りつけてやりたい衝動に駆られる。ホームラン狙いだ。でも朝が早すぎてそんな気力も出てこない……それに中身も傷ついてしまうだろう。さすがにそれは意地が悪い。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3570
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_5be785bf:

    # "I slide it into the hallway. It sails along the smooth floor with little difficulty and stops with a soft and almost inaudible bump on colliding with Kenji's door. Immediately, a dozen locks unbolt in succession like a mounting symphony."
    "俺は箱を廊下に押し出す。それはなんなくなめらかな床を滑って、健二の部屋のドアにぶつかると、ほとんど聞き取れないくらいやわらかな音を立てる。 その直後に１ダースほどの錠前が、盛り上がる交響曲のように立て続けに外れる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3582
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_63e10f06:

    # ke "Who is it?"
    ke "誰だ？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3584
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_3be6201c:

    # "He says, as he blindly steps forward into the hallway anyway, somehow stepping over the box in a way that would be uncharacteristically, impressively graceful if it weren't for the fact I know it was wholly accidental."
    "と健二が言い、返事も待たずにのこのこと廊下に出る。どういうわけか健二らしくない見事な優雅さで、転ぶことなく箱の上をまたぐ。俺には全くの偶然だというのが明らかだったけど。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3586
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_5c37c2be:

    # hi "It's me, I got your mail. You're standing over it."
    hi "俺だよ。お前の小包、受け取ってきたぞ。お前が今上に立ってる"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3591
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_8235ca7b:

    # ke "I know. Thanks a lot, man."
    ke "わかってる。ありがとよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3593
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_7dff34d4:

    # hi "…Yeah, whatever."
    hi "……ああ、まあ別に"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3595
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_2735e6d4:

    # hi "So what's in it?"
    hi "で、中身は何だよ？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3600
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_e94e0107:

    # "He cringes, instantly turning very defensive and agitated."
    "健二は縮み上がると、一瞬で身構えて動揺し始める。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3602
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_d471571b:

    # ke "It's nothing."
    ke "なんでもねえよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3604
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_a1f0fcb3:

    # hi "Come on, tell me, I'm curious."
    hi "いいだろ、教えろよ。気になるんだよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3606
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_ff0731c8:

    # hi "And you know, I almost broke my neck falling over it, and before that I had to carry the stupidly large box around with it blocking my vision, crossing roads with it in front of me… I think you can at least tell me what's inside in return."
    hi "俺それにつまずいて首を折りそうになったんだぞ。それにそのバカみたいにでかい箱を目の前に抱えて、前も見えないまま道を渡らなきゃいけなかったんだ……お礼に中身が何か教えてくれたっていいんじゃないの"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3608
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_d086b3d2:

    # ke "It's secret stuff. I can't tell you, because then it wouldn't be very secret and shit. It's nothing important."
    ke "秘密のブツなんだよ。バラしたら秘密でもなんでもなくなるだろ、だからだめだ。大したもんじゃねえよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3610
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_8b158e12:

    # hi "Well, if it's nothing important, you can tell me."
    hi "へえ、大したもんじゃないなら教えたっていいだろ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3612
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_b7cdee3a:

    # ke "If it's nothing important, why do you have to know?"
    ke "大したもんじゃないんだから、知る必要なんてないだろ？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3614
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_f1001217:

    # hi "Why is that wrong?"
    hi "知りたいことの何がおかしい？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3616
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_1f9ce9a8:

    # ke "Why do you have to know?"
    ke "どうして知りたいんだよ？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3618
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_3e7d1d41:

    # hi "Why can't I know?"
    hi "どうして知ったらいけないんだよ？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3623
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_7c4ba949:

    # ke "Why are you answering my questions with questions?"
    ke "どうして俺の質問に質問で返すんだよ？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3625
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_d05b8097:

    # hi "Why won't you answer my first question?"
    hi "どうして俺の最初の質問に答えないんだ？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3627
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_49219b98:

    # ke "Why won't you answer my last question?!"
    ke "どうして俺の最後の質問に答えねえんだよ！？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3629
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_7ef7efcd:

    # "I realize our voices are getting higher with each reply. Down the hall, a door pops open and someone sticks his head out quizzically to see what is going on."
    "どちらも言葉を返すたびに声がうわずっているのに気づく。廊下の奥でドアが開いて、誰かが不審そうな表情で頭を突きだして様子をうかがっている。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3631
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_e8748865:

    # "We must look like such tools, but I bet I'm the only one out of the two of us with enough shame to realize it."
    "きっと２人ともバカみたいに見えているに違いない。でもそれに気づけるほど恥の意識を自覚しているのは俺だけだろう。賭けてもいい。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3633
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_980f567f:

    # hi "Fine, you can take it to your grave. I have to get ready for school anyway."
    hi "わかったよ、じゃあそいつは墓場まで持ってけ。どうせ学校の準備しなきゃいけないしな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3638
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_b576e267:

    # ke "Damn, no. Why are you so hasty to leave? Stick around a little. You want some coffee? It's been a while. You know, I thought you were dead since you were so slow with the package delivery."
    ke "なんだよ、ちげえよ。何をそんなに急いでるんだ？　少しつき合えよ。コーヒー飲むか？　しばらくぶりだしな。そういえば、お前が小包を持ってくるのがあんまり遅かったから、死んだのかと思ってたんだぜ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3640
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_5e075d9a:

    # hi "You're lucky I was willing to do package delivery in the first place, smartass!"
    hi "そもそも俺がそれを運ぶのを引き受けた時点で運が良かったって気づけよ、このうぬぼれ屋！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3645
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_86dc1805:

    # ke "Whoa, calm down. Man, you are so confrontational. Is it because of the Student Council thing? I hear you hang out with them now."
    ke "おいおい、落ち着けって。ほんと、お前って突っかかるよな。生徒会のアレのせいか？　あいつらとつるんでるって聞いたぞ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3647
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_5fe5c8bf:

    # hi "You heard it from me. When I told you."
    hi "俺から聞いたんだろ。お前に教えたときに"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3649
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_f14b3a41:

    # ke "Really?"
    ke "マジで？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3651
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_96dd1495:

    # ke "Yeah, well, whatever, man. The point is they are terrible."
    ke "ああ、まあ、そのなんだ。あいつらはろくでもないってことだ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3656
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_be3949f8:

    # ke "You're the new guy, so of course you wouldn't know, but around here she's a very divisive figure. Before you came here, she tried to institute a badge policy. It's a long story, so maybe you should sit down."
    ke "お前は新入りだからな、知ってるはずもないだろうけど、この辺じゃあいつはさまざまな対立の原因なんだ。お前が来る前に、あいつはバッジの着用を義務化しようとした。長い話だから、座った方がいいかもな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3658
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_1f2be48f:

    # "I look around for a chair, but can't find one as we are in a goddamn hallway. I raise a finger and start thinking that maybe I should tell him that, but he's already started talking. Not wanting to waste the arm movement, I look at my watch instead."
    "椅子がないかとあたりを見回すけど、このいまいましい廊下に立っているので１つも見あたらない。俺は指を立てて、そのことを健二に伝えるべきかと考えるけど、こいつはもう話し始めている。 せっかく腕を動かしたのを無駄にしたくないので、かわりに腕時計に目をやる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3660
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_c511c9c0:

    # ke "It would have been a real reign of terror, if it had happened."
    ke "実行されていたら、本物の恐怖政治になってただろうな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3662
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_c19eacbe:

    # hi "Wait, you're judging her based on something that didn't even happen?"
    hi "待てよ、起こりもしなかったことであいつのことを判断するっていうのか？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3666
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_2df3d6f9:

    # ke "Yes. Anyway, her idea was like merit badges, but there would also be demerit badges."
    ke "そうだよ。とにかく、あいつの案は得点バッジみたいなものだった。でも減点バッジもあったんだ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3668
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_45720725:

    # hi "What would those do?"
    hi "それが何の役に立つんだ？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3673
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_8d101d6b:

    # ke "I don't know, it never happened. It seemed bad, though, so when I heard about it I didn't leave my room for a few weeks."
    ke "知らん。一度も実施されなかったしな。でもヤバそうだったから、話を聞いたときは何週間か部屋から出なかった"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3675
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_16137d55:

    # hi "So you heard there would be massive change and hid in your room, trying to just ride the change out."
    hi "じゃあお前は何か大きな変化があると聞いて、部屋にこもって全部やり過ごそうとしたわけだ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3680
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_cd51d19b:

    # ke "Nah, I decided to do something about it. I found the student council office after a while and marched right in with a list of demands and a bunch of people I grabbed in order to make myself look like I had supporters."
    ke "いや、どうにかしようと決心したんだ。しばらくあとに生徒会室を見つけたから突撃した。要求書を持って、賛同者がいると見せかけるためにその辺の生徒をひっつかまえてな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3682
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_c239aa31:

    # hi "Wait, so not only did it not happen, but no one even cared?"
    hi "待てよ、じゃあ最初から起こりもしなかった上に、誰も気にしてなかったってことか？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3689
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_3fcd1913:

    # "Kenji doesn't hear me, having gotten a good momentum going. Wrapped up in the energy of his own ranting, he starts to completely flip out and flail his arms, appearing to wildly throw gang signs."
    "勢いが付いた健二には俺の言葉が聞こえていない。自分のわめき声のエネルギーに包まれ、完全に理性を失って腕を振り回している。まるでギャング・サインを適当にやっているみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3691
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_92ca99f2:

    # ke "I walked up to the desk and said to her, 'Hey you, fascist woman! What is this badge idea? How out of touch can you be, here in your ivory tower, smugly looking down upon us like we're just a bunch of idiots? Who do you think you are?'"
    ke "俺は机に詰め寄って、あいつに言ったんだ 『おい、このファシスト女！　なんだこのバッジ計画ってのは？　この象牙の塔で、俺たちを愚民の集まりみたいに傲慢に見下しやがって、世の中のことが全然わかってねえな！　何様のつもりだ！』"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3693
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_cc8b0b9c:

    # ke "'Your level of elitism is terrible, you're probably one of those outrageous rich people who have chaffeurs drive them around slums so they can point and laugh…'"
    ke "『エリート意識丸出しにしやがって。お前は運転手付きの車を持ってて、スラム街を運転させて、人を指さして笑うような、そういうたぐいのとんでもない金持ちに違いない……』"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3695
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_89241bbb:

    # ke "'…and only drink pricey coffee beans shat out by the last living dinosaur and brewed in a solid gold skull.'"
    ke "『……それにこの世の最後の恐竜の生き残りが排泄した高いコーヒー豆を、黄金の頭蓋骨で淹れたコーヒーしか飲まないんだろう』"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3697
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_d756b645:

    # ke "'And how could you? Go open up a history book; don't you know that the bourgeoisie are always overthrown in a bloody revolution for shit like this? Stupid! You're an idiot!'"
    ke "『そんなことができると思ってるのか？　歴史の教科書を開いてみろ。こういうクソみたいなことのおかげでブルジョアジーはいつも血塗れの革命で追放されるって知らないのか？　愚かだ！　お前はバカだ！』"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3699
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_56291e2a:

    # ke "'Sure, the revolutionaries usually end up turning everything into an utter clusterfuck later on, but a maniac is the only kind of person who would create a policy like this…'"
    ke "『確かに、革命派はたいてい何もかもどうしようもなく台無しにして終わっちまうもんだ。だがこんなルールを作るのは狂人だけだ……』"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3701
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_cfce0eb5:

    # ke "'…it's like something I would create to make people suffer, only real and you want to institutionalize it! Where will this desecration of our rights end? We are people! This is not justice!'"
    ke "『俺も民衆を苦しめるためならこんなルールを作るだろう。だがこいつは本物で、お前はそれを制度化しようとしている！』 『どこまで俺たちの権利を踏みにじろうというんだ？　俺たちは人間だ！　これは正義ではない！』"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3706
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_8f276637:

    # ke "That's what I said."
    ke "そう言ってやった"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3711
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_3e9cc050:

    # ke "Then I added a cry of 'They can take our things, but they'll never take our freeeeeedoooooom!' to appeal to the masses like in that movie about the life of William Wallace where they took his things but not his freedom, and then killed him."
    ke "んで、大衆にアピールするために『我々の持ち物は奪えても、我々の自由は奪えなあああい！』ってシュプレヒコールを上げてやった。あのウィリアム・ウォラスの映画みたいに 映画じゃ持ち物は奪われたけど自由は奪われなくて、その後殺されたけどな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3718
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_944a00d8:

    # ke "…But she just ignored me and didn't even look up from writing in her little paper shit."
    ke "……でもあいつは無視しやがった。くだらない書類書きから顔も上げやがらねえ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3720
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_b720b195:

    # ke "Maybe I overwhelmed her with my logic, so badly that she just retreated into denial. Maybe she is just an asshole. Either way, she didn't reply, and the future refused to change."
    ke "俺の理論がヤツを圧倒したのかもしれない。反論しようがなくて耳を閉ざしたんだ。あるいは、ただのろくでなしだったのかも。とにかく、あいつは答えなかったし、未来は変わることを拒んだんだ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3722
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_2af99330:

    # ke "To top it off, on the way back I realized I had lost my student ID somewhere. This is the story of my life. A constant and seemingly futile struggle. Like trying to climb up a brick wall with sponges for hands."
    ke "あげくのはてに、帰り道に学生証をどこかでなくしたことに気づいた。これが俺の人生の物語さ。絶え間ない、一見すれば無意味な戦いだ。スポンジでできた手で、レンガの壁を登るようなもんだ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3724
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_a1ab1e2e:

    # hi "Hey, you said nothing changed, but she didn't make everyone wear a bunch of stupid badges. So, it did change."
    hi "おい、何も変わらなかったっていったよな。でも静音がくだらないバッジをみんなにつけさせることはしなかったんだろ。じゃあ変わったんじゃないか"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3731
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_0513ed9d:

    # ke "Yeah, that's true. Okay, maybe they're not so bad, then."
    ke "ああ、それはそうだな。それじゃあ悪い結果じゃなかったのかもしれないな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3733
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_c72e9f02:

    # "I guess that counts for something, if I can get Kenji to admit that maybe two women may not be so bad after all. I'll take it. Especially if it allows me to slip out of this conversation; I didn't realize how much time had gone by."
    "女子２人の存在がそんなに悪いものじゃないと健二に認めさせることができたなら、それは意味のあることといえるんじゃないだろうか。 俺はそう思うことにする。この会話から脱出できるチャンスになるのだからなおさらだ。気づかない間に、ひどく長い時間が経ってしまっていた。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3740
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_b9db8298:

    # "I try to run through my usual morning routine as quickly as possible. I check my watch again as I leave the dorms and see that I'm already late."
    "できるだけ急いでいつもの朝の手順をこなす。寮を出るときに腕時計をもう一度チェックして、すでに遅刻していることに気づく。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3747
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_219a26eb:

    # "Fortunately, the rest of the day goes more smoothly, and after classes are over, I head to meet with Shizune again."
    "幸い、その後の１日は平穏に進む。授業が終わった後、再び静音に会いに向かう。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3752
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_e36c87d6:

    # "Behind the school, I catch her leaning against a completed stand with parts of it still flecked with bits of paper and tape, remnants of signs from the last time it was used. Absentmindedly spinning a nail in her hand, she hasn't noticed me yet."
    "校舎の裏で、完成した屋台に寄りかかっている静音を見つける。屋台の一部には紙切れやテープの切れ端が残っている。前に使われたときの張り紙の名残だ。 静音はぼんやりと手の中で釘を回しているけど、俺にはまだ気づいていない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3754
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_c616abab:

    # "The temptation to sneak up on her is unbearable. Years of watching foreign wildlife documentaries have prepared me for this. I'm downwind, conditions are favorable. However, the more I think about it, the more it seems like a bad idea."
    "静音にそっと忍び寄る誘惑は耐えがたい。外国の野生動物ドキュメンタリーを何年も見続けていたので、心の準備はできている。こちらは風下で、状況は理想的だ。 でも考えれば考えるほど、まずい考えなんじゃないかという気がしてくる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3756
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_f154160e:

    # "If get caught halfway I'll look like an idiot, and if she doesn't know it's me, I could end up with an injury. Either way, I'll also look a little insensitive. So, it would probably be best not to try anything funny… as disappointing as it is."
    "途中で捕まったらただのバカみたいに思われる。俺だと気づかれなかったら、こっちがけがをするかもしれない。どっちにしても、思いやりがないと思われるだろう。 やっぱり変なことはしないほうが一番いいだろう……まったく面白くないけど。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3761
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_548c44ad:

    # "I walk in front of her, startling her a little."
    "静音の正面に歩み寄ると、少しびっくりされる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3763
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_6c19e46d:

    # his "Why so surprised? Did I catch you slacking off?"
    his "何を驚いてるんだ？　さぼってるところを見つけちゃったか？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3768
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_5ff0dc60:

    # ssh "No, I was taking a break."
    ssh "違うわ、休憩してたの"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3770
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_2f2029b7:

    # his "You don't look like you even broke a sweat. That's some break there, president."
    his "汗一つかいたように見えないけどな。大した休憩じゃないか、生徒会長"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3775
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_c37f812d:

    # "Shizune's eyes dart back and forth momentarily, and I think I've managed to fluster her."
    "静音の目がしばらくあちこちに動く。どうやら動揺させることができたようだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3777
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_e5753e9e:

    # "There's exasperation on her face, and a little tension as well, but she can't back down; that would be unthinkable for her. Her fingers dance across each other impatiently."
    "怒った表情が顔に浮かぶ。すこし緊張しているのも見える。でも引き下がることはできないのだろう。静音にとっては問題外なんだ。指がいらついたように小刻みに動いている。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3782
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_3793e637:

    # ssh "You're acting competitive today. Are you trying to get my blood boiling? Do you want to make it a contest? We'll race to see who can construct the most stalls by sundown."
    ssh "今日は突っかかってくるわね。私を切れさせようとしてるの？　勝負がしたいの？　日が沈むまでにどっちがたくさん屋台を作れるか勝負よ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3784
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_4649ad08:

    # his "No, no! I'm teasing you. That's okay, it's not a real Student Council if you can't tease the Student Council president a little. You agree, don't you?"
    his "違う、違うよ！　からかっただけ。いいって、ちょっとくらい生徒会長をからかえなかったら、それは本物の生徒会じゃない。そう思うだろ、な？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3789
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_4a07e0a7:

    # ssh "That isn't in the student council charter, so it isn't true."
    ssh "生徒会の会則にはそういう決まりはないから、それはないわ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3791
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_6a633260:

    # his "There is no charter!"
    his "会則なんてないだろ！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3793
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_eb390f53:

    # "At least, I don't think there is. The only thing they pledge loyalty to are a stack of takeout menus."
    "少なくとも俺はあるとは思っていない。こいつらが忠誠を誓うのは出前メニューの山だけだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3798
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_b0175a14:

    # ssh "Anyway, it's good that you're finally here, even if you could have been earlier. Pick up a hammer and we'll resume where we left off."
    ssh "とにかく、もっと早く来られたのかもしれないけど、来てくれてよかったわ。さっさと金づちを持って。昨日やり残したところから始めるわよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3805
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_98b03cb8:

    # "As we work assembling stalls again, I slowly realize that it's really much less work than I would have expected. In fact, according to Shizune, we should be done by the end of the day with a little luck."
    "また屋台の組み立てにとりかかりながら、思っていたよりも仕事の量がずっと少ないことにだんだん気づき始める。それどころか静音によれば、運が良ければ今日中には終わってしまうらしい。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3807
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_0bd50985:

    # "The last time I did something like this for them, it took her, Misha, and myself almost four days to do it. It can't be just my imagination."
    "この前に同じような作業をしたときは、静音、ミーシャ、そして俺でほぼ丸４日かかった。俺の思い過ごしなわけがない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3811
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_a5b3a604:

    # his "You know, this doesn't seem like that much work."
    his "なあ、これってあまり大した作業量に見えないぞ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3816
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_655246a8:

    # ssh "Because it isn't."
    ssh "大した量じゃないからよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3820
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_9a182232:

    # "That answer leaves me wanting a little more. Knowing that it isn't the best, Shizune puts down her hammer to elaborate."
    "その答えを聞いて、もう少し詳しく聞きたくなる。良くはないと知りつつ、静音はハンマーを置いて説明する。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3825
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_3c54f7e8:

    # ssh "It would be impossible for two people to do that much work in less than a week. The truth is that I don't dismantle half the stalls, I just store them someplace else. Actually, more like I hide them in plain sight."
    ssh "１週間足らずで、たった２人でこれだけの作業をこなすのは不可能よ。ほんとのことを言うと、最初から屋台の半分は解体せずにしまっておいたの。しまうというより、その辺に隠しておいたってところかな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3830
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_dee46a47:

    # "She waggles a finger mischievously."
    "静音はいたずらっぽく指を振る。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3835
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_c3369c8e:

    # ssh "But that's a secret, and it's not proper to reveal the tricks of the trade."
    ssh "でも今のは秘密だからね。それに商売の秘訣をばらすのは不作法よ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3837
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_b6c39d27:

    # his "You're not a magician."
    his "お前はマジシャンじゃないからな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3842
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_7cdde7d9:

    # "Winking, she takes out two plastic containers from her bag, then puts them down on a nearby board before raising her hands slightly as if to say 'ta-da!'"
    "ウィンクしながら、静音はかばんからプラスチックの容器を２つ取りだし、手近な板の上に置くと、『ジャジャーン！』とでも言うかのように両手を少し持ち上げる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3847
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_bcbc7022:

    # ssh "I made lunch today for both of us."
    ssh "今日はお弁当を２人分作ってきたの"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3852
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_6515fe1b:

    # ssh "You can have this one. The food shifted in my bag and now some of it is mixed together."
    ssh "こっちを食べて。かばんの中で中身が片寄って、少し混ざっちゃったから"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3854
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_41f22558:

    # "She hands me one of the containers. I open it. It looks delicious, if a little simple. She hands me a pair of chopsticks, as if she had just remembered to, and I eat what looks like some grilled beef."
    "静音が弁当箱を１つ渡してくれる。それを開けてみる。とてもおいしそうだ。たった今思い出したかのように、静音は箸も渡してくれる。牛焼き肉に見える何かを俺は口に運ぶ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3856
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_cb83c917:

    # his "It's very tasty."
    his "すごくおいしいぞ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3858
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_944da5f0:

    # his "You don't like your food touching other food?"
    his "食べ物がほかの食べ物に触れるのは好きじゃないのか？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3863
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_e181d0f7:

    # ssh "I do not."
    ssh "好きじゃない"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3865
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_3061a233:

    # his "You're very picky."
    his "ずいぶん細かいんだな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3870
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_bc98c103:

    # ssh "Sometimes I mix my food on my own, but not always, and not everything. I don't like it when it's done for me. What is important is the choice."
    ssh "自分で食べ物を混ぜることもあるけど、いつもじゃないし、何もかも混ぜるわけじゃない。勝手に混ざるのはいやなの。自分が選んでそうしてるってことが大事なのよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3875
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_2b40fc27:

    # "She points decisively to emphasize it, and then breaks her chopsticks apart to eat her own meal."
    "断固たる態度で指をさして力説すると、静音は割り箸を割って自分の弁当を食べ始める。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3877
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_c4b4933b:

    # "As I continue to eat, I notice two things. The first is that almost everything I'm eating besides the rice is fried. Even the vegetables are fried."
    "食べ続けながら、俺は２つのことに気づく。１つは、ご飯をのぞけば食べ物のほぼ全部が炒め物だということだ。野菜まで炒めてある。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3879
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_47351c4f:

    # "And there's so much meat. Does she eat this kind of stuff all the time? I wonder how she manages to stay so thin in spite of it."
    "そして肉があまりにも多い。静音はいつもこんな食事をしているのか？　これでどうやってあんなに細い体でいられるんだろう。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3881
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_2b156415:

    # "The second thing I notice is that I can't talk to her while eating. Talking with your mouth full is a little rude anyway, but with our hands holding our chopsticks and bowls, communication between us is impossible. Just like yesterday."
    "２つ目は、食べている間は静音と話せないことだ。口の中いっぱいに食べ物を含んだまましゃべるのはそもそも不作法だけど、両手が箸と器でふさがっていると、俺たち２人が会話をするのは不可能だ。昨日のように。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3883
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_f6c0fe44:

    # "Even though we're spending time together, even though I took the time to learn sign language, it feels like I'm talking to her less. Despite that, it also feels like I'm understanding her more."
    "一緒に過ごしているのに、時間をかけて手話を身につけたのに、静音と話をする時間は少なくなっている感じがする。それなのに、俺は静音のことをもっと理解できているような気がする。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3894
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_250927df:

    # "I hear the sound of something tapping against one of the stands and look up to see Lilly standing off to my side, feeling her way around with her cane."
    "何かが屋台の１つをこつこつと叩く音が聞こえる。目を上げるとリリーが俺のそばに立っていて、杖であたりを探っているのが見える。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3896
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_ca61152d:

    # hi "Hi."
    hi "やあ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3898
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_aa751679:

    # "I narrowly catch myself before I can say 'didn't see you there.'"
    "『見落とすところだったよ』と言いそうになるのを危ういところでこらえる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3903
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_08ab3479:

    # li "Oh, Hisao, is that you? I thought that I smelled something delicious cooking, and wondered who it might be."
    li "あら、久夫さんですか？　なんだかおいしい料理を作っている匂いがしたので、誰だろうって思ってたんですよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3908
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_338f5925:

    # ssh "What is she saying?"
    ssh "なんて言ってるの？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3912
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_36bd6000:

    # "It's hard to move my hands in parallel to saying something completely different to Lilly. This has to be why Misha just signs everything all the time. A bit sillier, but it seems like it would simplify things a lot."
    "手を動かしながら、まったく別の言葉をリリーに話すのは大変だ。だからミーシャはいつも全部の会話を手話にしているに違いない。ちょっとおかしな感じがするけど、そのほうがずっと簡単そうだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3917
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_289ff81a:

    # "Shizune tents her fingers delightedly at my translation, as if from hearing a joke."
    "静音は俺の通訳を見て、ジョークを聞いたかのようにうれしそうに指を合わせる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3922
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_5095d472:

    # ssh "All of this food was cooked hours ago, but for someone as slow as yourself, who can't even turn in a piece of paper without being a week late, I guess your perception of time would have to be a little different!"
    ssh "ここにある食べ物は全部一時間前に作ったの。一週間過ぎても紙切れ一枚提出できない誰かさんと違ってね。きっとあんたの時間のとらえ方はちょっとずれてるんでしょうね！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3924
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_70756512:

    # hi "That's… not very nice."
    hi "それは……ちょっとひどくないか"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3929
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_aff01e36:

    # "A frown crosses Lilly's face in response to a reply to something she didn't hear."
    "自分が耳にしなかった言葉への返事を聞いて、リリーがふと眉を寄せる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3931
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_3b770e0f:

    # hi "Ah, sorry. I'm just having a late lunch here. The Student Council president cooked everything."
    hi "ああ、悪い。遅い昼飯を食べてるところでさ。全部生徒会長が作ったんだ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3936
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_a699faea:

    # li "Is the Student Council president here right now?"
    li "生徒会長も今ここにいるんですか？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3938
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_b397b7a4:

    # hi "She's right here."
    hi "すぐそこにいるよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3943
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_57afcee2:

    # li "I apologize, I didn't notice. Normally her level of presence is much higher. I was not aware that the Student Council serves lunch outdoors, why wasn't I invited? I think that it is good to have enough free time to be able to do things like this, however."
    li "失礼しました、気づきませんでした。普段なら彼女の存在感はずっと目立つんですけどね しかし生徒会が屋外でお昼を振る舞うなんて知りませんでした。どうして私は招待されなかったんですか？　でもこんなことをするくらい自由な時間があるというのは、いいことだと思います"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3948
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_338f5925_1:

    # ssh "What is she saying?"
    ssh "なんて言ってるの？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3950
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3955
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_16024e57:

    # ssh "If I were to invite you anywhere, you would just show up late."
    ssh "私があんたを招待したところで、どうせ遅れてくるくせに"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3957
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_72fcb4bd:

    # "But Shizune's words are outside of Lilly's perception, a fact that is by the second increasingly maddening to her."
    "でも静音の言葉をリリーは認識することができない。その事実がますます静音の怒りをつのらせる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3962
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_a035d1dd:

    # ssh "Translate for me completely, please."
    ssh "ちゃんと一字一句訳してちょうだい。お願い"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3964
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_c18335ef:

    # "What polite phrasing. It's a shame she's essentially asking me to let her fully release the dogs of war. Still, I can't just do nothing. The feeling of being unable to even respond and be understood is so isolating. She would never forgive me."
    "やけに丁寧な言葉遣いだな。自分の怒りをぶつけてくれと俺に頼むなんて、実に残念な話だ。 それでも、俺だって何もしないわけにはいかない。返事をして自分の考えを理解してもらうことさえできないなんて、寂しすぎる。静音は絶対に許してくれないだろう。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3966
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_56405d26:

    # "I'll just try to soften her words a little."
    "少しだけ言葉を柔らかくしようとしてみる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3968
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_a2288f0c:

    # hi "Well, actually, this was all cooked a while ago."
    hi "まあ、ほんとのこというと、みんな何時間か前に作ったものなんだ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3973
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_cd038d3b:

    # li "Really? That's nice."
    li "本当ですか？　いいですね"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3978
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_33dcc3b1:

    # ssh "Turn over here, it's very disrespectful to not look at the person you're speaking to. That isn't the way a prim and proper lady should conduct herself."
    ssh "こっちを向きなさいよ、話している相手にちゃんと向き合わないのはすごく失礼よ。上品で礼儀正しいレディの振る舞い方じゃないでしょう"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3980
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_5039ad6c:

    # hi "Half of what I'm saying is really what Shizune is saying. She doesn't like it when people don't look in her direction when she's trying to make a point. She's, uh, to the right of my voice."
    hi "俺の言ってることは静音の言葉の半分くらいなんだけど。静音は自分が話しているときに相手が自分の方を向いていないのはいやなんだって。静音なら、その、俺の声の右側にいるよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3982
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_d3f8881b:

    # "Although in this case I can understand why Lilly wouldn't. This is a very awkward situation and it's daunting being the sole conduit for dialogue between the two of them."
    "とはいえ、こういう状況ではリリーがそうしないのもわかる。状況は非常に気まずくて、２人の会話の唯一の接点役をつとめるのはとても気疲れする。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3984
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_f4133ee1:

    # "Truthfully, I had forgotten what happened the last time they butted heads like this. It's clear Shizune remembers, and Lilly is being pretty hostile herself, in her own way."
    "実は、以前こうやって２人が衝突したときのことを度忘れしてしまっていた。静音が根に持っているのは明らかだし、リリーも彼女なりに敵意をむき出しにしている。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3989
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_25dcd29e:

    # li "I'm sorry, such formalities slipped my mind completely. I forgot that the Student Council president is the type of person who would demand such respect and adherence to the rules at all times."
    li "ごめんなさい、そういうお作法はすっかり頭から抜けてしまっていました。生徒会長がいついかなるときも尊敬とルール厳守を求めるような人だってこと、忘れてしまってました"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3994
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_93c2752c:

    # li "I suppose student government requires you to keep a tight ship. Then again, she certainly has time for her own fun as well, so that must not be completely true."
    li "生徒会はみんなに厳しい統制を要求するんでしょうね。とはいっても、見るからにご自分のお楽しみの時間もあるようですし、常にそういうわけではないんでしょうけど"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:3999
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_645959c2:

    # ssh "Student Council is not a dictatorship, nor a zero-sum game!"
    ssh "生徒会は独裁じゃないし、ゼロサムゲームでもない！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4003
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_a7360478:

    # "Shizune points at Lilly with her finger out like the barrel of a gun and snaps her fingers explosively, causing her to flinch and become visibly upset."
    "静音は指先を銃身のようにリリーに突きだして、大きな音で指を鳴らす。リリーは一瞬ひるんで、明らかに不機嫌そうになる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4009
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_e376da07:

    # li "Is that so? Then that makes it more impressive that you have been a part of it for so long, playing it as though it were one. I admire the fact that you are so tenacious. To manage it all, you must be so responsible as well."
    li "そうですか？　ではこんなに長い間生徒会に入って、独裁者みたいに振る舞っていることになおさら感心しますね。そのしつこさには感服します。万事うまくやるには、とても責任感が強くないといけませんから"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4014
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_f21a3e4c:

    # ssh "Not as much as I would like to be. You can't complain about yourself, though, can you?"
    ssh "自分がそうありたいほどじゃないわ。あんただって自分のことは文句言えないんじゃないの？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4019
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_b468efc0:

    # ssh "You're very responsible; actions like requesting a deadline to be extended and then running all the way through to the next deadline? That's the very model of responsibility!"
    ssh "あんたも責任感は強いわね。締め切りを延ばしてくれって頼んで、その延ばした締め切りぎりぎりまで仕事を引っ張ったり？　責任感の模範よね！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4021
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_72811f86:

    # hi "Shizune is happy to hear that. But, apparently you're pretty responsible yourself, she says."
    hi "静音はそれ聞いて喜んでるよ。でも、リリーも結構責任感あるよねって言ってるみたい"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4027
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_c6616c9e:

    # li "Does she really?"
    li "本当ですか？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4029
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_21bc48ec:

    # hi "More or less…"
    hi "大体はね……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4031
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_0783f076:

    # "Lilly doesn't seem very happy."
    "リリーはあまりうれしくなさそうだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4033
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_b826bc48:

    # hi "We're not holding a cookout, we're just taking a little lunch break. We're actually out here building stalls for the festival."
    hi "俺たち野外料理会をしてるわけじゃないんだ。ただの昼休みだよ。実は今度のお祭りの屋台を組み立ててるんだ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4038
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_a7b23c0d:

    # ssh "You wouldn't know, since you never go outside. Did you run out of tea?"
    ssh "あんたは知らないでしょうね、絶対外出なんてしないだろうから。紅茶でも切らしたの？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4040
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_ab083890:

    # hi "Are you going into town? Shopping?"
    hi "町に行くの？　買い物？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4046
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_14365b59:

    # li "No. As I said before, I was just passing by, in case you did not hear. I would hate to interrupt the Student Council president. You're not doing anything now, but you must both be very busy."
    li "いえ。さっきも言いましたけど、通りかかっただけです。聞こえていなかったようですね。生徒会長の邪魔をしたくはありません。今は何もしていないけれど、きっと２人ともとてもお忙しいんでしょう"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4052
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_5291800a:

    # li "In any case, Hisao, I'm sure that the Student Council president will be able to find or make work for the both of you if she needs to."
    li "とにかく、久夫さん、必要があれば生徒会長はきっと仕事を見つけるなり思いつくなりしてくれると思いますよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4057
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_f236f00d:

    # ssh "I'll devour you!"
    ssh "ギッタギタにしてやる！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4059
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_85910286:

    # hi "Yeah, very busy."
    hi "そうだな、すごい忙しくなるよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4061
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_ef7de013:

    # "'Devour' is a hard word. I'm pleased that I can read it. This isn't time to celebrate, though, not over that. Instead, it looks like they might stop squabbling. I would drink to that."
    "『ギッタギタ』は難しい言葉だ。自分にも読めたのがうれしい。そんなことに喜んでいる場合ではないけど。ただ、これで２人の言い争いは終わりそうだ。これには祝杯をあげたっていい。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4066
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_c57b0765:

    # li "Have a nice day, Hisao. Goodbye, Student Council president."
    li "ごきげんよう、久夫さん。さよなら、生徒会長"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4068
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_1a79c612:

    # hi "Thanks, you too."
    hi "ありがと、リリーもな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4073
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_49e3b195:

    # ssh "Stay classy."
    ssh "お上品ぶってなさい"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4084
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_5e3dc947:

    # "As soon as Lilly leaves, Shizune dives into the remains of her lunch as quickly as possible, as if each bite she shovels away is a means to forgetting any of this ever happened."
    "リリーが去ったとたん、静音は弁当の残りを全速力でかきこむ。まるでその一口一口が、今の出来事が最初から起きなかったがごとく忘却に追いやる手段であるかのように。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4089
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_6d47d1c6:

    # "When she is done, she heads right back to hammering with the same mindset. It's good that she's working off her frustration, but now it doesn't look like she is in any mood to talk any more."
    "食べ終わると、静音は同じ精神状態を保ったまま組み立て作業に舞い戻る。いらだちを仕事で発散しているのはいいことだけど、もう話をするような気分ではないようだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4096
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_3b71a08f:

    # "About two hours later, she stops, having mowed through the rest of the stalls nonstop in that time."
    "休むことなしにすべての屋台を片づけ、二時間ほどして静音は手を止める。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4098
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_a6b00fdc:

    # "It still feels hard to approach her, and I think about how easily a conversation can die. After it took so long to be able to get her alone and speak to her directly, it almost hurts."
    "まだ静音には近寄りづらい気がする。会話というのはあっけなく終わってしまうものなんだな。二人きりになって直接話ができるようになるまでこんなに時間がかかったというのに、つらい気持ちになってくる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4103
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_9d05dc72:

    # ssh "Your translation was good."
    ssh "翻訳、上手だったわ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4105
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_bc383121:

    # his "Really?"
    his "ほんとか？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4110
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_301fccb9:

    # ssh "First class!"
    ssh "一流よ！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4112
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_f1bde3f2:

    # "She punctuates it with a thumbs up."
    "静音はサムズアップで強調する。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4117
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_fb78d173:

    # ssh "…For your level."
    ssh "……あなたのレベルにしてはね"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4122
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_44e3b107:

    # ssh "There aren't many deaf people in the school, and sign language classes have been on the edge of getting cut for a while now. I'm sure you don't have many classmates, am I right?"
    ssh "学校には聾の生徒は多くないし、手話のクラスはずいぶん前から閉鎖されそうになってる。クラスメイトだってあまり多くないでしょう、違う？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4127
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_d8b68fbd:

    # ssh "If you're only learning sign language now, your speed is going to be limited. That is why interest in it wanes, because it takes more effort than normal just to communicate. I imagine it's the same with all languages."
    ssh "今手話を習っているだけだったら、速度はあまり伸びないの。だから興味もなくなってしまう。単にコミュニケーションを取るだけでも、普通よりもたくさんの労力が必要だから。どんな言語でも同じことだろうけど"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4132
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_c36e0e52:

    # ssh "In such a situation, conversations in sign language are less … than they would inherently be to start with."
    ssh "こういう状況だと、そもそも手話による会話は本来の……なものではなくなってしまう"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4134
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_45e931e2:

    # his "I don't understand that word. Less what?"
    his "今の単語わからなかったぞ。何じゃなくなるって？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4142
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_c0eb8b48:

    # ssh "Sp—{w=0.2}on—{w=0.2}ta—{w=0.2}ne—{w=0.2}ou—{w=0.2}s."
    ssh "じ—{w=0.2}は—{w=0.2}つ—{w=0.2}て—{w=0.2}き—{w=0.2}な"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4147
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_cd743631:

    # ssh "Misha is the only person who can really capture it."
    ssh "これを本当にとらえることができるのはミーシャだけよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4149
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_a839e7b4:

    # his "Yeah, that's definitely true."
    his "ああ、それは間違いないな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4157
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_710c6f81:

    # "Her expression changes for a second, and changes back too quickly to digest, but I get the feeling that this isn't meant to be pursued."
    "一瞬だけ静音の表情が変わり、それを理解する前にあっという間に元に戻る。でもそれを追及してはいけないんだろうという気がする。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4159
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_c6ea559a:

    # "What I really want to know about is…"
    "俺が本当に知りたいのは……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4161
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_43965cc3:

    # his "Why do you and Lilly fight so much?"
    his "どうしてリリーとそんなにけんかするんだ？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4166
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_58448d4d:

    # "Tensing a little and visibly frowning, Shizune tents her fingers and overlays them repeatedly as if shuffling an invisible deck of cards."
    "体を堅くして、見るからに顔をしかめ、静音は何度も両手の指を合わせたり重ねたりする。目に見えないトランプをシャッフルするかのようだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4171
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_f613d40e:

    # ssh "Two fights that you know of aren't worth calling 'so much.' If you had been here last year you could say that."
    ssh "あなたが見た２回は、『そんなに』というほどたいしたものじゃないわ。去年学校にいたなら、そういう言い方もできるでしょうね"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4173
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_13fc588e:

    # his "I heard it was a rough year. Something about how you tried to institute a badge policy."
    his "大変だったらしいな。校則でバッジをつけさせようとしたとかなんとか"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4178
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_8491f64f:

    # his "Ha ha, surprised? Well, I want to hear more about that later, definitely, but… you don't like Lilly very much, do you? Don't dodge my question."
    his "はは、驚いたか？　その件は後で聞かせて欲しいけど、マジで、でも……お前、リリーのことあまり好きじゃないんだろ？　はぐらかすなよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4183
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_3fe11616:

    # ssh "I'm not dodging anything."
    ssh "何もはぐらかしてなんかないわ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4188
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_d2005d09:

    # ssh "She was part of the Student Council until last year. We didn't get along very well. She wanted to keep doing things like the old Student Council did. The old Student Council was just so ineffectual. It was stupid, and insulting."
    ssh "リリーも去年まで生徒会に所属してたの。お互いあまりうまが合わなかった。リリーは前の生徒会と同じように物事を進めようとした。前の生徒会は本当に無能だった。バカだったし、失礼だった"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4193
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_26980c35:

    # ssh "I wanted to do more, and we had a fight."
    ssh "私はもっと多くのことがしたかった。それでけんかになったの"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4198
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_06d613f3:

    # ssh "A lot of fights."
    ssh "いっぱいけんかをした"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4203
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_c9d5f0ed:

    # ssh "She couldn't do anything on time."
    ssh "リリーはいつも締め切りを守らなかった"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4208
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_e4fc9f64:

    # ssh "Then, she said that what I wanted to do was meaningless, just extra busywork. Does this look like meaningless busywork to you?"
    ssh "そしたら、私がやっていることは無意味な、ただのよけいな時間つぶしだって言ってきた。これが意味のない暇つぶしに見える？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4210
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_698a0c97:

    # "Shizune gestures around us."
    "静音は俺たちのまわりを手振りで示す。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4215
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_68872c36:

    # ssh "What's really meaningless is a Student Council that doesn't do anything. Weak, lazy, and boring. Especially boring!"
    ssh "無意味なのは何もしない生徒会の方よ。無力で、怠惰で、退屈な。とびきり退屈！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4220
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_3ede13fd:

    # ssh "I couldn't get excited over sitting in a room with nothing to do, that's just a waste of time. Why would I even be there? It didn't get my blood flowing. Arguing with her does that!"
    ssh "何もしないで部屋に座ってても心は躍らないのよ。そんなのただの時間の無駄。どうしてそんなとこにいなきゃいけないの？　それじゃ私の血はたぎらない。リリーと言い争うと私の血はたぎるのよ！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4225
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_73ac3247:

    # ssh "If she could have been that motivated before, she wouldn't have to put so much dedication into being my enemy. But if she shows that much spirit, it's not a complete loss. At least it's something! It's still exciting."
    ssh "あのときあれだけリリーがやる気を出していたなら、今こんなに熱心に私につっかかる必要もなかったのに でもあれだけの気合いを見せているなら、全くの無駄じゃない。少なくとも何かは残ったわけだし！　まだ心は躍るわね"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4227
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_d6fe8821:

    # his "I see."
    his "なるほどな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4229
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_3a392638:

    # his "And what about the badge thing?"
    his "それでバッジの話は？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4236
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_9e0c10c8:

    # "She laughs, covering her mouth with her hand as if to hide it. Her laughter is the only thing she regularly tries to hide."
    "静音は笑う。その笑いを隠すかのように手で口を覆っている。自分の笑いだけは、静音がいつも隠そうとする唯一のものだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4241
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_85e92070:

    # ssh "That was just a joke."
    ssh "あんなの、ただの冗談よ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4246
translate jp a2_shizune_spring_into_action_8835c2e0:

    # ssh "Having a little fun sometimes is important, too."
    ssh "時にはお楽しみも大事なのよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4264
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_a00c6551:

    # "The next day, I end up having to hunt around a bit at the start of lunch when I find that my usual vending machine near the dormitory buildings is sold out of my usual favorite canned coffee. The detour takes longer than I expected."
    "翌日、寮舎の近くの自販機でいつも買っているお気に入りの缶コーヒーが売り切れていて、昼休みの始めにあちこち探して回る羽目になった。思ったよりも長い回り道になってしまった。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4269
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_774a9927:

    # "Things have been so hectic lately that it takes some time for me to register why something smells different as I walk through the school gardens back to the cafeteria. The grass has been freshly mowed."
    "最近は何もかも忙しすぎて、校庭を歩きながら普段と違う匂いがする理由に気づくのにもしばらく時間がかかる。芝刈りが行われたばかりだった。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4271
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_e3103454:

    # "The realization makes me pause and watch for a bit. The odd group of students chatting or playing around on the grass and a couple of teachers conversing on the path ahead make for a very idyllic scene."
    "しばらく立ち止まってあたりを眺める。生徒のグループがいくつかいて、おしゃべりをしたり、芝生の上で遊んでいたりする。その先の小道で先生たちが数人話し合っている。とても牧歌的な光景だ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4275
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_1417a48e:

    # "Unfortunately, a feeling of imminent dread starts creeping up on me after a while. The feeling that I'm not alone."
    "残念なことに、しばらくして恐怖が間近に迫っている感覚が体に這い登ってくる。自分が一人じゃないという感覚が。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4282
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_77478a80:

    # ke "Hey, Hisao, is that you?"
    ke "よう、久夫、お前か？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4284
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_5f766ea9:

    # hi "Yeah, it's me."
    hi "ああ、俺だよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4286
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_b820ef16:

    # "I guess I should be happy it's him and not, say, a slasher. Kenji begins talking as if he's having a conversation with someone other than me."
    "こいつが切り裂き魔か何かじゃなくて健二だったことに感謝すべきなんだろう。まるで俺以外の誰かと会話しているかのように、健二は話し始める。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4291
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_171ad753:

    # ke "Knew it. That haircut is unmistakable. No normal person would have a haircut like that."
    ke "やっぱり。その髪型、間違えようがないぜ。普通の人なら絶対そんな頭しないからな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4293
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_21554ddc:

    # "Unconsciously, I start touching the back of my head. Once I realize what I'm doing, I feel insulted, yet too surprised to even get indignant about it."
    "無意識に俺は後頭部に手をやる。自分のやっていることに気づいて、俺はバカにされた気分になると同時に、腹も立たないくらい驚愕する。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4295
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_4502d81d:

    # hi "Yeah… What are you doing here?"
    hi "ああ……ここで何してるんだ？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4300
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_4785dd11:

    # ke "Measuring the temperature."
    ke "気温を計ってる"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4305
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_150d10f0:

    # ke "Winter will come soon. It will be too cold for women to go out and have their Sex and the City-style power lunches, followed by obstructive human wave formation walks in crowded urban areas."
    ke "もうすぐ冬がくる。女どもが外出してセックス・アンド・ザ・シティ式のパワーランチを食べて、人が一杯の都市部で邪魔くさい群れをなして並んで歩くには寒すぎる時期になる"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4307
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_8fe97495:

    # ke "When this happens, man will be able to walk the streets unfettered once again, and reclaim what is his heritage."
    ke "すると、男たちはふたたびのびのびと通りを歩くことができるようになる。自分たちの遺産を取り戻すことができるんだ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4312
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_08f13daa:

    # ke "In order to prepare for that day, I've been eating nothing but pizzas for the past week, to store energy."
    ke "その日が来たときに備えて、俺はこの一週間ピザしか食べてないんだ。エネルギーを蓄積するためにな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4314
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_16a7dec2:

    # hi "Okay."
    hi "そっか"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4316
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_56ea7df5:

    # hi "That's what bears do."
    hi "熊もそういうことするよな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4321
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_b895cc21:

    # ke "So? There is much we can learn from the bear."
    ke "それがなんだよ？　熊から学べることはたくさんあるんだぞ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4323
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_d172b0bd:

    # "Kenji nods, emphatically agreeing with himself."
    "健二は自分自身に同意するように、力強くうなずく。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4328
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_70307f2d:

    # ke "Okay, so check this shit out: I was in town today, buying milk. They had a new clerk, some hipster girl with a baseball cap with two hockey sticks on it. I'll call her hipster hockey baseball hat girl."
    ke "よし、じゃあこれはどうだ。今日、ミルクを買いに町に出た。新しい店員がいたんだ。ホッケースティックが２本描いてある野球帽をかぶってる格好付けてそうな女子だ。これを格好つけホッケー野球帽女子と呼ぼう"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4330
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_aae65c99:

    # ke "I noticed the milk didn't have a price tag, so I told her to get over there and label that milk, for future generations."
    ke "ミルクに値札がついてないことに気づいて、その女子にこっちに来て値札をつけろと言ったんだ。将来の世代のためにな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4332
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_02ea1777:

    # "He was in town today? He must have cut his morning classes. I want to scold him, but his verbal torrent prevents me from getting a word in."
    "今日町に行ってたって？　朝の授業をさぼったに違いない。どやしつけてやりたいけど、こいつの言葉の奔流にさえぎられて、割り込むことができない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4337
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_0a516632:

    # ke "She told me not to bother her, because she was sick. Sick? Sick!? We live in a society, here. You can't just opt out of human interaction because you're sick. Do you know how much effort it takes me to even get up in the morning?"
    ke "その女、自分は気分が悪いから邪魔するなと言ってきたんだ。気分が悪い？　気分が悪いだと！？　俺たちは社会生活してるんだぞ。気分が悪いくらいで人同士のコミュニケーションから逃れられると思ってるのか 今朝起きるだけで俺がどれだけの労力を費やしたと思ってるんだ？　今だって労力を費やしてるんだがな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4342
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_34741a94:

    # ke "I still do, though, and I got up that morning to go down there and buy milk, not to have my vital questions just brushed aside by some hipster doofus college girl who wears a {b}hockey baseball cap{/b} to work. {b}Indoors{/b}."
    ke "こっちは仕事中に{b}ホッケー野球帽{/b}を、しかも{b}屋内で{/b}かぶってる勘違いオシャレ女子大生ごときに重要な質問をシカトされるために、わざわざ朝っぱらからミルクを買いに行ったわけじゃないんだよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4347
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_7cf5d67d:

    # ke "Anyway, I was just trying to uphold the integrity of her products. A milk carton without a price tag? When I see something like that, it just leads to questions. Important questions. It's her job to answer them, dammit."
    ke "とにかく、俺は店の品物をきちんとさせたかっただけだ。値札の付いてないミルク？　そんなもの見つけたら、疑問がわいてくるだけだ。それも重要な疑問だ。答えるのがその女の仕事だろうが、ったく"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4349
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_1dd1922e:

    # ke "That's the problem with women, they have no sense of duty."
    ke "女ってやつはこれだから困る。義務感ってものがない"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4354
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_8b89f416:

    # ke "I get diarrhea a lot, but you don't see me complaining about it. I soldier on and do what I have to do anyway, because that's what being a man is all about. Even if you have diarrhea, you keep going, for the dream of a better tomorrow."
    ke "俺、よく下痢するんだ。でも文句を言ったりしてないだろ。俺はとにかく困難に耐えて、やるべきことをやるんだ。男ってのはそういうものなんだよ。下痢してたって、前に進み続けるんだ。よりよい明日を夢見て"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4356
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_f25ea576:

    # hi "You know, frequent diarrhea is bad."
    hi "あのさ、しょっちゅう下痢するってのは良くないと思うぞ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4358
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_9359986e:

    # hi "Maybe you should stop drinking so much milk."
    hi "そんなにミルク飲むのやめた方がいいんじゃないか"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4360
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_60786fc1:

    # ke "I can't do that, it's what allows me to maintain my awesome strength. And in this world… a man's strength is the only thing that can't be browbeaten out of him by an increasingly pussywhipped society."
    ke "そんなことできるかよ、そのおかげで今の超絶パワーを保ってるんだぞ。それにこの世界では……女の尻に敷かれる男がどんどん増えている社会で、男の力ってのは絶対に奪うことのできない唯一のものなんだ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4365
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_2a48fb2b:

    # ke "That's why I walk around leaving open jars of olives everywhere. Sometimes just to show that I can."
    ke "だから俺はあっちこっちにふたを開けたオリーブのビン詰めを放置しているんだ。そういうことができるんだってことを示すために"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4367
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_e5636d2e:

    # hi "Do you refrigerate after opening?"
    hi "開けた後は冷蔵庫に入れてるか？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4372
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_3a6edbd5:

    # ke "What? Man, I don't know, that's not important."
    ke "はあ？　そんな、知るかよ、どうだっていいだろ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4374
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_58c82162:

    # hi "You have to refrigerate after opening. Even elementary school kids know that."
    hi "開けた後は要冷蔵だろ。小学生のガキだって知ってるぞ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4379
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_09b1b3aa:

    # ke "They can't get the jar open in the first place, so it doesn't matter."
    ke "奴らはそもそもビンのふたも開けられないから、関係ない"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4381
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_1c7ef1cd:

    # hi "Ah, that's true."
    hi "ああ、それはそうだな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4386
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_a628ba23:

    # ke "I'm a genius."
    ke "俺って天才だろ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4388
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_375f283c:

    # "He self-assuredly rubs his chin, which is something I imagined scientists did, until I met Mutou and was tremendously let down."
    "満足げにあごをなでる。俺はそれが科学者のするしぐさだとばかり思っていた。そして武藤先生に会ってから、ひどくがっかりする羽目になった。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4393
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_6695b4dd:

    # ke "Anyway, I can't go to that store again, since it's clearly been compromised by bitches. Unless… I disguise myself. Maybe change to a different pair of glasses."
    ke "とにかく、もうあの店には行けない。明らかにビッチどもが幅を利かせてるからな。ただ……変装すれば話は別だ。別の眼鏡をかけるとか"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4395
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_ed2182d6:

    # hi "Worst disguise ever."
    hi "史上最悪だ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4400
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_ccb9e47e:

    # ke "Pffft, it's been working flawlessly all these years. I don't even need glasses to see. They're for effect. Also, to protect my identity. I'm like Superman."
    ke "ぷー、もう何年も完璧に通用してますぅー。そもそも眼鏡なんてなくたって目は見えるんだよ。これは見た目のためだ。それと顔を隠すために。スーパーマンみたいだろ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4402
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_ed2182d6_1:

    # hi "Worst disguise ever."
    hi "史上最悪だ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4407
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_ab7e237d:

    # ke "I'm telling you, when people see my school ID, they can't even recognize me."
    ke "いっとくけどな、人が俺の学生証見ても、俺だってわからないんだぜ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4409
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_c863c420:

    # hi "Really? Let me see."
    hi "ほんとか？　見せてみろよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4414
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_11c22b39:

    # ke "Can't do that. I can't go around showing my ID to everyone. It was made long ago. In a different time. I had hippie hair."
    ke "それはだめだ。誰彼構わず学生証を見せびらかすわけにはいかないんだよ。大昔に作ったんだ。時代が違うんだよ。ヒッピーみたいな髪型だったんだ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4418
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_79fdadf0:

    # "While I'm trying to imagine that, Kenji takes his glasses off."
    "その様子を想像しようとしていると、健二は眼鏡を外す。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4433
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_d9e21376:

    # "He squints as soon as they're off his face, which makes him look even more tired than he already does. He was right; he does look very different. Kind of like he hasn't slept in years. Not different enough for it to be a good disguise, though."
    "眼鏡を外したとたんに健二は目を細める。おかげで実際よりもずっと疲れているように見える。 健二の言うとおりだった。確かにとても違って見える。もう何年も寝ていないかのようだ。でも、うまい変装と呼べるほどの違いじゃない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4435
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_5636c97b:

    # hi "You need more sleep."
    hi "お前よく寝てないんじゃないか"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4440
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_cec583aa:

    # ke "Nah."
    ke "いや"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4442
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_be601a1c:

    # hi "You look like you need it."
    hi "寝不足っぽいぞ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4447
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_2d277b09:

    # ke "No way. These are just the eyes of a man who has seen things. A shaman's eyes. Terrible things, that you can't imagine."
    ke "んなわけあるか。これは真実を目撃した男の目だ。シャーマンの目だよ。想像もつかないような、ひどいことだ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4449
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_42f3c1fc:

    # ke "Like when I made a ship in a bottle and my mom sat on it. There was blood and shreds of floral print everywhere. That's what life experience is."
    ke "ボトルシップを作ったら母ちゃんが上に座ったときみたいに。そこら中が血と花柄の布切れだらけだった。人生経験ってのはそういうもんだ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4451
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_66f4960c:

    # "Kenji doesn't seem very horrified, even though I think this is actually the first thing he told me about himself that could have been legitimately traumatic."
    "健二が正真正銘のトラウマになりそうな過去の経験を話してくれたのはこれが初めてだと思う。でもあまり恐ろしがっている風には見えない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4453
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_bf52f4b5:

    # "He's also talking about thirty degrees to my left, so I guess his blindness is real. I wave a hand in front of him anyway, to little effect."
    "ついでに、こいつは俺から３０度くらい左にずれた方向に話しかけている。ということは視覚障害は本当なんだろう。それでも念のため目の前で手を振ってみるけど、何の反応もない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4455
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_d79bf453:

    # ke "Man, I hope you realize I'm just joking."
    ke "ったく、わかってると思うけど冗談だぞ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4457
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_f7d599f2:

    # "I laugh, pretending that I did. Somehow, looking him in the eyes is more difficult than usual."
    "わかったふりをして、俺は笑う。どうしてか、健二と目を合わせるのがいつもよりも難しい。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4462
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_cb376b47:

    # ke "Want some trivia? People with small eyes wear big glasses."
    ke "ちょっとした小ネタ、知ってるか？　目の小さい人はでかい眼鏡をかけるんだ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4464
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_031e0101:

    # hi "I've read that somewhere. It's because it makes your eyes look less beady."
    hi "どっかで読んだことあるな。そのほうが目が輝いて見えるからだって"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4466
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_ca328630:

    # ke "Really? I didn't know that."
    ke "そうなのか？　知らなかったぞ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4478
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_0e59ea83:

    # "He puts his glasses back on, and I feel oddly relieved for a moment until I remember that I still have to deal with him, glasses or not."
    "健二は眼鏡をかけ直す。おかしな話だけど、一瞬それを見て安心する。でも眼鏡をかけていようがいまいが、目の前のこいつの相手はしないといけないことを思い出す。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4482
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_45fa5817:

    # ke "Well, anyway… This artist girl wanted to paint my portrait once, I think. I had to talk to her like five times before she started making sense."
    ke "まあ、とにかく……どっかの絵描き女が俺の肖像画を描きたいと言ってきたんだ。確か。そいつの言っていることが理解できるまで５回くらい話しかけなきゃいけなかった"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4484
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_99a479d4:

    # "Must have been Rin, I suppose."
    "琳に違いない。たぶん。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4486
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_1d9babe9:

    # hi "What'd she look like?"
    hi "その子、どんな格好だった？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4491
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_e58b356d:

    # ke "I don't know. A woman with sandals."
    ke "知らねえ。サンダルはいてる女だった"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4493
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_b3473dc5:

    # "I was hoping he'd say something more specific, like 'she had no arms.' Rin does wear sandals, but I feel like the chance of there being another freespirited female art student wearing sandals besides her is reasonably high."
    "もう少し具体的に言ってくれればいいのに。『腕がなかった』とか。確かに琳はサンダルを履いてるけど、ほかにもサンダルを履いてる気ままな絵描きの女子生徒がいる可能性は結構高いと思う。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4498
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_56c7b2e7:

    # ke "I was thinking, sure. Someday, after I burn all documentation that I exist, it might be okay to leave a portrait behind, so that people can look at it and remember the savior of mankind. They'll need it to model the statue."
    ke "そりゃ考えたさ。いつか自分の存在を証明する文書をすべて焼き払った後に、肖像画を残すくらいはいいだろうって。人々がそれを見て、人類の救い主のことを思い起こせるように。彫像を作るのに必要だからな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4503
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_8fe2d732:

    # ke "Then I thought about it some more and had to turn her down. It was tempting, but she wanted it for some school thing. It would be displayed."
    ke "でももう少し考えて、結局拒否することにした。いい話だったけど、そいつは学校の課題か何かのために描きたかったんだと。絵も展示されるんだと"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4508
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_2f341eb4:

    # ke "People would ask who I was, only I haven't saved society yet, so it would be pointless. And then if someone recognized me, I'd have to explain myself."
    ke "そしたらみんな俺がどういう奴か聞くだろ。でも俺はまだ社会を救ってない。だからこれじゃ意味がないんだ。それに誰かが俺の顔に気づいたら、俺自身のことを説明しなきゃいけない"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4510
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_3cfb7d02:

    # ke "That's already a chain of events I don't want to deal with. I don't want to get mixed up in some weird situation; shit like that always happens. Sticking out is a surefire way to get put on a list."
    ke "そういう一連の出来事にはそもそも関わりたくないんだよ。なんだか妙な状況に巻き込まれたくないんだ。そういうクソッタレな事態はしょっちゅう起きるんだ。目立てば確実にリストに載っちまう"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4515
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_4a5ff12c:

    # ke "That's why I make such a careful effort to blend in with people in my daily life. Until I can make my move."
    ke "だから俺はこんなに念を入れて日常生活の中で周りの奴らにとけ込む努力をしてるんだ。次の一手を打てるまでな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4517
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_21ce94c5:

    # hi "Sure."
    hi "だろうな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4519
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_56247377:

    # hi "What list?"
    hi "リストって何だよ？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4521
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_62e9a90e:

    # ke "There are many lists."
    ke "リストならいくつもある"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4526
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_fad7f49f:

    # ke "So what are you doing here, anyway?"
    ke "で、お前ここで何してんだよ？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4528
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_427be96d:

    # hi "Nothing. I kind of got here by accident."
    hi "なにも。たまたま来ちゃっただけさ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4530
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_f8b7533a:

    # ke "Happens to me all the time. Well, hope that works out for you. I think I'm going to go back to my dorm room. I need to set my TV to record my shows."
    ke "俺なんかしょっちゅうだぜ。まあお前はそれで問題なければいいけどな。俺もう寮に戻るわ。テレビの録画予約しないと"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4532
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_78d53385:

    # hi "You have TV?"
    hi "テレビ持ってるのか？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4534
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_7b9e6da9:

    # ke "Yes, you should come over sometime, we can watch the game. In high definition."
    ke "ああ。たまにはうちに来いよ。一緒に試合見ようぜ。ハイデフで"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4541
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_28b1914e:

    # "Before I can ask him what he's talking about, he's gone. He left like he came: with zero respect towards other people. Kind of amazing."
    "いったい何を言っているのかと尋ねる前に、健二はいなくなっていた。来たときと同じように去っていった。人のことなんてまるで考えていない。ある意味驚きだな。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4543
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_7b444609:

    # "Now that Kenji is gone, I resume looking aimlessly at the school gardens in their summer splendor. It's no use, he ruined them for me."
    "やっと健二もいなくなったので、華々しい姿の夏の校庭をあてもなく眺める作業に戻る。でも無駄だった。あいつのせいで台無しだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4551
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_9cef0b71:

    # "When I get back to the cafeteria, exhausted but alive, I think of eating lunch with Shizune again, but find her sitting at a table with Misha already."
    "疲れ切ってはいるけど生きたまま食堂に戻り、また静音と昼でも食べるかと考えるけど、当人はもうミーシャと一緒にテーブルについている。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4553
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_d4295f7e:

    # "If it were anyone else, I would think how they were too far away for me to hear them. This is Shizune and Misha, however."
    "ほかの誰かだったら、二人の声が聞こえるには遠すぎるだろうと考える。でもこれはほかならぬ静音とミーシャだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4555
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_a1e7e416:

    # "If I wanted to, I could 'eavesdrop' on their conversation easily. What a dirty thing to think about, but it's there. …I don't want to, though."
    "その気になれば、二人の会話を『盗み聞き』することも簡単だ。なんて卑劣な考えだろう。でもできるんだ……やりたいとは思わないけど。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4557
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_9ead1de3:

    # "They must have a lot of catching up to do, even if it's only been a few days. I'm inclined to just leave them alone so they can do just that."
    "たった数日だとしても、きっと積もる話がたくさんあるんだろう。二人をそっとしてやりたい気分になる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4559
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_456f072c:

    # "However, the second they see me, they wave me over."
    "でも俺の姿を見た瞬間、二人は俺を招き寄せてくる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4568
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_300b2599:

    # mi "Hi, Hicchan~!"
    mi "こんちは、ひっちゃん～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4570
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_7ba53158:

    # "Hearing her voice again even after such a short time apart is jarring, and I wince."
    "ほんの少し離れていただけなのに、ミーシャの声をまた耳にするのは神経にきつくて、俺は顔をしかめる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4572
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_2a36ff78:

    # "These past few days, I had forgotten that communication with Shizune is almost entirely silent, and concentrating on getting it right, I had tuned out even ambient noise."
    "この数日、静音との会話がほとんど無音だったことを忘れきっていた。きちんと会話することに集中しているうちに、周りの雑音もシャットアウトしてしまっていたんだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4574
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_ec7cae6d:

    # "Well, I'll get used to it again. I'm glad she is back."
    "まあ、またそのうち慣れるだろう。ミーシャが戻ってきてくれてうれしい。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4579
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_4d211843:

    # mi "I'm done making up all my work~! Just in time~, I won't have to miss the festival. Wahaha~."
    mi "遅れてた勉強、全部追いついたよ～！　ちょうど間に合ったよ～、これで七夕祭りも参加できるよ。わはは～"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4584
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_dae1c767:

    # ssh "If they really tried to enforce that, I would pull you out on student council business."
    ssh "本当に参加禁止なんて言い出したら、私が生徒会の名目で引っ張り出すから"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4589
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_b0479d1a:

    # mi "If they really really tried to enforce that, you would pull me out on student council business~?"
    mi "本当に参加禁止なんて言い出したら、しっちゃんが生徒会の名目でわたしを引っ張り出してくれるの～？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4591
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_ad51644b:

    # hi "That's abuse of power."
    hi "それは職権乱用だろう"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4596
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_ef2b123c:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4601
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_2e02105b:

    # mi "No it isn't, Hicchan~!"
    mi "それはちがうよ、ひっちゃん～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4606
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_29b84a43:

    # mi "Shicchan says that if there were only two Student Council members overseeing the festival, it would be a problem, wouldn't it? Yeah~, definitely! It has to be at least three! It's for the good of everyone, it's perfectly reasonable, it's necessary~!"
    mi "もし七夕祭を運営する生徒会メンバーが二人しかいなかったら問題になるでしょ、違う？　そうだよ～、絶対！　少なくとも三人はいなきゃ！　みんなのためなんだから、完璧に筋が通ってるよ、必要なんだよ～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4612
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_154ff725:

    # "Shizune leans across the table a bit as Misha delivers her slightly disturbing, militaristic justifications in a childish, bubbly, up-and-down tone."
    "ミーシャがなんだか物騒な軍隊っぽい自己正当化を、子供っぽくて陽気で大げさな抑揚でまくしたてている間、静音はほんの少しテーブルに乗り出している。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4614
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_775ba19c:

    # "Shizune looks so happy, though, tenting her fingers and trying to hold back a laugh as Misha pouts more seriously on her behalf."
    "でも静音はとても楽しそうに見える。両手の指を重ねて、自分のかわりに真剣そうに頬を膨らませるミーシャの横で笑いを抑えようとしている。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4616
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_c958ed86:

    # hi "If you say so."
    hi "まあ、そう言うなら"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4618
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_52da27de:

    # "I'm actually happy right now, that we can talk so easily to each other. All three of us."
    "実は俺も、今は楽しいと思っている。みんなが、俺たち三人が、お互いこんなに気楽に話せているから。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4620
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_5f3fcda0:

    # "In the beginning I thought that I might have found myself in a bad situation. I was sure that Shizune would hate getting saddled with being tour guide for the new guy."
    "最初は、自分がまずい立場に置かれているかもしれないと思っていた。静音も新入りの案内役なんて役目を押しつけられるのはごめんだろうと確信していた。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4622
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_f7f3661c:

    # "I didn't want to be that kind of burden, either. It would be awkward even if she weren't deaf and mute, too."
    "俺自身もそんな面倒をかけるのはいやだった。静音が聾唖者でなかったとしても気まずかっただろう。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4624
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_6ce2a4f1:

    # "Just now, she said that we would all have to be at the festival, the whole Student Council. I don't think that the Student Council has any real jurisdiction over Tanabata. It's only Shizune's way of saying that she wants us to spend it together."
    "たった今、静音は俺たち全員が、生徒会のフルメンバーがお祭りにいなくてはだめだと言った。七夕祭に対して生徒会がなにか権限を持っているとは思わない。みんなで七夕を過ごしたいという、静音なりの表現なんだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4626
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_4102db9a:

    # "It's nice to have friends."
    "友達がいるってのはいいもんだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4628
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_db783ebf:

    # "It's a simple thought, but one that makes me genuinely happy, that we could slip into being such with so much ease. Despite the roundabout way in which she said it, I'm glad that Shizune thinks it strongly enough to express it at all."
    "単純な考えだけど、こんなに簡単に仲良くなれたということに、本当に満ち足りた気持ちになる。回りくどい言い方だとしても、そもそも言葉にするくらい静音が強い思いを抱いていることをうれしく思う。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4633
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_84742865:

    # ssh "Why did you wait until we waved you over to come sit with us?"
    ssh "どうして私たちが手を振るまでこっちに来て座らなかったの？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4635
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_8fc2bf24:

    # "A question out of nowhere. Shizune's eyes are expectant as Misha repeats her message. I feel like teasing her."
    "出し抜けに質問が飛んでくる。ミーシャが質問を繰り返す間、静音の目が答えを待ちかねている。ちょっとからかってやろう。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4637
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_ce932b4f:

    # hi "You want me to sit with you that badly?"
    hi "そんなに俺に一緒に座ってほしかったのか？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4642
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_148fc6d9:

    # ssh "We're in the Student Council. We should sit together as much as possible. It's logic."
    ssh "私たちは生徒会に所属しているんだから。できるだけ一緒に座るべきよ。それが道理でしょ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4647
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_8d01febd:

    # ssh "Anyone would jump at the chance to sit with two cute girls anyway."
    ssh "それに、こんな美少女二人と一緒に座るチャンスに飛びつかない人なんていないでしょ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4649
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_cfe2d207:

    # "She pauses, in case I might say something like 'You're not that cute!' and instantly lock myself into an obvious no-win situation. When I don't take the bait, Shizune becomes more energetic and continues."
    "言葉を切る。こっちが『そこまでかわいくないだろ！』みたいなことを言って負け確定の状況に陥いるのを待っているんだ。俺が餌に食いつかなかったので、静音はさらに活気づいて話し続ける。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4654
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_54bc0024:

    # ssh "You're abnormal."
    ssh "あなたは異常ね"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4656
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_c43895df:

    # "Well, I didn't expect her to end it like that."
    "そういう締め方をされるとは思わなかったぞ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4658
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_000caf5b:

    # hi "You're too quick to call other people abnormal. So arrogant."
    hi "安易に人を異常呼ばわりしすぎだろ。ほんとに失礼だな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4663
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_178a1256:

    # ssh "You're too quick to call other people arrogant. That makes you arrogant, and arrogance is also abnormal. You're double-abnormal."
    ssh "そっちこそ安易に人を失礼って言ってる。あなたも失礼だし、失礼なのも異常。だからあなたは二重に異常ってこと"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4665
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_79689f55:

    # hi "It doesn't work that way. It's a sliding scale."
    hi "そうはならないだろ。こういうのは程度で決まるんだよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4670
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_65993481:

    # mi "Hahaha~."
    mi "ははは～"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4672
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_b8449417:

    # "Leaning on her arm, Misha closes her eyes and lets out a low, slow laugh like a chuckle."
    "頬杖をつきながら、ミーシャは目を閉じてゆっくりと低く笑う。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4674
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_bc07d653:

    # hi "Don't laugh…"
    hi "笑うなよ……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4679
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_35c34961:

    # ssh "Don't laugh in this kind of situation."
    ssh "こんな状況で笑うんじゃないの"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4681
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_cb67b6fc:

    # "I notice that Misha signs everything I say to Shizune anyway, even though I'm signing myself. This is redundant, but it's an unconscious action for Misha. On the other hand I can't stop."
    "俺が自分で手話をしているのにかまわず、ミーシャが俺の言葉をすべて手話で伝えていることに気づく。無駄な行為だけど、ミーシャにとっては無意識の行動なんだ。でも俺だって手話をやめるわけにはいかない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4683
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_8e9f18af:

    # "If I let myself take it easy and sign less just because Misha is back, then what was all this for? I don't want to risk losing familiarity with how to sign either. My hands are pretty slow to speak on my behalf as it is."
    "ミーシャが戻ってきたからというだけで手抜きをして手話をしなくなったら、今までやってきたことは何だったんだ？　身についた手話を忘れる危険はおかしたくない。今だって、手を使って会話するととても遅いんだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4688
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_0e26fc98:

    # mi "Hicchan, you and Shicchan talk to each other much more now~! Back and forth, it's really funny too! Like an old married couple, right~ right~?"
    mi "ひっちゃん、もうしっちゃんと二人ですごくいっぱい話してるね～！　やりとりがすごく面白いよ～！　おしどり夫婦みたいだよ、でしょ～でしょ～？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4690
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_597a53f9:

    # "What a loaded comment, in so many ways. Although, because it's Misha, it can't have been on purpose."
    "今のはいろいろと意味深すぎるだろう。でもミーシャだし、わざと言ったとは思えない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4692
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_a3444f35:

    # hi "That's not a compliment."
    hi "ほめ言葉になってないぞ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4694
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_1ee72cde:

    # "Shizune doesn't react to Misha trying to pair the two of us up. Maybe she didn't see it. Sometimes it does happen, I've noticed. I still wonder if it's really that simple, and why I care so much, but I don't want to think about it too hard."
    "俺たち二人をくっつけようとするミーシャの言葉にも、静音は反応しない。見ていなかったのかもしれない。 前から気づいていたけど、時々そういうことがある。そんなに簡単なことだろうかと思うし、どうしていちいち気になるんだろうかとも思うけど、あまり深く考えたくはない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4696
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_c91de257:

    # "I want to leave. I keep thinking that I'm hogging Misha's time with Shizune, and it could be that Misha cut in just now on purpose, feeling that way too. I doubt that either of them will let me leave, though. In some ways they're too nice."
    "そろそろこの場を離れたい。ミーシャが静音と一緒にいるのを邪魔している気がしてならないし、ミーシャもそう思ってわざと割り込んだのかもしれない。でも二人とも俺を帰してはくれない気がする。 ある意味、優しすぎるんだよな。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4698
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_9ac54a73:

    # hi "Anyway, Shizune, if you really want to know, I didn't want to sit here because I didn't want to intrude."
    hi "とにかくさ、静音、そこまで聞きたいなら言うけど、こっちに来たくないと思ったのは邪魔したくなかったからだよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4700
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_0d8e171a:

    # hi "I thought that because of Misha being away for supplementary lessons or whatever, you two would have a lot to talk about, and I should just leave you alone to catch up. That's why I thought I would just hang back."
    hi "ミーシャが補習とかで一緒にいられなかったから、二人とも積もる話があるだろうし、それを邪魔しちゃいけないなと思ったんだよ。だから近づかなかったんだ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4702
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_fde327d9:

    # hi "Don't worry, Misha, I'm not trying to monopolize Shizune."
    hi "心配するなよ、ミーシャ。静音を独り占めしたいわけじゃないから"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4707
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_aa20259a:

    # mi "Wahaha~! Hicchan! It's not like that~."
    mi "わはは～！　ひっちゃん！　そういうのじゃないよ～"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4712
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_ef2b123c_1:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4717
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_122a1a18:

    # mi "You're so considerate, Hicchan! Shicchan is sorry~ and apologizes."
    mi "ひっちゃん、とっても親切なんだね！　しっちゃん反省してるって～、謝ってるよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4719
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_926c2a0e:

    # hi "I don't really think it's worth apologizing over, so, don't worry about it. Hey, don't you both think that since Misha is back, we should go celebrate somehow? I think so."
    hi "別に謝るようなことじゃないだろ、気にするなって。なあ二人とも、ミーシャも戻ってきたことだし、なにかお祝いすべきじゃないか？　俺はそう思うぜ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4724
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_29bcb554:

    # mi "Hicchan~! Usually, having to make up work isn't something to celebrate over."
    mi "ひっちゃん～！　遅れた勉強を取り戻すのはお祝いするようなことじゃないでしょ、普通は"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4729
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_9d7f1c2f:

    # ssh "No, it's a good idea."
    ssh "いいえ、いい考えだわ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4731
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_24ac69a8:

    # hi "The timing is perfect, and Shizune said that the Student Council should have a little fun too sometimes. You've probably heard that too, right, Misha? It should be fine."
    hi "タイミングもばっちりだし、生徒会だってたまにはちょっとお楽しみがあるべきだって静音も言ってたしな。ミーシャだって聞いてるだろ？　問題ないさ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4736
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_ef2b123c_2:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4738
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_c64384e7:

    # hi "Actually, wait a second. Didn't you have to make up work because you were missing so many classes to begin with? So, skipping out to celebrate would be kind of stupid. Maybe the timing isn't perfect, like I said, but we could go after school."
    hi "というか、ちょっと待てよ。そもそも授業をさぼりすぎてたから補習を受けるはめになってたんじゃなかったのか？　お祝いするのに授業をさぼってたら、なんかバカみたいだぞ タイミングは微妙かもしれないけど、放課後に行ったっていい"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4743
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_fb8d2e15:

    # mi "Where should we go?"
    mi "どこに行く？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4745
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_f4fd86e8:

    # "Misha speaks Shizune's question to her aloud before she even stops to think it over, both of them completely ignoring me."
    "答えを考えることもせず、ミーシャが静音の問いを大声で口にする。二人とも完全に俺を無視している。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4747
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_3b2f800a:

    # hi "Hey, listen to me, two-man shortsighted Student Council team!"
    hi "おい人の話を聞けよ、そこの二人組近視眼生徒会チーム！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4752
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_ef2b123c_3:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4757
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_cd163339:

    # mi "Wahaha~! Hicchan, you're a part of this team, too!"
    mi "わはは～！　ひっちゃんだってチームの一員だよ！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4759
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_0f0f3cb5:

    # hi "Ah, yeah. I guess I am."
    hi "あー、そうだな。そうかも"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4764
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_f762313c:

    # mi "Yeah yeah~! You are, Hicchan!"
    mi "そうだそうだ～！　そうなんだよ、ひっちゃん！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4769
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_75ebcdf0:

    # ssh "So forgetful, and troublesome. I feel sorry for the girl who falls in love with you."
    ssh "本当、物忘ればかりで厄介よね。あなたに惚れちゃう子には同情するわ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4774
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_059e4afb:

    # mi "So~! Where do you think we should go?"
    mi "さてと～！　どこに行くのがいいかな？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4776
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_b5f422cf:

    # "I'm laughing in spite of myself, wanting to point out how Misha seems so enthusiastic now, when she was the one who was most apprehensive about it just a few seconds ago. For whatever reason, I can't bring myself to do it. But, this is okay, too."
    "一番気乗りしていなかったミーシャが今ではすっかり乗り気なので、それを突っ込みたくて思わず笑い出してしまう。でもどういうわけかそれを口にする気にはならない。それでもいいんだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4780
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_1bcc1085:

    # "After a short discussion on where to go, it seems like the only place all three of us know and are willing to travel to is the Shanghai."
    "行き先について少し話し合ったけど、結局俺たち三人が知っていて、かつ行く気になれる場所は上海しかなさそうだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4782
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_84f90213:

    # "A teahouse doesn't look like a bad place to celebrate, especially because I'm sure they sell cake there, and cake is the most celebratory food."
    "お祝いする場所として喫茶店は悪い場所じゃなさそうだ。特に間違いなくケーキが食べられるとわかっている。ケーキはお祝い用の食べ物として一番だ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4787
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_556d1630:

    # "I haven't seen Yuuko in a while, either, and neither have the girls. For all these reasons, plus the fact that it's so close, I end up standing in front of the little tea shop with Shizune and Misha before I know it."
    "それに、しばらく優子さんに会っていない。静音とミーシャもだ。こうした諸々の理由と、とても近いということもあって、気づいたときには二人とともに小さな喫茶店の正面に立っていた。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4797
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_d4fd5b8e:

    # yu "Welcome!"
    yu "いらっしゃいませ！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4801
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_ace5d772:

    # "It's been a while since I heard Yuuko's voice, so I'm surprised all over again by the energy she puts into her greetings. Kind of like an extremely nervous Misha."
    "優子さんの声を聞くのも久しぶりで、そのあいさつの気合いの入りぶりにまたしても驚かされる羽目になる。極度に緊張したミーシャみたいなものだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4810
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_5f215a0a:

    # mi "Hi~! But~! you don't have to do that all the time if it's just us."
    mi "こんちは～！　でも～！　わたしたちの時は、毎回それやらなくてもいいんだよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4815
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_6ed11c6f:

    # yu "Yes I do…"
    yu "やらなきゃだめなの……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4820
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_5d2f525e:

    # mi "But—"
    mi "でも――"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4825
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_9f34b625:

    # mi "Okay~! Okay~! If you say so, Yuuko! Hahahahaha~!"
    mi "おっけ～！　おっけ～！　優子さんがそう言うなら！　ははははは～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4827
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_2f76679c:

    # "I take this moment to glance around the teahouse and notice that it is as empty as ever. It's lunch time; essentially the peak hour for an establishment of this type. And yet, it's as barren as ever. I don't understand. There has to be a reason for this."
    "二人が話している間に店内を見回すといつものように客がいない。今はランチタイム。こういうお店にとってはピークの時間だ。なのに毎度のごとく人の気配がない。わけがわからない。何か理由があるとしか思えない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4838
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_37623dbb:

    # "Shizune gently taps my arm to get my attention."
    "静音がそっと俺の腕を叩いて注意を引く。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4843
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_cb845620:

    # ssh "What do you want to get?"
    ssh "何を頼む？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4848
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_df623924:

    # "Yuuko looks a little agitated after Misha automatically relays the question."
    "ミーシャが反射的にその質問を伝えると、優子さんは少し動揺したようだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4850
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_5865f165:

    # yu "N-no, I'm supposed to… ask that… Is there anything that I can do for you?"
    yu "だ、だめよ、それは私が……聞かなきゃ……ご注文はおきまりですか？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4858
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_7520b622:

    # hi "Just some coffee for now, I guess. Thanks."
    hi "とりあえずコーヒー、かな。どうも"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4863
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_0af0becc:

    # "The dedication Yuuko has towards her waitressing duties is sort of admirable. So is the speed at which she whisks slices of cake and our drinks to our table when we order."
    "ウェイトレスの仕事に対する優子さんの熱心さはある意味尊敬に値する。オーダーの後にケーキと飲み物をテーブルまで持ってくるときの素早さもだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4876
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_b62b8d61:

    # "Then again, we're the only customers here. Who knows what it would be like with a full house."
    "とはいえ、俺たち以外に客はいないわけで。満員の時にどうなるかはわかったものじゃない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4878
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_5698db7c:

    # "Shizune and Misha immediately dig into their cakes with gusto, probably because they can't talk with utensils in their hands."
    "静音とミーシャはすぐにむしゃむしゃとケーキを食べ始める。食器を手に持ったままでは話せないからだろう。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4880
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_2545d0e6:

    # "The whole point of sharing a meal with friends like this is being able to talk over it, after all. It makes sense that it would be the same with them."
    "そもそも友達といっしょにこうして食事をするのは、食べながら会話をするためだ。二人も同じ考えでいるというのは理にかなっている。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4882
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_4807c02d:

    # "I'm barely halfway through my cake when I hear their forks clinking as they set them down on their empty plates."
    "二人が空のお皿にフォークを置く音が鳴るのを聞いたとき、俺はまだケーキを半分も食べていなかった。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4884
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_dbac074b:

    # hi "It's not healthy to inhale your food."
    hi "早食いは体に悪いぞ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4889
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_9da223a0:

    # mi "Hahaha~! Hicchan sounds like an old man~!"
    mi "ははは～！　ひっちゃん、それおじいちゃんみたいだよ～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4891
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_9ca29d45:

    # "I cringe and instantly feel like I've been punched."
    "身が縮む思いがする。一発殴られた気分だ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4896
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_ef2b123c_4:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4901
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_82da0343:

    # mi "Are you going to wear a yukata tomorrow, Hicchan?"
    mi "明日は浴衣を着るの、ひっちゃん？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4903
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_d6a9f297:

    # hi "No, I don't even have one. Well, even if I did, I'm not the kind of guy who does stuff like that."
    hi "いや、そもそも浴衣がないし。あったとしても俺はそういうことをするタイプじゃないから"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4905
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_2adabbc1:

    # hi "What about you? Are you two going to dress up?"
    hi "お前たちはどうなんだ？　二人とも着るのか？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4911
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_1da05530:

    # ssh "Of course."
    ssh "もちろん"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4913
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_573e6e99:

    # hi "What do you mean 'of course?' You didn't dress up last time."
    hi "『もちろん』ってどういうことだよ？　前は着飾ったりしなかっただろ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4918
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_de3d9ab5:

    # ssh "One time is not a trend! It's a completely different situation anyway. Aside from not being Tanabata, the festival was on school grounds; students should wear their uniform on school grounds."
    ssh "一度そうだったからっていつもとは限らないでしょ！　だいたい状況がまるで違うんだから。七夕じゃなかったのを抜きにしても、学園祭は学校の敷地内で開催したのよ。生徒は学校内では制服着用よ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4920
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_4ad13e01:

    # "Clearly a joke, but her delivery isn't any different from the usual. That isn't normal, but her sense of humor never was, and I'm used to it."
    "冗談なのは明らかだけど、その言い方はいつもとまるで変わらない。それは普通ではないけど、静音のユーモアのセンスが普通であったためしはないし、俺ももう慣れている。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4922
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_68cf72a0:

    # "I guess her way of saying outrageous things seriously is a little better than if she were to say serious things outrageously."
    "静音は真剣なことをとんでもない風に言うよりも、とんでもないことをさも真剣そうに言うほうが少しだけ得意なんだろう。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4924
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_26ac090e:

    # "What's more troubling in any case is that I've started to associate a voice with her signing, and it's clashing with how Misha says out loud everything Shizune signs anyway. I feel disoriented."
    "とにかく、それ以上に悩ましいのは、静音の手話にあわせて頭の中で声が聞こえ始めているということだ。それが静音の手話を逐一読み上げるミーシャの大きな声とぶつかり合って、わけがわからなくなってくる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4929
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_19904dee:

    # ssh "I'll dress up this time!"
    ssh "こんどはちゃんと着飾るわよ！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4934
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_132293f0:

    # mi "I'll dress up this time~! You'll see, Hicchan!"
    mi "こんどは着飾るよ～！　見ててよ、ひっちゃん！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4939
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_8ef59f73:

    # mi "Not just Shicchan, but me too~!"
    mi "しっちゃんだけじゃなくて、わたしもね～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4944
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_6a5918ca:

    # mi "Maybe~ I'll change my hairstyle, too."
    mi "もしかしたら～、髪型も変えるかも"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4946
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_66d0c91a:

    # hi "Don't do that, I can't really imagine you looking differently."
    hi "それはよせよ、ミーシャが違う髪型なんて想像できないぞ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4951
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_7ce77db3:

    # "Shizune wags a finger and smiles."
    "静音が指を振って笑顔を見せる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4956
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_a242bc36:

    # ssh "Such a quick and firm disapproval. What if I were to change my hairstyle?"
    ssh "あっさり否定してくれるじゃない。私が髪型を変えたらどうなるでしょうね？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4958
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_fa12b472:

    # hi "Maybe you should grow your hair out and make it look like drills."
    hi "髪伸ばしてドリルみたいにしたらいいんじゃないか"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4970
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_038e4d1b:

    # "She looks unamused. Luckily, I see Yuuko making her way over, likely to clear our plates or ask if we need anything from her."
    "面白くなさそうだ。幸い、優子さんがこっちに来るのが見える。たぶん食器を下げて追加の注文がないか聞くためだろう。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4972
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_a43b51fd:

    # hi "Yuuko, are you doing anything for Tanabata?"
    hi "優子さん、七夕は何かするんですか？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4977
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_2d966d51:

    # yu "Huh?"
    yu "えっ？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4979
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_81421728:

    # "It's like she was practicing how to most smoothly ask if I needed a refill of coffee while walking over, but she has no idea what to do having been asked a question first. I feel bad."
    "そばを通りかかりながらスムーズにコーヒーのおかわりがいるか尋ねる練習をしていたみたいだけど、先に質問されてしまってどうしたらいいかわからないようだ。悪いことしたな。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4984
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_4ca42366:

    # yu "Yes, I'm… working…"
    yu "うん、その……仕事してる……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4989
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_8e919ebc:

    # mi "Yuuko~, they make you work on holidays? Awwww…"
    mi "優子さん～、休日に働かされるの？　え～～～～……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:4994
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_44499bc7:

    # yu "W-we have the most business on holidays, and sometimes tourists. I don't mind. I have to do my best."
    yu "あの、うちは休日が一番忙しいから。あと旅行客の人も。だから気にしてないわ。全力を尽くさないとね"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5000
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_4b516129:

    # ssh "I understand completely. So admirable."
    ssh "とてもよくわかるわ。尊敬しちゃう"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5002
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_7a38acaf:

    # "Shizune nods her head in solidarity, feeling a kind of kinship with Yuuko through their shared determination to be the best, although for her it's a matter of pride whereas Yuuko might just feel that she really, really needs this job and maybe a raise."
    "最善を尽くすという、自分と同じ決意を共有する優子さんに親近感を抱きながら、静音がうなずく。 でも静音にとってはそれはプライドの問題だけど、優子さんはこの仕事と、あと多少の給料アップがなければ本当にやっていけないと思っているだけかもしれない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5004
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_688efb8a:

    # hi "The most business, huh? So, how many people on average during a holiday?"
    hi "一番忙しいんですか？　じゃあ休日は平均でどれくらいお客さんが来るんですか？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5009
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_7e5f113d:

    # yu "Ah, well…"
    yu "あー、その……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5014
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_5716abb1:

    # yu "…"
    yu "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5027
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_69bc9b25:

    # "Yuuko walks away and starts cleaning a cup of swizzle sticks. That isn't polite. This is not what a proper waitress would do! Nevertheless, I sort of got my answer anyway. Clearly, business is scarce at best."
    "優子さんは逃げ、マドラーの入ったカップを洗い始める。失礼だな。ちゃんとしたウェイトレスの接客態度じゃないだろう！　でも何となく答えはわかった気がする。明らかに、商売はよくてカツカツなんだろう。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5029
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_17c8cbd1:

    # "I start to wonder again how the Shanghai remains open at all. Maybe this eclectic style of teahouse is a trend that was outrageously successful before I got here but isn't any more, and they're just keeping it like this while they retool."
    "そもそもどうして上海が営業を続けていられるのか、と再び疑問に思う。以前はこういう和洋折衷式の喫茶店がとても流行っていたけど、今ではその流行も過ぎていて、改装するまでそのままにしているだけなのかもな。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5031
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_2932d826:

    # "Maybe the owner is rich and is involved in some sort of bet with someone else or a crazy scheme to see who can lose the most money. Maybe I just conveniently miss mobs of customers by seconds each visit."
    "もしかしたら店のオーナーが金持ちで誰かと賭けみたいなものをしているのか、あるいは誰が一番浪費するかを見るいかれた計画に熱中しているのか。 たまたま俺がここに来るたびに、大勢の客と数秒の差で入れ違いになっているだけなのかもしれない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5033
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_117105f3:

    # "Or maybe this place is just a front for arms dealers."
    "あるいは、ここはただの武器商人の窓口なのかも。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5035
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_8f0615ba:

    # hi "Since there's no one else here, why don't you sit down with us?"
    hi "ほかに誰もいないし、優子さんもいっしょに座りませんか？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5037
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_64a63648:

    # "We can talk about economic infeasibility. …But Yuuko doesn't take the bait, shaking her head from side to side emphatically."
    "この店の客の入りについて話せるだろう……でも優子さんは誘いに乗らずに、頭を力強く左右に振る。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5042
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_65ff7dbe:

    # mi "I've never really celebrated Tanabata before, or dressed up for anything like this~! I'll finally be able to wear my yukata. Yay yay~!"
    mi "七夕のお祝いとか、こういうときに着飾ったりするのって、今まで一度もしたことがないんだ～！　やっと浴衣が着られるよ。やったやった～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5044
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_6a5a8df7:

    # hi "What do you mean never? What about last year?"
    hi "一度もないってどういうことだ？　去年はどうしたんだよ？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5049
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_8c71f6a2:

    # mi "Hm~… last year, Shicchan, me, and the 3-2 class rep ran a stall for the festival! It was a soba stall, I think~? Yeah, it was~! Yup!"
    mi "ん～……去年はしっちゃんと、わたしと、３－２の目の見えないクラス委員とでお祭りの屋台をやったんだよ！　焼きそばの屋台だった、と思うよ～？　うん、そうだよ～！　確かに！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5054
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_e7deffe1:

    # "The blind class rep of 3-2 must be Lilly. I'm surprised they were able to work together on anything, but Misha would likely be the best possible buffer for that kind of thing, with how innocent she is."
    "３－２の目の見えないクラス委員はリリーに違いない。この顔ぶれがいっしょに何か作業ができるなんて驚きだ。でもそういう状況では無邪気なミーシャが一番いい緩衝材になるだろう。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5059
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_9c2a2f26:

    # mi "Shicchan cooked, and Lilly took the orders, and I translated for them~!"
    mi "しっちゃんが料理して、リリーが注文を取って、わたしが二人に通訳したんだよ～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5064
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_5b0f713b:

    # mi "Shicchan kept saying, 'It's so inefficient~! Misha~! Why do you have to be the middleman? As in~, why is there a middleman in the first place? Huh~? It would be fine if I did the cooking and you took orders! It doesn't make sense at all!'"
    mi "しっちゃんはずーっと、『効率悪い～！　ミーシャ～！　どうしてあなたが通訳なんかしなきゃいけないの？　つまり～、そもそもなんで通訳が必要なの？　え～？』 『わたしが料理してあなたが注文取ればいいじゃないの！　意味わかんない！』って言ってたんだよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5069
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_c328a18c:

    # mi "But~! I think everyone had fun in the end. Right, Shicchan~?"
    mi "でも～！　最後はみんな楽しんでたと思うんだ。そうでしょ、しっちゃん～？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5074
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_12e64098:

    # shi "… … …"
    shi "…… …… ……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5076
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_e5a5b24f:

    # "Shizune adjusts her glasses grudgingly, causing Misha to break into laughter."
    "いやいやながらといった様子で静音は眼鏡を直す。それを見てミーシャが急に笑い出す。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5081
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_85b5f3dd:

    # mi "It was the old Student Council's idea~! That's why~!"
    mi "前の生徒会の案だったんだよ～！　だからだよ～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5083
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_b1a98019:

    # hi "So, what was the last Student Council like, then?"
    hi "じゃあ、前の生徒会ってどんなだったんだ？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5085
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_b756faf1:

    # "Shizune finally decides to step in again, or it's more like she can't stop herself."
    "静音がついに再び介入を決断する。というか、口を出さずにはいられないみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5090
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_7c43f35c:

    # ssh "Terrible."
    ssh "ひどかった"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5092
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_40199a59:

    # "That was blunt. She ends with a chopping motion, as if passing judgment on them. I hope she's going to elaborate a little."
    "単刀直入だな。判決を下すかのように、手で空を切る仕草で言葉を締める。もう少し詳しく説明してくれるといいけど。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5097
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_ef2b123c_5:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5102
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_3fd8dcaf:

    # mi "At universities and some private schools, student councils can have control over millions of yen to budget and distribute as needed! Wow~! Really? Millions? Ah, right~! And they are much more involved in school activities, too, Hicchan!"
    mi "大学とか一部の私立高校だと、生徒会には何百万円も予算があって、必要に応じて配布できるの わーお！　ほんとに？　何百万も？　あー、そうだね～！　しかも生徒会は学校の活動にずっといっぱい関わってるんだよ、ひっちゃん！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5104
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_53979be1:

    # "From Misha's tone, it seems like this is newer to her than it is to me."
    "その口調からすると、それは俺よりもまず、ミーシャにとって初耳だったみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5109
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_bfa7c726:

    # mi "This school's Student Council was like a joke in comparison~! Don't give people positions of power if they don't have any power at all! What's the point~?"
    mi "それに比べれば、この学校の生徒会は冗談みたいなものだったの～！　まったく力のない人に権力のある地位を与えたらだめ！　そんなことして何の意味があるの～？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5114
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_2b8dbab8:

    # ssh "So…"
    ssh "それで……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5119
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_ef2d9e83:

    # mi "…I wanted us to have more and more work~! It was hard to convince the school and the other Student Council members to allow it. Actually~, a lot of the work you've seen us do really is work that I took on, which is what Lilly was talking about."
    mi "……わたしは自分たちの仕事をもっと増やしたかったの～！　それを認めるよう学校やほかの生徒会メンバーを説得するのは大変だった 実は～、ひっちゃんが見たようなわたしたちの仕事はわたしが引き受けたものなの。リリーが話していたのはそういうこと"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5124
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_9796b198:

    # mi "If it wasn't for Shicchan, the Student Council would just file attendance reports day in and day out~!"
    mi "しっちゃんがいなかったら、生徒会は来る日も来る日も出席簿を整理するだけだったんだよ～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5129
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_cbcc1866:

    # mi "Hahaha~! Would you prefer that, Hicchan?"
    mi "ははは～！　そんなのがいいと思う、ひっちゃん？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5134
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_e2392625:

    # mi "Of course, Hicchan, as soon as the workload started going up, most of the Student Council stopped coming."
    mi "もちろん、ひっちゃん、仕事の量が増え始めたとたんに、生徒会のメンバーはほとんどが顔を出さなくなったの"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5139
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_69277904:

    # mi "Wahahaha~!"
    mi "わははは～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5145
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_ef2b123c_6:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5147
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_4c4918e6:

    # "Shizune's fingers fold over each other carefully. It looks like she wants to add something, but she can't bring herself to."
    "静音の指が注意深く重なり合う。一言付け加えたいのに、そうする気分になれないかのようだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5149
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_0e4fad93:

    # "Like she said, sign language gives you a little more time to think about what you 'say.' I guess she feels like she can't talk about this."
    "静音が言ったように、手話では自分が『話す』ことについて考える時間が少しだけ増える。このことについては話せない、と思っているんだろう。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5154
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_fafea6b5:

    # ssh "That was then, and this is now. Let's just have fun tomorrow."
    ssh "昔は昔、今は今。いいから明日は楽しみましょう"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5156
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_db164197:

    # "That is what she finally settles for."
    "結局、静音が言葉にしたのはそれだけだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5158
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_142d50b9:

    # hi "Yeah."
    hi "そうだな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5163
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_ef2b123c_7:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5170
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_56ed04c6:

    # mi "Okay~! Then, Student Council is ad—jour—ned? for today~!"
    mi "おっけ～！　じゃあ、今日の生徒会はへ――い――かい？　だね～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5175
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_6c0a1f79:

    # mi "It has to be adjourned excitingly, because today was a good day."
    mi "元気よく閉会しないとね。今日はいい日だったから"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5180
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_c9033fad:

    # mi "Ahahaha~!"
    mi "あははは～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5185
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_a2664937:

    # "School seems to be over by the time we leave the teahouse, as I can see students coming down from the school as we walk up the road towards it."
    "店を出る頃には、学校は終わっていたようだ。俺たちが坂を上っていると、学校から下に降りてくる生徒たちが見える。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5187
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_8707a092:

    # "A couple people wearing our school uniform look at Shizune as she walks by, and I wonder if they recognize her as the Student Council president or if their eyes are just being drawn to Misha's head."
    "学校の制服を着た人たちが、何人かすれ違いざまに静音を見る。彼らは静音のことを生徒会長として認識しているのか、それともミーシャの頭に目を引かれているだけなのだろうか。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5189
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_0a62afd9:

    # "It's impossible not to overhear the chatter in the air, and the topic is more often than not plans for Tanabata. I wonder how many of them will be using or going to the stalls that I reassembled."
    "あたりの会話がいやでも耳に入ってくる。話題の多くは七夕の予定だ。そのうちの何人が、俺の組み立てなおした屋台で露店を開いたり、それとも立ち寄るのかな。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5191
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_e3793ee1:

    # "It makes me feel a little pride, an emotion I've never felt doing something for school."
    "ちょっと誇らしい気分になる。学校のために何かをしてこんな気分になったことはなかった。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5193
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_126137f5:

    # "Maybe this is how Shizune feels as well. I almost want to ask, but it seems stupid to want to do so."
    "静音もこういう気持ちなのかもしれない。聞いてみたいという気になるけど、そんなことを考えるのはバカみたいなものだろう。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5198
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_d69d4063:

    # "So I just hold on to the thought as the three of us walk onto campus and then separate; Shizune to the student council room, and Misha and me to our dorms."
    "なので、それは思いとどまって、三人で学校に戻ってから別れる。静音は生徒会室へ、ミーシャと俺は寮の部屋へ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5200
translate jp a2_shizune_past_imperfective_39589ded:

    # "It isn't until they're gone that I realize I again didn't ask when and where they wanted to meet up tomorrow."
    "二人の姿が見えなくなるまで、明日の待ち合わせをどうするか、また聞き損ねたことに気づかなかった。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5214
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_a97aca4d:

    # "Even though it is a holiday, I wake up at the same time as usual, on a day when everyone else is likely sleeping in for another six hours."
    "今日は休日だというのに、普段と同じ時間に目が覚める。ほかのみんなはあと６時間はぐっすり寝込んでいるだろう。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5218
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_d7e66473:

    # "I take my morning regimen of pills for the first time in a few days. Admittedly, I'd let my medication slip my mind. Looking at the rows of bottles in front of me, I don't know how I managed to."
    "数日ぶりに朝の服用分の薬を飲む。正直、薬のことは頭からすっぽり抜けていた。目の前にずらりと並ぶ薬の容器を見ていると、どうして忘れてしまったのか見当もつかない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5220
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_534440ce:

    # "Seventeen different medications. I feel full enough to skip breakfast after taking all of them."
    "１７種類の薬。全部飲み終わると、もう朝食を抜いてもいいくらい腹が一杯になる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5222
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_7ae3a481:

    # "I'm already up, so I might as well take a walk."
    "もう起きてしまったので、散歩にでも出かけるか。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5227
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_6061711c:

    # "The weather looks nice outside, giving off an idyllic atmosphere I'd often dreamed of."
    "外はいい天気みたいで、よく夢に見たのどかな雰囲気が伝わってくる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5229
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_4a1aa36a:

    # "It's always been kind of a romantic notion to me to be able to meander around in the countryside, taking in the fresh air."
    "田舎の地をあてもなく歩いて、新鮮な空気を味わえたらな、なんて非現実的な空想を以前からしていたものだった。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5231
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_40ff9ce2:

    # "Now that an opportunity to do just that is here, I can't resist, even though I know it must seem silly."
    "それを実践するチャンスが目に前にある以上、じっとしてはいられない。バカみたいに見えるだろうとわかってはいるけど。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5236
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_459fa1a8:

    # "I stop at the main building in order to buy a drink, and then decide to enter it and maybe hang around on the roof a little bit."
    "本校舎に寄り道して飲み物を買ったあと、中に入って屋上で少しぶらぶらしていくことにする。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5238
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_008ec97b:

    # "The view might be pretty cool at this time, and I'm sure that nobody else will be up there either. And I've never been up there by myself."
    "この時間なら結構いい眺めが見られるかもしれないし、俺以外に誰もいないのは確実だ。それに一人きりで屋上に上がったことは一度もない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5246
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_fd41f66d:

    # "The school is quiet today. Deserted. My footsteps echoing in the staircase to the roof are unnervingly loud."
    "今日の学校は静かだ。人っ子一人いない。屋上への階段にこだまする自分の足音がぞっとするほど大きい。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5248
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_2847cf47:

    # "It shouldn't bother me due to how much time I've spent in sign language class in near-total silence, or working so much with Shizune lately, but it still does."
    "ほぼ完全に無音の手話クラスに延々時間を費やしたのと、このところ静音と長い間一緒にいたことを考えれば、この状況は別にどうってことはないはずだけど、でもやっぱり落ち着かない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5250
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_7be715e5:

    # "It makes the smallest noises that I wouldn't have even noticed before seem boomingly loud. It feels like I'm sneaking around some place I shouldn't be. I wonder why I'm getting that vibe. Maybe the school is haunted or something."
    "以前なら気にも留めなかったちょっとした音も轟音のように感じる。いけない場所に忍び込んでいる気分だ。どうしてこんな感覚になるのかわからない。もしかしたらこの学校、幽霊にとりつかれていたりするのかも。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5259
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_5d9345ff:

    # "When I open the door to the roof, I see I'm not alone. Misha leans against the fence, looking over the school grounds, not having noticed me at all."
    "屋上のドアを開けると、俺は一人じゃなかった。ミーシャがフェンスにもたれながら校庭を眺めている。俺にはまったく気づいていない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5261
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_2beec755:

    # "Instantly, I know what I have to do: I have to put my hands over her eyes and say 'Guess who?' It's the only option."
    "その瞬間に、とるべき行動が頭に浮かぶ。手で目隠しをして『誰だ？』って言ってやるんだ。それしかない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5263
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_76474849:

    # "Halfway, I start thinking of how bad this would look if Shizune suddenly popped in, having left just for a second to get some sandwiches, and saw me sneaking up on Misha like this."
    "途中まで近寄りながら、サンドイッチを買いに行ったばかりの静音が突然戻ってきて、俺がこうやってミーシャに忍び寄っているのを見られたらどんなに格好悪いだろうか、などと考え始める。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5265
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_db0ff099:

    # "I pray silently that such a coincidental misunderstanding doesn't happen."
    "そんな偶然の誤解が起きないことを無言で祈る。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5270
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_87a6c165:

    # hi "Guess who?"
    hi "誰だ？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5272
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_8288801c:

    # mi "Hicchan!"
    mi "ひっちゃん！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5274
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_01f269ba:

    # "She says, without hesitating for a second, without deviating even slightly from her normal tone. My fun was over before it started."
    "一瞬もためらわずに言う。いつもの声の調子から少しもはずれていない。俺のお楽しみは始まる前から終わっていた。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5286
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_24b85182:

    # mi "Hi, Hicchan! Good morning~!"
    mi "こんちは、ひっちゃん！　おっはよ～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5291
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_71a85225:

    # "She reflexively tries to move her hands to form a greeting and entangles them in the fencing."
    "反射的に挨拶をしようとしたミーシャの手が、そのままフェンスに引っかかってしまう。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5293
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_9bddcf7f:

    # hi "Good morning. I didn't expect to find you here. What're you doing up so early?"
    hi "おはよう。こんなとこにいるとは思わなかったぞ。朝っぱらから何してるんだ？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5298
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_3696369d:

    # mi "I could ask you the same thing, Hicchan! What are you doing up so early? I didn't expect to find you here~!"
    mi "こっちが聞きたいよ、ひっちゃん！　こんな朝早くに何してるの？　ここで会うなんて思わなかったよ～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5300
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_16a1a1ab:

    # hi "I asked you first."
    hi "先に聞いたのはこっちだぞ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5305
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_55398889:

    # mi "Hm~… you're right. Wahaha~!"
    mi "ん～……それもそうだね。わはは～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5310
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_3acf6cf7:

    # mi "You sound just like Shicchan."
    mi "今の、しっちゃんみたいな言い方だね"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5312
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_fcca188f:

    # hi "No, I don't."
    hi "そんなわけあるか"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5314
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_f653a36d:

    # "…I say, in the least convincing manner possible. Luckily, Misha doesn't notice what a bad actor I am."
    "……と、まったく説得力のない口調で言う。幸い、俺のへたくそな芝居にはミーシャは気づかない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5316
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_d559b3ec:

    # hi "Are you looking forward to tonight?"
    hi "今晩のこと、楽しみにしてる？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5321
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_bb86e855:

    # mi "Of course, Hicchan~! I don't like celebrations, or maybe not as much as Shicchan does, but Tanabata stands always have interesting things to buy and all kinds of seasonal food. And~! I get to wear a yukata~!"
    mi "当たり前だよ、ひっちゃん！　お祭りとかは好きじゃないけど、というかしっちゃんほどにはだけど、でも七夕の屋台はいっつも面白いものや季節の食べ物が一杯買えるんだよ。それに～！　浴衣も着られるし！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5323
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_679395ae:

    # "Her choice of words is a little strange. It sounds like she's saying that she doesn't like celebrations, but likes doing everything involved with them. I don't know if it's worth pursuing, though, and it could be that I just misunderstood."
    "おかしな言い方だな。お祭りは好きじゃないけど、それにまつわることはみんな好き、と言っているように聞こえる。でも追及するほどのこととも思えないし、俺が誤解しただけかもしれない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5328
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_aed2ef0b:

    # mi "What about you, Hicchan~?"
    mi "ひっちゃんはどうなの～？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5330
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_0d5332ed:

    # hi "I am, or else I'd just stay home, wouldn't I? That's the logical step."
    hi "俺だって楽しみだよ。でなきゃ自分ちに引きこもってるだろ？　それが理屈ってもんだ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5335
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_8ac61042:

    # mi "Ahaha~! Hicchan, you're not that logical~! So~! That's really surprising! Hm, okay, though. I was just making sure, because you didn't look like you were having a lot of fun last time. Me and Shicchan were a little worried, because of that."
    mi "あはは～！　ひっちゃんはそんなに理屈っぽい人じゃないよ～！　だから～！　それってとってもびっくり！ うん、でもわかったよ。確認したかっただけなの。学園祭の時はあんまり楽しくなさそうだったから。それでわたしもしっちゃんもちょっと心配してたんだよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5337
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_3b266f1e:

    # hi "Hey, I had fun. I guess I ended up appreciating it more than I expected to."
    hi "おいおい、俺だって楽しんでたぞ。思ってたより面白かったくらいさ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5342
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_d2f1d7db:

    # mi "Really, Hicchan~? Wahahaha~! What part of it? Tell me~!"
    mi "ほんと、ひっちゃん～？　わははは～！　どのへんが面白かったの？　教えて～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5344
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_fe463db2:

    # hi "Well, there were fireworks at the end. They were… really nice."
    hi "そうだな、最後の花火。あれは……すごくよかった"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5346
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_e4713620:

    # hi "I think you slept through them."
    hi "お前は眠り込んでたみたいだけどな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5351
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_a271f04c:

    # mi "Aw~… I always fall asleep early. But~! I won't sleep through them this year! I'll definitely stay awake!"
    mi "え～……わたし、いつも早寝しちゃうから。でも～！　今年は眠ったりしないよ！　絶対最後まで起きてるから！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5353
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_ca136366:

    # hi "I don't think they have fireworks during Tanabata. It's a different mood entirely."
    hi "七夕には花火はないと思うけどな。雰囲気が全然違うし"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5355
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_da20d537:

    # hi "Maybe you can get Shizune to petition them to have them, though. And to move the fireworks to an earlier time."
    hi "花火をやってほしいって嘆願書を静音に出してもらうよう頼めばいいんじゃないか。それと花火の時間を早めにしてもらえば"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5360
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_ffff02ac:

    # mi "Hahahahahaha~! Maybe I will~! That's a great idea, Hicchan!"
    mi "はははははは～！　それもありだね～！　すごくいいアイディアだよ、ひっちゃん！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5362
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_792c87b1:

    # hi "Ah, no, no it's not! Don't do that. I wasn't being serious."
    hi "えっ、いやいやいや違うだろ！　やめろって。冗談だよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5364
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_ce18b9a4:

    # hi "Although… maybe it would annoy Shicc— Shizune."
    hi "でも……しっちゃ――静音は怒るかもしれないけどな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5369
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_7bafff5c:

    # mi "Wahaha~. You make it sound like you would like that, Hicchan."
    mi "わはは～。でもひっちゃんはそうしたいって感じに聞こえるよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5374
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_2a2d48db:

    # mi "Hicchan~! Do you like Shicchan?"
    mi "ひっちゃん～！　しっちゃんのこと、好きなの？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5376
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_beac5440:

    # "I can't say yes or no, and, sitting down like I am, I can't even smoothly leave."
    "イエスともノーとも言えない。しかも座っているのでさりげなく立ち去ることもできない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5378
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_505017b0:

    # hi "Don't be silly; the one I like is you."
    hi "バカなこと言うなよ。俺が好きなのはお前だよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5383
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_ba654572:

    # mi "Ahahaha~! Really, Hicchan? Hm~! No, you're kidding, right? You must like Shicchan more."
    mi "あははは～！　ほんと、ひっちゃん？　ん～！　違うな、今の冗談だよね？　しっちゃんの方がもっと好きに決まってるよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5385
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_9b183fcb:

    # hi "Misha, you jump to conclusions too much."
    hi "ミーシャ、お前早合点しすぎだろ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5390
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_12747661:

    # mi "But you almost called her Shicchan! So~! I'm right, right~?"
    mi "でもしっちゃんって言いそうになったじゃん！　だから～！　わたしは合ってるの。でしょ～？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5392
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_6bd11eb8:

    # hi "It's because you call her Shicchan all the time. It got stuck in my head. Osmosing language is common, you know. Besides, it's one little slip-up. And by your logic, you should like her more than me. And… are you making fun of me or something?"
    hi "お前がいっつも静音のことをしっちゃんって言ってるからだよ。こっちの頭の中から離れないんだ。言葉が移るってのはよくあることなんだぞ。それにたった一回言い間違えただけだし お前の理屈だと、お前の方が俺より静音のことを好きじゃなきゃおかしいだろ。それと……お前からかってるのか？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5397
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_e39fcd2d:

    # mi "Wahaha~!"
    mi "わはは～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5402
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_ee6c7aae:

    # mi "Maybe~."
    mi "そうかもね～"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5407
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_09c79bf5:

    # mi "I'm hungry. Did you eat breakfast, Hicchan?"
    mi "おなか減っちゃった。朝ごはん食べた、ひっちゃん？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5409
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_08aed60b:

    # hi "No. Just medicine."
    hi "いや。薬だけ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5414
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_eede1043:

    # mi "Hm…"
    mi "ふむう……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5416
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_ef01529b:

    # "Misha twirls her finger lazily in the air to keep her hands busy as she thinks."
    "考えている間も手を遊ばせないように、けだるそうに指をくるくると回している。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5421
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_ea4870eb:

    # mi "We should eat something, then~! Do you think they will be serving breakfast today?"
    mi "じゃあ何か食べようよ～！　今日は学食の朝ごはん、あるかなあ？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5423
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_c7ed0915:

    # "That's really the kind of thing a member of the Student Council should know. I can't say that, though. I'm on the Student Council and don't know."
    "そういうことは生徒会のメンバーなら知らなきゃいけないことだと思う。でも俺の口からは言えない。俺だってメンバーだけど知らないし。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5425
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_e8577c02:

    # hi "It didn't seem like anyone was working in the kitchen when I entered the building, but I don't know for sure."
    hi "俺が校舎に入ったときは、厨房で働いてる人は誰もいなさそうだったぞ。はっきりとはわからないけど"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5430
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_b20375e3:

    # mi "Hey, Hicchan, have you ever heard about those vending machines that you can get food from, like burgers, soup, and even pizza? Wouldn't it be great if we had some of those at our school~?"
    mi "ねえひっちゃん、食べ物が買える自動販売機って聞いたことある？　バーガーとかスープとか、それにピザも！　そういうのがうちの学校にもあったらすごいと思わない～？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5432
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_e95da307:

    # hi "I don't know, I always thought those machines were kind of weird."
    hi "どうだろうな。ああいう自販機って変な感じだなっていつも思ってたから"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5437
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_764c3997:

    # mi "Imagine how cool it would be if we had machines like that at our school, Hicchan~! It would almost be like magic, wouldn't it?"
    mi "そういう自販機があったらどんなにいいか考えてみてよ、ひっちゃん～！　ほとんど魔法みたいだよ、そうじゃない？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5439
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_e151a294:

    # mi "Hot food coming out of a vending machine, that's so amazing, I could never imagine that. Seeing one of those machines would be like a dream!"
    mi "自動販売機からあったかい食べ物が出てくるなんて、ほんとにすごいよ。わたしなら想像もできないよ。そういう自販機に出会えたら、もう夢みたいだよ！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5444
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_1b36168a:

    # mi "Hm~… We don't have machines like that in this whole town, though~. It's too early to even go into town~! I won't be able to eat breakfast, Hicchan, that's the most important meal of the day. Everyone says so~! Ah, I want to eat!"
    mi "ん～……でも、そんな機械はこの町のどこにもないんだよ～。まだ町に出るのだって早すぎるよ～！　これじゃ朝ごはん食べられないよ、ひっちゃん、一日で一番大事な食事なのに。みんなそう言ってるよ～！ あー、ごはん食べたーい！ "

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5446
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_99501956:

    # hi "You're really silly. If it bothers you so much, I'll buy you a soda."
    hi "ほんとにばかだな。そんなに腹減ってるなら、俺がソーダおごってやるよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5451
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_c0f4852b:

    # "Misha puffs out her cheeks and puts on her serious face."
    "ミーシャは頬を膨らませて、真剣そうな顔をする。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5453
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_a5b2b5ba:

    # mi "Hicchan, a soda is not a breakfast. It's like water~."
    mi "ひっちゃん、ソーダは朝ごはんじゃないよ。水みたいなものじゃん～"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5455
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_b8c8d5db:

    # hi "It's not like water, it's a liquid. Water isn't food. Liquid can be food."
    hi "水みたいじゃない、液体だ。水は食べ物じゃない。液体は食べ物にはなる"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5457
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_117745e9:

    # "'Now who sounds like Shizune, Misha?' I want to say it. Even her tone reminds me of Shizune's unblinking, matter-of-fact way of stating the ridiculous. If I did say that, though, I would be the one who sounds like Shizune again."
    "『そっちこそ静音みたいな言い方じゃないか、ミーシャ？』そう言ってやりたい。その口調さえ、平然とした事務的な態度でとんでもないことを言う静音を彷彿とさせる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5459
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_2d6a07ef:

    # "It's terrible, her competitiveness is really rubbing off on me."
    "でも俺がそう言ったら、今度は俺がまた静音みたいな口のきき方になってしまう。ひどい話だ、あいつの負けず嫌いが本当に移ってしまっている。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5461
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_3f9263f0:

    # hi "Let's look for something to eat, then."
    hi "じゃあ何か食い物でも探すか"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5466
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_824fd7d3:

    # mi "…"
    mi "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5471
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_ac28c8e4:

    # mi "Okay. Ahahahaha~!"
    mi "おっけー。あはははは～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5479
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_3f43c53c:

    # "Predictably, our search for food in an empty school building this early in the morning leads only to failure."
    "予想はできていたけど、こんなに早い時間に無人の校舎で食べ物を探す努力は無駄にしかならなかった。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5481
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_cd5a3756:

    # "Misha decides to go off on her own after we both decide to give up for now, vowing to eat breakfast even though by now it's closer to time for brunch."
    "捜索をいったん断念した後、朝食をとると誓ったミーシャは一人で探し続ける決断をする。でももうブランチといってもいい時間だけど。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5486
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_df3d01aa:

    # "I go back to my dorm. The following hours tick by slowly, and I pass the time by catching up on my reading."
    "俺は寮の部屋に戻る。続く時間はゆっくりと流れ、俺はたまった本を読んで暇をつぶす。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5495
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_fc7a683d:

    # "Some of these books I haven't touched since I was in the hospital. Thinking back on it, it wasn't that long ago, even though it definitely feels like it was."
    "いくつかの本は、入院中に読んで以来手も触れていなかったものだ。振り返ってみると、そんなに昔のことでもない。気持ちの上では間違いなくそう感じられるのに。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5497
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_102c4dab:

    # "A free day, and I can't think of anything to do. I take a short nap, and as I change for the second time today, I realize that I never actually confirmed with Shizune or Misha when and where we would meet up."
    "暇な一日、そしてやることが何も思いつかない。少し昼寝をして、今日二度目の着替えを済ませながら、結局静音やミーシャと待ち合わせの場所や時間を全然確認していなかったことに気づく。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5499
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_0014c746:

    # "I guess that eventually they would come looking for me, but I would look pretty stupid if it came to that."
    "いずれ向こうから探しに来るだろうとは思うけど、でもそこまでいくと非常にばつが悪い。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5503
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_2e8f987d:

    # "It's already evening, so I should at least make an effort to find them first."
    "もう夕方だし、少なくとも先に二人を探す努力はすべきだろう。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5508
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_a5b47bad:

    # "Even though the grounds aren't exactly flooded with people and it should be impossible to miss Misha's pink hair even if they were, I have a lot of difficulty finding them."
    "まだ学校内はそれほど人は多くないし、仮に混んでいてもミーシャのピンクの髪を見逃すことなんてあり得ないけど、それでも二人を見つけるのは大変だった。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5513
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_68b120a3:

    # "Finally, I run into them at the front gate, which was the first place I had looked."
    "最初に見に行った正門で、ようやく二人にはち合わせる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5518
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_850e0796:

    # ssh "Hello!"
    ssh "こんにちは！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5520
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_00eaf5cf:

    # "She attempts to punctuate her normal greeting with a grand little sweep at the end."
    "いつもどおりの挨拶を、最後にもったいぶったように手をさっと振って強調しようとする。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5529
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_68f17d0d:

    # mi "Hicchan~! How're you?"
    mi "ひっちゃん～！　気分はどう？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5531
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_1104b593:

    # "It's strange seeing them in yukata, though I've been seeing yukata in general all night."
    "今夜は浴衣姿の人をたくさん目にしているのに、浴衣姿の二人を見るのは奇妙な感じがする。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5533
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_028a729b:

    # "Shizune's is simple and tasteful, which seems obvious for her in retrospect. For all her grand flourishes and over-the-top behavior, I think she would rather die than dress the part."
    "静音の浴衣はシンプルで上品だ。後から考えれば、わかりきっていたことだけど。普段は大げさな身振りや無茶な態度をとるけど、でも派手に着飾るくらいなら死ぬ方を選ぶと思う。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5535
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_0e033d81:

    # "What draws my eye is the hairpin she is wearing, a pearl flower that gleams softly in the moonlight."
    "身につけているヘアピンが目にとまる。月明かりを受けて柔らかく輝く真珠の花だ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5537
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_0e67f5d7:

    # "It looks pretty on her, but in a way it also feels out of place. As if it's too elaborate for a high school girl, or maybe just for someone as secretly childish as Shizune."
    "よく似合っているけど、ある意味では場違いな感じもする。女子高生には、というか、密かに子供っぽいところのある静音みたいな奴にはちょっと精巧すぎるように見える。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5539
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_71612e43:

    # "Misha's yukata is about what I expected, so it actually fits a little too well. Paired with her bubblegum pink hair, she looks cute, but anachronistic."
    "ミーシャの浴衣はだいたい予想通りで、なんだか似合いすぎている。風船ガムのようなピンクの髪と合わさって、かわいく見えるけど時代錯誤な感じだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5541
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_baceb866:

    # hi "You two look nice."
    hi "二人ともきれいだな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5546
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_183e608f:

    # mi "Thanks, Hicchan~!"
    mi "ありがと、ひっちゃん～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5551
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_ef2b123c:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5553
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_4e02e853:

    # mi "Hicchan, you're a little late. We were waiting here a while for you, did you forget the time or the place?"
    mi "ひっちゃん、ちょっと遅かったね。しばらく待っててあげたんだけど、時間とか場所は忘れちゃったの？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5555
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_1b065a38:

    # mi "Oh well~! Let's get going, Hicchan~!"
    mi "まあいっか～！　じゃあいこ、ひっちゃん～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5560
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_ef2b123c_1:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5562
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_4db2fe1b:

    # "Misha dropping this line of discussion saves me what could potentially be a pretty embarrassing thing to own up to; specifically, that I had been looking for them for at least an hour."
    "ミーシャが話を切り上げてくれたので、実は一時間も前から二人を探していたという、白状してしまったら非常に恥ずかしい羽目になる事態を逃れることができた。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5564
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_e3611868:

    # "Seeing Shizune and Misha looking so cheerful, it's hard not to want to fall into the atmosphere and enjoy a nice night out."
    "こんなに上機嫌な静音とミーシャを見ていると、雰囲気に身を任せて夜を楽しみたいという気分に逆らえなくなる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5566
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_996ae1d6:

    # "What bothers me is that I'm having some trouble reading Shizune's signing tonight. I haven't been to sign language class in almost a week, so I'm not surprised. I guess having lost focus for a while, I'm slipping. It certainly wouldn't be the first time."
    "厄介なことに、今夜は静音の手話が読み取りにくい。一週間くらい手話のクラスに出ていなかったので、無理もないけど。ちょっと集中力をなくしていたんだろう。記憶が薄れている。今回だけではすまないだろうな。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5568
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_45da7a79:

    # hi "Hold on, where are we going? Into town?"
    hi "ちょっと待てよ、どこに行くんだ？　町に出るのか？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5573
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_1d374688:

    # ssh "Yes."
    ssh "そう"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5575
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_ab22119c:

    # hi "That doesn't make any sense. We haven't even checked out what's on the grounds. Unless you two decided to have fun while I wasn't looking."
    hi "わけわかんねえぞ。学校の中の出し物だってひとつもチェックしてないじゃないか。二人とも俺がいない間に楽しんでたっていうなら話は別だけどさ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5580
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_b8ef2dc7:

    # ssh "We're going to come back; we'll be working our way up."
    ssh "また戻ってくるわ。下から上がってくるのよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5585
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_8c7a40f2:

    # mi "Hahaha~! Either way, Hicchan, we have to walk into town and then back up if we want to see everything. So~! This way, after we're done, we'll be right by our dorms when we're tired. It works out perfectly~!"
    mi "ははは～！　どっちにしてもね、ひっちゃん、お祭りを全部見たければ町に降りてから戻ってくるしかないの。だから～！　こうすれば、全部終わってくたびれた後は寮の目の前に戻ってくるわけ。完璧だね～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5592
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_6447555a:

    # "That is admittedly logical. Shizune doesn't give me much time to argue anyway, grabbing me by the arm and lightly trying to pull me along."
    "確かに理屈には合ってるな。どのみち静音はあまり反論する時間を与えてくれず、俺の腕をつかんでそっと引っ張り出そうとする。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5605
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_1583d288:

    # "The streets illuminated only by the light of the moon and low lanterns tinted with tissue paper put me at ease."
    "月明かりと薄い紙で彩られ、低く掲げられた提灯だけが町並みを照らしている。その光景を見ると穏やかな気分になる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5607
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_5a9801a8:

    # "Now that we're in town, Shizune moves a bit more slowly in order to see the sights."
    "町に着くと、あたりの様子をよく見ようと静音が歩みをゆるめる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5609
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_6ba0b62b:

    # "So, I decide to walk more briskly in order to mess with her, but she quickly readjusts her own speed to match, letting out a soundless laugh before quickly signing to Misha with her off hand."
    "なので、ちょっかいを出そうとしてわざと早く歩いてみる。でも静音はすぐにスピードを合わせてきて、声のない笑い声を上げながら、空いている方の手でミーシャに手話を見せる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5611
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_ef2b123c_2:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5613
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_e35b7410:

    # mi "What do you want to do first, Hicchan~?"
    mi "まずはなにしよっか、ひっちゃん～？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5615
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_e5b2ad28:

    # hi "How about some games, if there are any?"
    hi "あるんだったら、ゲームでもやろうか？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5617
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_d69d042c:

    # mi "I thought you didn't like games, Hicchan."
    mi "ゲームは嫌いなんじゃなかったっけ、ひっちゃん"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5619
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_e305242d:

    # hi "I don't mind."
    hi "別にいいよ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5621
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_658149b3:

    # "For the second time today, I feel her slim fingers wrapping around mine. It feels like all this time, I've been pulled along by Shizune's will. Occasionally, it's quite tiring, but I think that for the most part, I wouldn't say I hate it."
    "静音の細い指が俺の指に絡み合う。これで今日二度目だ。今の今までずっと、俺は静音の意志に引きずられてきたような気がする。時にはとても気疲れするけど、でもだいたいは悪くなかったんじゃないかと思う。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5623
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_3660727b:

    # "It's just the quality of some people to drag others into their lives, like a storm. That word fits Shizune sometimes, I think. Although I didn't want to tell Misha earlier today, I do like her."
    "まるで嵐のように、自分の生き方に他の人を巻き込んでしまえるという性格でしかないんだろう。時にはその言葉が静音に合っているようにも思う。今朝ミーシャに言いたくなかったけど、俺は確かに静音が好きだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5625
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_f9f4036c:

    # mi "Hicchan, you're going to win a doll for me too this time, right~?"
    mi "ひっちゃん、今度はわたしにも人形ゲットしてくれるんだよね、ね～？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5627
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_c02f6c7f:

    # hi "You're still thinking about that? Okay, I will."
    hi "まだそのこと考えてるのか？　わかったよ、取ってやる"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5635
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_95ffaac8:

    # "The time passes by faster than I thought it could as we run around, trying to do as many frivolous things as possible."
    "たわいないことをできるだけいっぱいこなそうとあちこち回っているうちに、時間は思っていたよりも早く過ぎていく。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5640
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_00ba16c9:

    # mi "Snow cones! Hicchan, do you want one~?"
    mi "スノーコーンだよ！　ひっちゃん、一つ食べる～？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5642
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_7a11023a:

    # "Misha runs towards the stand, not even waiting to hear my answer."
    "俺の答えを待つまでもなく、ミーシャは屋台に駆け寄る。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5651
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_c9bd26e3:

    # ssh "They look delicious, I want one too. We'll play rock-paper-scissors to see who can pay for them all."
    ssh "おいしそうね、私も欲しい。誰が代金を払うか、じゃんけんで決めましょう"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5653
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_ad3c38b9:

    # hi "Or… we could each pay for our own."
    hi "もしくは……割り勘でいいんじゃないか"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5658
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_07fede90:

    # mi "Hicchan~, what flavor do you want?"
    mi "ひっちゃん～、何味がいい？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5660
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_629b47c7:

    # hi "The blue one."
    hi "青いやつ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5665
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_852c41a3:

    # ssh "Blue is not a flavor."
    ssh "青は味じゃないわ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5667
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_bbedd4fb:

    # hi "I knew that…"
    hi "わかってるよ……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5669
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_81e17156:

    # ssh "Ordering something based on color is childish."
    ssh "色でものを頼むなんて子供みたい"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5671
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_c805a510:

    # hi "You're childish. What are you getting? Are you getting strawberry? Ha! That's such a childish flavor, only children eat strawberry."
    hi "そっちがガキっぽいんだよ。お前は何頼むんだ？　イチゴ？　はは！　それこそガキっぽい味じゃないか。イチゴなんて子供しか食べないんだぞ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5676
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_fa80fec3:

    # ssh "You should get plain, the most mature flavor of all!"
    ssh "プレーンを頼みなさいよ。一番大人の味！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5678
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_7991cdec:

    # "I want to know where her personality comes from. I wonder if I would think that way if she hadn't been the first student I ended up having a conversation with on my first day here."
    "こういう性格がどこから出てくるのか知りたい。俺の登校初日に最初に話をしたのが静音じゃなかったら、果たしてそんな考えが出てきただろうか。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5680
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_9ddd7b8e:

    # "It's entirely possible that I'd have missed the parts of her that kept drawing me in."
    "もしそうなっていたら、いつも俺を引きつけ続ける静音の特徴を見逃していたに違いないと思う。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5682
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_212cf224:

    # "If I didn't know that she couldn't hear me, and that she was so competitive, and so focused with getting me to join the Student Council, and so alternatingly playful and sharp…"
    "俺の言葉が聞こえないこと、負けず嫌いなこと、俺を生徒会に引き入れることにあんなに必死なこと、お茶目さと鋭さが入り交じること、それを知らなかったとしたら……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5684
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_4488b1f9:

    # "Without these constant new facets to keep my interest in her, would I have grown to like her so much?"
    "静音はいつも新しい側面を見せて、俺の興味を引き続ける。それがなかったら、俺は彼女を好きになっていただろうか。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5686
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_0186d5c6:

    # "It's likely that I'm overthinking it."
    "考えすぎだろうな。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5688
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_b4c71994:

    # hi "Aren't you going to make a wish?"
    hi "何か願い事はしないのか？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5693
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_11fbaa44:

    # mi "Shicchan never makes wishes, Hicchan!"
    mi "しっちゃんは願い事なんてしないんだよ、ひっちゃん！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5695
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_380e2d66:

    # hi "Oh really? Not even on New Year's? Why's that?"
    hi "ほんとか？　新年の時も？　どうして？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5700
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_ef2b123c_3:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5702
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_b6d34bd4:

    # "Shizune tents her fingers and smiles, but won't answer."
    "静音は指を重ねて笑みを浮かべるけど、答えない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5704
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_1e3b1637:

    # ssh "It's a secret."
    ssh "秘密"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5709
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_8ac3ec22:

    # mi "I know~!"
    mi "知ってるよ～！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5711
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_b7dceb18:

    # mi "Hicchan, do you want me to tell you?"
    mi "ひっちゃん、教えてほしい？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5716
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_b33ba1f7:

    # shi "…!"
    shi "……！"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5718
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_b3d21ad1:

    # hi "Yes."
    hi "ぜひ聞きたい"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5723
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_7ad8102e:

    # "Shizune alternates between as many forceful iterations of 'no' she can think of."
    "静音は思いつく限りの力強い『ノー』の表現を次々と繰り出す。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5728
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_d5d053ce:

    # mi "Wahaha~! I'll tell you later, okay?"
    mi "わはは～！　じゃあ後で教えてあげる。おっけ～？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5735
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_5e9ae620:

    # mi "Actually, I feel tired. I think I'm going to go to bed early~."
    mi "なんだか疲れちゃった。今日は早めにお休みするかも～"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5740
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_da806237:

    # ssh "Really?"
    ssh "ほんとに？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5742
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_09dc25cd:

    # hi "It doesn't feel like it's been that long."
    hi "そんなに時間がたった気もしないけどな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5744
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_d8bf73cf:

    # "Time flies when you're having fun."
    "楽しんでいるときは時間が早く感じるな。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5749
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_e5d214fe:

    # mi "But~! it has, Hicchan. Maybe I can visit Yuuko first, then go back? Or~… I don't know~."
    mi "でも～！　もう経っちゃってるんだよ、ひっちゃん。先に優子さんのとこ行って、それで帰るかも？　それとも～……わかんないな～"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5754
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_67ed0a78:

    # mi "Well, it doesn't matter. Have fun without me, okay~?"
    mi "まあ、いいや。わたし抜きで楽しんでね、い～い？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5756
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_6cabda70:

    # hi "We're going to go back to the school soon anyway, Misha."
    hi "どうせもうすぐ学校に戻るんだぜ、ミーシャ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5765
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_3d506c20:

    # "Misha doesn't want to hear it, and leaves anyway. Shizune starts to wonder why just as soon as I do, but while I keep it in my head, she signs it, seeming to want to discuss the possible reasons."
    "ミーシャは聞きたくなかったようで、そのまま立ち去ってしまう。静音も俺と同じように怪訝そうだ。俺はその疑問を口にしなかったけど、静音は理由を話し合いたいかのように手話をし始める。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5771
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_26573e60:

    # "After we're both done seeing all there is to see, I check the time, and find that it is pretty late. My energy is starting to wear off, and it's a miracle that I managed to have even this much, too."
    "見るものを全部見て回ったあと、時間を確かめると、もうずいぶん遅くなっていることに気づく。俺の体力も底をつき始めている。ここまで持ったこと自体が奇跡的だ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5773
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_214f936c:

    # "Even Shizune is starting to look a bit tired. We make our way back to the grounds."
    "静音も少し疲れているように見える。俺たちは学校への帰り道をたどる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5782
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_c9375239:

    # "Shizune seems disappointed when she sees the school building lit up and teeming with students."
    "明かりがついていて、生徒で一杯の校舎を目にして、静音はがっかりしているようだ。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5784
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_52cbc3f0:

    # his "Something wrong?"
    his "どうかしたのか？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5789
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_279cce1a:

    # ssh "I wanted to go up to the roof, but now there are too many people. I'm tired, so it might be for the best."
    ssh "屋上に行きたかったけど、これじゃ人が多すぎる。私も疲れているし、これで良かったのかも"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5791
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_7ae7f44c:

    # his "There are probably couples on the roof, since it's that kind of holiday."
    his "屋上はカップルばかりだろうな。今日は休日みたいなものだし"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5793
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_6ef9e37d:

    # his "Then again, I wouldn't know. Is that how it really is? I'd never really been to any festivals before coming here."
    his "でもそうでもないかもな。実際、そういうもんなのか？　ここに来る前はお祭りなんて一度も行ったことがないからさ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5795
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_ef2b123c_4:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5797
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_8824ac42:

    # his "I'm disappointed, I thought you said you wanted to see what the school was doing last, like saving the best for last. Now you're telling me you don't want to? Not even a little? I thought you would have more energy. I don't feel tired."
    his "がっかりしたぞ。学校のお祭りを最後に見てみたいって言ったのはそっちじゃないか。一番いいのは最後に取っておくって それで今度はもう行きたくないって言うのか？　全然？　お前はもっとエネルギーがあると思ってた。俺は疲れてなんかいないぞ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5802
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_771ea872:

    # "This seems to spark her competitive spirit, and Shizune immediately perks up, although it's then that I realize I didn't have anywhere in mind to take her, and I don't feel like going to the main building myself."
    "今のが負けん気に火をつけたらしく、静音はすぐに頭を上げる。でも言っては見たものの、どこへ連れて行く当てもなかったことに気づく。それに俺自身も本校舎に行く気にはならない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5809
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_93ac5f0a:

    # "Fortunately, the area behind the school is both deserted and impressive-looking today. I'd never appreciated how sprawling and well kept it was until seeing it at night. It almost seems to go on forever in the moonlight."
    "幸い校舎の裏は人気もなく、今夜は眺めが良さそうだ。夜中に見るまで、その広さと行き届いた手入れぶりにちゃんと目を向けていなかった。月明かりに照らされて、校庭は果てしなく広がっているように見える。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5815
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_04eedca3:

    # ssh "It's very pretty, even though it's just a field."
    ssh "ただの校庭なのに、とてもきれいね"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5817
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_d619db7a:

    # "I'd thought earlier that she was too immature to pull off the old-fashioned clothes she is wearing tonight, but right now, she is quite beautiful in them."
    "さっきまで、静音は今夜の浴衣みたいな古風な服を着こなすには若すぎると思っていた。でも今は、静音の浴衣姿がとても美しいと思う。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5819
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_630676bd:

    # "It makes me think back to that day, the other festival that I went to with her. She had looked the same way then."
    "その姿が、前の学園祭を一緒に見て回ったときの日のことを思い起こさせる。その時も静音は同じように見えた。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5825
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5829
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_5e4f5eee:

    # n "{vspace=30}I want to tell her that I like her. Decisively, in one go. But even thinking about it is just so awkward."
    n "\nお前のことが好きだ、と伝えたい。はっきりと、一息に。でもこんなことを考えるだけでも、とんでもなく気まずい気分になってくる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5831
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_0dbb6f45:

    # n "And the more I like her, the more awkward and afraid I am of telling her how I feel, even now, when I could do so if I wanted without having to go through another person."
    n "それに静音のことを好きになればなるほど、自分の気持ちを伝えるのが決まり悪く、怖くなってくる。今だってそうだ。今なら別の人を介さなくても伝えられるというのに。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5833
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_8da8d3c3:

    # n "Not to mention, what if what happened last time happens again? If it does, I might not get off so easily with a months-long hospital stay. I don't want to even think about it."
    n "それどころか、前と同じことが今度も起きたらどうする？　もしそうなったら、何ヶ月もの入院生活くらいでは済まないかもしれない。そんなの考えたくもない。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5835
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_913cbeef:

    # n "I try to shove the thoughts out of my mind any way possible. I try to dismiss them as unlikely fears."
    n "どうにかしてそんな考えを頭から追い出そうとする。心配のしすぎだと思おうとする。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5837
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_583716dd:

    # n "Still…"
    n "それでも……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5839
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_dfc465e1:

    # n "The first time I had seen all of my pills, I'd imagined them cascading before me, enough of them to choke me."
    n "あれだけの量の薬を初めて見たとき、それが滝のように俺の前に流れ落ちる様子を想像してしまった。自分が埋もれてしまうくらい、大量に。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5841
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_5b1b4af2:

    # n "I still think about it from time to time. I can't say that it's not a legitimate concern. Times like these are nice enough that I can forget, though."
    n "今でも時々そのことを考える。当然の懸念とは言えない。でもこういう素晴らしい瞬間には、そんな記憶も忘れられる。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5843
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5852
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_4da977b5:

    # ssh "My favorite thing about this school is that it's on top of a mountain."
    ssh "この学校の好きなところは、山のてっぺんにあるってこと"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5854
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_fd15df0b:

    # his "Is it because it's that much closer to the sky?"
    his "それだけ空に近いからか？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5856
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_1d374688_1:

    # ssh "Yes."
    ssh "そう"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5858
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_be8d6102:

    # his "I like it too, but more because of the fresh air."
    his "俺も学校は好きだけど、どっちかというと空気がきれいなのがいいな"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5860
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_4b6ffd93:

    # his "You're so competitive. Too competitive. If a whale bit you, you would bite it back."
    his "お前はほんと負けず嫌いだよな。負けず嫌いすぎる。お前、鯨に噛まれたら噛み返すだろ"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5865
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_ef2b123c_5:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5867
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_6141f9df:

    # "That makes her laugh, and she winks."
    "それを聞いて静音は笑い、ウィンクする。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5869
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_ce226af0:

    # ssh "Would that be so bad?"
    ssh "それ、そんなに悪いこと？"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5871
translate jp a2_shizune_when_stars_embrace_2aa646f4:

    # "Her smile is contagious."
    "こいつの笑顔は伝染する。"

# game/script-a2-shizune.rpy:5873
